msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Language: English\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"

msgid "diary_text_quest_20000"
msgstr ""
"I successfully killed ten goblins, and now the farmers of Sanguine can get "
"back to work feeding the refugees.  It sounds like there is more "
"investigating to be done to find out how Goblins got this close to the "
"Mercian capital."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20001"
msgstr ""
"It may take awhile to wash the smell of Lizard on a Stick out of my bag, but "
"I am glad I was able to help the people of Sanguine by reducing the amount "
"of Goblin Axes and food supplies the Goblin raiders have."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20002"
msgstr ""
"I successfully passed Allan the Councillor's trial, and collected the "
"achievement title of The Limber."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20003"
msgstr ""
"I met Simeon the Merchant, one of the other members of the Sanguine City "
"Council."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20004"
msgstr ""
"I was able to demonstrate my basic cooking skills to Simeon the Merchant."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20005"
msgstr ""
"I was able to demonstrate my basic taming skills to Simeon the Merchant."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20006"
msgstr ""
"I met Talaod the Blacksmith, one of the other members of the Sanguine City "
"Council."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20007"
msgstr "I was able to demonstrate my basic armorsmithing skills for Talaod."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20008"
msgstr "I was able to demonstrate my crafting skills for Talaod."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2001"
msgstr ""
"Our old enemies the gnolls have appeared once more within the tribelands, "
"this time in {$i13}. I have reported for duty with Isenda the Clever to "
"assist with removing the gnolls from our lands once again."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20014"
msgstr ""
"I was able to get enough fish to cook up quite a feast for the Monkfield "
"Militia. 5 Cooked Herring, Trout and Cod."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20015"
msgstr ""
"The first of the quickness achievement titles in now mine. I completed "
"Simeon the Merchant's challenge, and killed 200 Akathars."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20016"
msgstr ""
"I have gained the first of the wisdom achievement titles, that of The "
"Thoughtful, after completing Talaod the Blacksmith's task."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20017"
msgstr ""
"I have helped Sanguine deal with the Scumling infestation of the city sewer "
"system, by accepting to enter the sewers and kill 10 Scumling Workers and 5 "
"Scumling Guard, and the Scumling Queen. According to Talaod the Blacksmith, "
"occasional sewer sweeps are necessary, to maintain the Scumling population "
"as low as possible."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20018"
msgstr ""
"I was able to help out Talaod the Blacksmith and Jonn the Mage by re-killing "
"some zombies in the sewers and bringing their corpseflesh to Jonn for "
"enchanting.  There was a strange cultist responsible for raising the dead."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20019"
msgstr "Niane the Arcanist paid me to craft a Trollstaff."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2002"
msgstr ""
"The gnolls are no match for the mahirim. I have returned victorious from "
"their pathetic camp in {$i13}, after I killing three gnolls just as Isenda "
"the Clever instructed me. Why the gnolls believe that they can live within "
"the tribelands is beyond me."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20020"
msgstr ""
"I was able to demonstrate my basic Alchemy skills for Niane and talk to "
"Sheena at the Market."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20021"
msgstr ""
"I created an enchanted Crystal and learned the Keen enchant by using "
"Darktaint, Bile and Cinder with a Numen catalyst at the Enchanting Ring."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20022"
msgstr ""
"After completing Niane the Arcanist's title challenge, I gained the the "
"first of the vitality badges and the title of The Stout."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20023"
msgstr ""
"I completed Jonn the Mage's trial, and gained the my first intelligent "
"achievement title, the title of The Clever."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20024"
msgstr ""
"I completed Torgard the Fighter's challenge, and gained the my first "
"strength achievement, the title of The Brawny."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20025"
msgstr ""
"I was able to kill 25 Goblins outside of Monkfield to help alleviate the "
"pressure on their local militia."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20026"
msgstr ""
"I've used my ever growing enchanting skills to help out the city of "
"Monkfield while they are beset by Goblin raiding parties."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20027"
msgstr ""
"I was able to help out the Monkfield Militia by crafting some Chainmail "
"armor to help with the battle against the Goblins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20028"
msgstr ""
"I was able to help out the Monkfield Militia by crafting some Cloth Armor "
"for their Ranger company."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20029"
msgstr ""
"I was able to help out Stonegar the Fighter in Monkfield by crafting some "
"weapons for their militia."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20030"
msgstr ""
"I was able to help the Monkfield Militia by supplying them with magic staves."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20031"
msgstr ""
"I was able to help the city of Monkfield by providing them some Minor "
"Healing Potions."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20032"
msgstr ""
"I was able supply the Monkfield Militia with a good quanity of raw materials "
"to use against the Goblin raiders."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20033"
msgstr ""
"I practiced my magic skills by attacking many goblins with the Mana Missile "
"spell."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20034"
msgstr ""
"I practiced my Archery skills by stabbing a whole mess of Goblins with "
"arrows."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20035"
msgstr ""
"I killed 5 Goblin Shamans on the mountain, but still feel like there is more "
"to this attack on Monkfield."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20036"
msgstr ""
"I found and destroyed a dark altar in the Goblin village that appears to "
"have been constructed by Malaut cultists."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20037"
msgstr ""
"I killed a bunch of Malaut cultists who were responsible for setting up a "
"dark altar and driving the Goblins to attack Monkfield."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20038"
msgstr "I killed the zombies outside the mining tunnel."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20039"
msgstr ""
"I killed some Skeletons at the Monkfield mine, and found Malaut cultists."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2004"
msgstr ""
"The humans have been reminded that it is we the mahirim who allow them to "
"live here within the tribelands. Four guildmasters dead, and if needed I "
"would gladly kill another four."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20040"
msgstr ""
"After clearing out the undead miners, I found and killed the Malaut Acolytes "
"responsible.  It seems as though Malaut is working a lot of dark magic in "
"Mercia and it is all part of a bigger plan."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20041"
msgstr "I crafted 25 Greataxes for the Monkfield Militia."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20042"
msgstr "I enchanted 1 Crystal for the Monkfield Militia."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20043"
msgstr ""
"I crafted 25 Chain Chausses to help protect the Monkfield Militia against "
"Goblins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20044"
msgstr ""
"I crafted 25 Cloth Arms to help the magic users in the Monkfield Militia."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20045"
msgstr ""
"I crafted 25 Troll Staves to help Alric fill his stockpile for the Militia."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20046"
msgstr ""
"I advanced my understanding of Greater Magic by using the Rend spell a "
"number of times while I fought monsters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20047"
msgstr ""
"I was able to stop the Malaut raiding party before it reached the city of "
"Monkfield.  This allowed the city council to send out scouts to get a better "
"idea of the overall situation in the region."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20048"
msgstr ""
"I wiped out the Goblins waiting to attack Monkfield in their staging area to "
"the North.  So many dead greenskins..."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20049"
msgstr ""
"I cleared a ruined house of dark cultists and undead for Arduin Strayshadow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2005"
msgstr ""
"Isenda the Clever seems to have everything under control he in {$i13}, and "
"has ask of me to deliver her report letter to the Circle of Neith. I have "
"reached the Circle of Neith and handed her letter to Celetia the White."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20050"
msgstr ""
"I fought an intense battle in Lainstone at an organized Goblin and Malaut "
"camp.  Barely made it out alive..."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20051"
msgstr ""
"Following my victories up North in Lainstone, I came back to Monkfield and "
"gave Cearl the Councillor a thorough report about everything we had done."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20052"
msgstr ""
"Cearl's scout, Eleanor, was killed by Mercian Highwaymen while she was out "
"scouting.  I decided to follow them West to see what else I could find out."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20053"
msgstr ""
"I tracked the outlaws down to the entrance of Castle Grayvale and killed "
"them, but heard dark sounding voices from inside the castle and decided to "
"head in."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20054"
msgstr ""
"I went farther into the Castle and killed a number of Malaut Cultists, and "
"the dark creatures they bring with them.  I heard more people up on one of "
"the top turrets of the castle though."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20055"
msgstr ""
"After battling through Grayvale Castle, I made my way up to the highest "
"turret and won an exhausting battle againt Count Grayvale, who was "
"transformed into some sort of monster, and Archduke Stabby, the leader of "
"the Goblins at Lainstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20056"
msgstr ""
"My initial adventure complete, I recounted the tale to Allan the Councillor "
"and he informed me that King Robert IV is largely an innefective ruler, and "
"his wife Queen Morgaine is more involved in managing the kingdom."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20057"
msgstr ""
"I have been rewarded with the achievement title of The Agile, the second of "
"the dexterity achievement titles, after killing a lot of Centaurs and some "
"Nalaed."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20058"
msgstr ""
"The third of the dexterity achievement titles has been claimed, that of The "
"Dextrous."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20059"
msgstr ""
"I have completed Niane the Arcanist's challenge, and gained the title of The "
"Hardy, the second of the vitality achievement titles."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20060"
msgstr ""
"After a lot of hard fighting, I was rewarded by Niane the Arcanist with the "
"title of The Tough, the third of the vitality achievement titles."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20061"
msgstr ""
"Jonn the Mage rewarded me with the title of The Sharp, the second of the "
"intelligence achievement titles."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20062"
msgstr ""
"Jonn the Mage was impressed to see me complete his challenge, and handed me "
"the third of the intelligence achievement titles, the title of The Smart."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20063"
msgstr ""
"I have gained the achievement title of The Muscular, after completing "
"Torgard the Fighter's challenge."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20064"
msgstr ""
"The title of The Strong, the third of the strength achievement titles and "
"the enchanted badge is now mine."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20065"
msgstr ""
"I have completed Talaod the Blacksmith's challenge, and gained the title of "
"The Knowledgeable, the second of the wisdom achievement titles."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20066"
msgstr ""
"After a lot of hard work, Talaod the Blacksmith rewarded me with the title "
"of The Wise, the third of the wisdom badge upgrade."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20067"
msgstr ""
"I have been rewarded with the achievement title of The Fleet, the second of "
"the quickness achievement titles, after successfully completing Simeon the "
"Merchant's challenge."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20068"
msgstr ""
"The title of The Swift, the third quickness achievement titles has been "
"successfully claimed."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20069"
msgstr ""
"I got my first spell with a Knock-Up effect and used it effectively in "
"combat."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20070"
msgstr ""
"I was able to get enough fish to cook up quite a feast for the Monkfield "
"Militia. 10 Cooked Herring, Trout and Cod."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20071"
msgstr "I was able supply the Monkfield Militia with more Shortbows"

msgid "diary_text_quest_20072"
msgstr ""
"I advanced my understanding of Lesser Magic by using the Eldritch Sphere "
"spell a number of times while I fought monsters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20073"
msgstr "I supplied Alric with 25 Minor Healing Potions"

msgid "diary_text_quest_20074"
msgstr "I crafted 20 Great Mauls and brought them to Torgard the Fighter."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20076"
msgstr ""
"I advanced my understanding of Greater Magic by using the Unburden spell 20 "
"times."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20077"
msgstr ""
"I crafted 20 Banded Helms and brought them to Talaod the Blacksmith for "
"inspection."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20079"
msgstr "I crafted 20 portions of Dough."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20081"
msgstr ""
"I crafted 20 Padded Armor Chest Pieces and brought them to Simeon the "
"Merchant."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20083"
msgstr ""
"I crafted 25 Minor Healing Potions and brought them to Alric for inspection."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20085"
msgstr "I crafted 20 Goblin Angrysticks and brought them to Alric."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20087"
msgstr "I crafted 2 Magic Crystals and brought them to Jonn the Mage."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20089"
msgstr "I crafted 20 Flatbows and brought them to Stonegar for inspection."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20091"
msgstr "I practiced my Axe skills by chopping up some baddies."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20092"
msgstr "I practiced my Club and Maces skills by smacking some heads."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20093"
msgstr "I practiced my Sword skills by stabbing some creatures."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20094"
msgstr "I practiced my GreatSword skills by slicing some creatures."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20095"
msgstr "I practiced my Greatclub skills by bashing some creatures."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20096"
msgstr "I practiced my Greataxe skills by chopping up some creatures."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20097"
msgstr "I practiced my Knives skill by doing a lot of stabbing."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20098"
msgstr "I practiced my Polearms skill by doing a lot of swinging."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20099"
msgstr "I got my first Fire Magic spell and used it on enemies."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20100"
msgstr "I got my first Air Magic spell and used it on enemies."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20101"
msgstr "I got my first Earth Magic spell and used it on enemies."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20102"
msgstr "I got my first Water Magic spell and used it on enemies."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20103"
msgstr ""
"I found the group of Trolls attacking people on the road and was able to "
"easily dispatch them."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20104"
msgstr ""
"I advanced my understanding of WitchCraft by using the Needles spell 20 "
"times."

msgid "diary_text_quest_20105"
msgstr ""
"I learned how to attack while mounted, and pushed back some remaining "
"Goblins who were near the road."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2011"
msgstr ""
"The goblin threat has been dealt with for now. I have reported for duty with "
"Isinda-Dai in {$k13}. According to Andor-Kai the Councillor, {$k13} has "
"become infested by numerous hivekin. It seems that there is always something "
"threatening Hunter's Moon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2012"
msgstr ""
"The hivekin are doing a good job stripping the lands of all vegetation. I "
"can see why Isinda-Dai considers the hivekin the plague of the lands. I have "
"completed the task of killing four Hivekin Foragers and two Hivekin Soldiers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2013"
msgstr ""
"It is good to know that the hivekin are useful for one thing. Their claws "
"can be used for crafting magical items. Isinda-Dai instructed me to gather "
"four claws, and that I did."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2014"
msgstr ""
"I have killed three of the centaurs in {$l13} as the Wolfmasks requested, "
"after the reports about the centaurs attacking our scouting parties. Why the "
"centaurs in {$l13} have been attacking our scouting parties is a mystery."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2015"
msgstr ""
"I have just arrived at the Wolfmask headquarters in {$l14}, and delivered "
"Isinda-Dai's report to Mardem-Kai on how things are progressing in the "
"{$k13}. This has mostly to do with the hivekin in the area."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2021"
msgstr ""
"The goblins have been pushed back, and Leenglow is safe for now. The time "
"has come to deal with another intruder. I have reported for duty with Aurmon "
"the Brave, to help deal with a group of trolls and kobolds who have been "
"creating problems in {$k11}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2022"
msgstr ""
"My first mission in the campaign against the growing troll and kobold "
"population in the region of {$k11} has been successful. Six kobolds less now "
"occupy Lake {$k11}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2023"
msgstr ""
"I have returned from the plateaus in {$k11} after killing three trolls and "
"three kobolds. At this rate we are surely to clean up {$k11} from these "
"filthy intruders."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2024"
msgstr ""
"Harvesting four units of troll blood was a bloody job, but it was worth the "
"effort. As Aurmon the brave told me, what better way to make good use of "
"these stinking trolls."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2025"
msgstr ""
"I have just handed Aurmon the Brave's progress report to Yaleria-Sai the "
"Able at the Longclaw headquarters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2031"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully destroyed six skeleton, that have mysteriously appeared "
"in {$g19}. Until it is discovered what dark forces have spawned these "
"undead, all we can do is to destroy them."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2032"
msgstr ""
"After the skeletons, it was time to remove some zombies from {$g19}, in our "
"efforts to clear out the undead from miredil. I successfully destroyed six "
"zombies, and put these tormented souls out of their misery."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2033"
msgstr ""
"In our efforts to remove the horrid undead from {$g19} and eventually from "
"miredil, Silawen the Councillor suggested that we harvest Corpseflesh from "
"the zombies. Corpseflesh can be used for enchanting items and weapons. I "
"extracted four units of Corpseflesh."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2035"
msgstr ""
"After battling the undead in {$g19}, Silawen the Councillor conducted a "
"report letter about the mysterious undead outbreak in {$g19}. I have handed "
"this letter to Silverleaf Aelathil of the Serene Spire."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2041"
msgstr ""
"I have reported in for duty in {$i17} with Naianir Treedancer. The region of "
"{$i17} is been overrun by kobolds, and the Arrowhead have requests help."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2042"
msgstr ""
"The situation with the kobolds in the old mines of {$i17}, was quite "
"serious. The kobolds have managed over the years to transform the old mines "
"into a proper kobold stronghold. I succeeded in removing six of the kobolds "
"from the old mines."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2043"
msgstr ""
"Apparently the ancient site in {$i17} is of some importance to Charybdis. "
"Scholars believe the site holds many hidden artifacts of the past, and plan "
"to start excavations soon. The only problem were the trolls of the region. "
"So I helped by removing four of the trolls that occupied the ancient site."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2044"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered and delivered three units of Timeless Blood, as requested by "
"Lysandir the Councillor. Who would have thought that the blood of the filthy "
"trolls could be of any value."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2045"
msgstr ""
"After successfully dealing with the kobold situation in {$i17}, I reported "
"for duty with Eredethil Swiftarrow of the Arrowheads. I delivering to him "
"Lysandir's detailed report letter, with all the information that had been "
"gathered about the kobolds of {$i17}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2051"
msgstr ""
"The goblin hordes might have been pushed away from King's Holdfast, but that "
"was not the end of our worries. Bandit orks have entered the region of "
"{$i19}, and I have reported for duty with Larwain Crystaldew to help deal "
"with this new problem."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2052"
msgstr ""
"I have killed five bandit orks. The reports were true, that bandit orks had "
"entered the region of {$i19}. The scouts did a good job detecting these "
"orks, before they could establish a strong presence in the Mirendil."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2053"
msgstr ""
"The dead of the old mining town inside the ancient crater of {$i19} had "
"risen as zombies, haunting the old town. I have managed to put back to sleep "
"six of these tormented souls."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2055"
msgstr ""
"It has been confirmed that the bandit orks pose no threat to Mirendil, and "
"will be easily dealt with in the near future. I have delivered this good "
"news to Elvallie the Councillor as requested by Larwain Crystaldew."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2056"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Caradial Elmheart of the Emerald Throne, after "
"killing a Ghoul Devour that had been lurking in an abandoned mine southwest "
"of King's Holdfast in {$g19}. It would seem that the Emerald Throne is "
"interested in the undead outbreaks within Mirendil, and is now collecting "
"information about this strange phenomenon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2063"
msgstr ""
"The goblin threat has been dealt with for now. Onghra in safe. I have "
"reported for duty with Marhek Darkfrost in {$m22}. According to Taelis the "
"Councillor, {$m22} has become infested by numerous hivekin. It seems that "
"there is always something threatening Onghral."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2064"
msgstr ""
"The hivekin are doing a good job of stripping the lands of all vegetation. I "
"can see why the hivekin are referred to as the plague of the lands. I have "
"completed the task of killing six hivekin just as instructed by Marhek "
"Darkfrost."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2065"
msgstr ""
"It is good to know that the hivekin are useful for one thing. Their claws "
"can be used for crafting magical items. Marhek Darkfrost instructed me to "
"gather four claws, and that is exactly what I did."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2066"
msgstr ""
"The queen is dead. I killed that useless bag of flesh, along with four of "
"her broodguards. According to Marhek Darkfrost, the only way to by sure we "
"can rid the lands of the hivekin plague, is to kill the hivekin queen."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2067"
msgstr ""
"After having helped Marhek Darkfrost deal with the hivekins{$m22}, I "
"returned to Ongrhal and gave a full report to Taelis the Councillor about "
"the hivekin situation. The Councillor seems pleased with the news."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2068"
msgstr ""
"I have reached the Radiant Circle headquarters in {$l24}, and delivered to "
"Shulazu Nightshade a very strange and bizarre package from Taelis the "
"Councillor, a human ear. Apparently the Radiant Circle are interested in "
"acquiring materials that can be used in the creation of magical items."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2075"
msgstr ""
"Deep Yishku is no longer threatened by the goblins. I have reported for duty "
"with Laeseri Poisonglow in {$o22}, as instructed by the Harn Mandean to help "
"deal with a intruding kobolds and gnolls who have been creating problems in "
"{$o22}. The Harn Mandean are not please that these intruders have "
"established small villages in the region. We have instructed us to look into "
"this on their behalf."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2076"
msgstr ""
"I have engaged the kobold villages in {$o22}, killed six koblods as "
"instructed by Laeseri Poisonglow, and gathered information about these "
"pathetic creatures. According to Laeseri, it is a grand honor to work for "
"the Harn Mandean."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2077"
msgstr ""
"After assessing the koblods, I engaged the gnolls that had invaded the "
"region of {$o22}. Although stronger that the kobolds, I found no problem in "
"killing three gnolls, and later returning to Laeseri Poisonglow with my "
"assessment of their strengths."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2078"
msgstr ""
"Apparently more information was needed about the gnolls in {$o22}. This time "
"I gathered three gnoll stompers, a crude bludgeoning weapon used by many "
"gnolls. Laeseri Poisonglow somehow believes this will give us a better "
"understanding of these creatures."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2079"
msgstr ""
"Information about the kobolds and gnolls in {$o22} has been gathered. Having "
"completed all that the Harn Mandean has asked of us, Laeseri Poisonglow "
"instructed me to return to Deep Yishku and deliver a full report to Nirgash "
"the Councillor."

msgid "diary_text_quest_208"
msgstr ""
"Uzrok the Councillor requested that the escapee goblins from Chopping Necks, "
"be hunted down and killed. I successfully located and killed four of the "
"pathetic greenskins. Did the goblins think they could actually escape?"

msgid "diary_text_quest_2080"
msgstr ""
"I have reached the Harn Mandean and handed the Councillor's letter to "
"Aeshanta Darkspire. Nirgash the Councillor is pleased with the work I did in "
"{$o22}, and only saw it fit that I be the one to deliver his report letter "
"to the Harn Mandean."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2088"
msgstr ""
"The goblins have been pushed back, and Akathos is safe once again. I have "
"reported for duty with Aurmon the Brave, to help deal with the undead that "
"haunt the abandoned mining camp in {$o24}, as requested by the Temple of the "
"God King."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2089"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully destroyed six of the skeletons that have been haunting "
"the abandoned mining camp in{$o24}. Is the giant crystal really responsible "
"for the creation of all these undead?"

msgid "diary_text_quest_2090"
msgstr ""
"Harvesting those three units of Corpseflesh was a messy job. According to "
"Mugash, Corpseflesh can be used in the creation of magical items."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2091"
msgstr ""
"The Bone Knights were tough opponents, but not tough enough to stop me from "
"destroying four of them. According to Mugash Blackhaunt, the Bone Knights "
"are the strongest of the undead within the abandoned mining camp in {$o24}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2092"
msgstr ""
"We have cleared out a large number of undead that were roaming within the "
"abandoned mining camps in {$o24}, just as requested by the Temple of the God "
"King. I have reached the Temple of the God King, and handed to Nathar "
"Blackorb a report letter from Mugash Blackhaunt."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2098"
msgstr ""
"Once the goblin threat was removed from Eirhjelm, I reported for duty with "
"Dis Fatespinner in {$o10}. There is an undead outbreak in {$o10}, and I am "
"to help Dis Fatespinner gather information about this unnatural phenomenon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2099"
msgstr ""
"I successfully extracted four units of corpseflesh from the zombies in "
"{$o10}, as requested by Dis Fatespinner. I imagine these samples are part of "
"the information Dis Fatespinner is gathering, about the undead in {$o10}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_210"
msgstr ""
"I have retrieved two goblin axes from the fallen goblins. According to Uzrok "
"the Councillor, these looted axes will be used by the goblin slaves in "
"Chopping Necks, to gather firewood for the sacrificial pyres."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2100"
msgstr ""
"In the process of helping Dis Fatespinner gather information about the "
"undead in {$o10}, I managed to destroy six of skeletons that are haunting "
"the swamps of {$o10}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2101"
msgstr ""
"According to Dis Fatespinner, I have battled the strongest of the undead "
"that have appeared in {$o10}, the dire zombies, and successfully destroyed "
"three of them. If these are the strongest, we have nothing to fear."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2102"
msgstr ""
"I delivered Dis Fatespinner's report letter to Garin Silvervault to the "
"Voice of Ymir's headquarters. Dis Fatespinner had written a letter with all "
"the information that had been gathered about the undead outbreak in {$o10}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2108"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Skathi Shieldmaiden in Otredale. Arngard the "
"Councillor informed me that the abandoned dwarven mines of Otredale are "
"overrun by skeletons and kobolds. The time has come to retake the mines."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2109"
msgstr ""
"I ventured into the northern mines of Otredale, and destroyed six of the "
"skeleton that were lurking inside them. These mines have been deserted for a "
"very long time."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2110"
msgstr ""
"The kobold camp in front of the eastern Otredale mines, should not be a "
"problem much longer. I killed six of the kobolds, and send the rest running "
"for their lives."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2111"
msgstr ""
"I have found the Horn of the Five. All that remains is the bring the horn to "
"Skathi Shieldmaiden."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2112"
msgstr ""
"I successfully recovered the Horn of the Five from the kobold camp in "
"Otredale, and delivered it to Skathi Shieldmaiden.  Apparently, this is an "
"item of great importance to the Five Beards Trading Company."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2113"
msgstr ""
"After recovering the Horn of the Five, Skathi Shieldmaiden instructed me to "
"deliver it to the Five Beards Trading Company's headquarters in Ringfain. "
"Once there, I handed it to Garn Runeshield."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2119"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Magnus Forkbeard to help with a new problem. "
"Kobolds have appeared in {$p10}, an have begun attacking the trade routes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_212"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered five units of stone as requested by Bigthug the Blacksmith, "
"stone that will be used as the main building material for the construction "
"of the Small Stair in Chopping Necks."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2120"
msgstr ""
"I killed six of the kobolds, which according to Magnus Forkbeard were "
"attacking the caravans along the trade routes in {$p10}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2121"
msgstr ""
"I ventured up to the stone towers of {$p10}, and killed three trolls. The "
"trolls are behind the kobold attacks along the trading routes. Somehow the "
"trolls were controlling the kobolds, and using them for their dirty work."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2122"
msgstr ""
"It was only fair that since the trolls were stealing from our caravans, that "
"we in return should steal something from them. Three units of Timeless "
"Blood, is just the beginning."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2123"
msgstr ""
"After dealing with the thieving trolls and kobolds in {$p10}, I delivered "
"Magnus Forkbeard's detailed report letter to Thain Strongforge at the Order "
"of the Axe in {$p11}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2129"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Stranglar Bloodaks, to assist him gather "
"information about the trolls that entered {$u12}. But before that, I had "
"gathered and delivered three units of troll blood to Stranglar Bloodaks, "
"just to get on his good side as Uzrok the Councillor warned me."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2130"
msgstr ""
"I have killed five trolls, according to Stranglar Bloodaks's orders. The "
"goal was to assess the strength of these trolls before planning the next "
"move against them. Not that strong."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2132"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered Stranglar Bloodaks's report letter to Krushar Breakskull of "
"the Iron Orks. It is a detailed report with all the information gathered "
"about the intruding troll of {$u12}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2133"
msgstr ""
"The Troll Lords are definitely the strongest of the trolls, but I did what "
"was asked of me and managed to loot one of their weapons, a Ravager. I "
"delivered the Ravager to Stranglar Bloodaks."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2139"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Ugruk Elfstabber, after Bossork the Councillor "
"informed me of a serious problem. Bandit orks have been attacking the trade "
"routes. I am to assist Ugruk Elfstabber in eliminating these traitors of the "
"great ork empire."

msgid "diary_text_quest_214"
msgstr ""
"With the construction of the Small Stair in Chopping Necks, and the "
"sacrifices soon to begin, large quantities of firewood will be needed for "
"the sacrificial pyres. I have gathered and delivered five units of timber to "
"Bigthug the Blacksmith."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2140"
msgstr ""
"I have killed six of the lower ranking bandit orks that were hiding in the "
"abandoned military outpost in {$u14}. Three Ork Thugs and tree Ork Bruisers. "
"Their bandit raiding days will soon be over."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2141"
msgstr ""
"The hivekin are doing a excellent job in {$u14}of stripping the lands of all "
"vegetation. I can see why Ugruk Elfstabber considers the hivekin the plague "
"of the lands. I have successfully killed five Hivekin Foragers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2142"
msgstr ""
"A massive blow has been delivered to the bandit ork leaders in {$u14}. After "
"storming their headquarters, I managed to kill two Ork Thug and two Ork  "
"Beastmasters. Death is the only thing that awaits those thaty betray the ork "
"empire."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2143"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered Ugruk Elfstabber's report letter to Bigclubs Trollmangler "
"of the Defenders of the Swamp. It is a full report about the traitorous "
"bandit orks of {$u14}, and how their operations came to an end."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2149"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Amhard Blackfists. Apparently trolls have "
"appeared after many year in the {$w14} region, and a new troll slaughter is "
"about to begin."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2150"
msgstr ""
"I have taken part in the new troll slaughter, and killed five trolls. One "
"can only imagine what it must have been like many years ago in the first "
"troll slaughter."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2151"
msgstr ""
"The kobold tribe of {$w14} has been punished for the death of the two agents "
"from Flaming Skull. It seems they had forgotten how it is that allows them "
"to lives in Morak. Six of the kobolds have been killed as a lesson."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2152"
msgstr ""
"What is a troll slaughter, if there isn't a little Timeless Blood harvesting "
"involved? After I have enough of killing trolls, I extracted three units of "
"Timeless Blood. According to Amhard Blackfists, it is something like a "
"trophy."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2153"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Bigork Blacktongue at the Dragonbound headquarters. "
"Amhard Blackfists informed my that the Dragonbound have got their hands full "
"with the local bandits, and could use the extra help."

msgid "diary_text_quest_216"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered five units of mandrake to Bloodzkul the Mage as requested. "
"Mandrake is a reagent for casting spells, and will be used by the "
"spellcasters in Chopping Necks,  in the fight against the humans of Mercia."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2163"
msgstr ""
"Aidan the Councillor has requested from all, to assist Heart of Eanna repel "
"the goblin hordes that have been attacking the trading routes. The goblins "
"are many, and I am not sure that killing four goblins will be enough."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2164"
msgstr ""
"I have retrieved two goblin axes from the slain goblins that have been "
"attacking Heart of Eanna. According to Aidan the Councillor, by looting the "
"axes from the fallen goblins before the other goblins can retrieve them, we "
"are in fact disarming the goblin army. Time will show."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2165"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered the amount of stone Jeremiah requested, stone that would be "
"used for the construction of Heart of Eanna's new guard houses. We need to "
"do all we can to safeguard the trade routes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2166"
msgstr ""
"Jeremiah the Blacksmith had requested that enough timber be gathered, for "
"the construction of the guard towers. After the goblin attacks, it is "
"obvious that Heart of Eanna's defenses along the trade routes will improve "
"with the addition of the guard towers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2167"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered five units of mandrake to Caradwen the Mage as requested. "
"Mandrake is to be used by the spellcasters against the goblin hordes. I hope "
"it was worth it, because my back still hurts from all the scrounging about "
"in the undergrowth."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2168"
msgstr ""
"I have completed the bloody task of gathering four teeth from the slain "
"goblins. Aidan the Councillor informed me that teeth are one of the many "
"materials that can by used in the art of imbuing items with magical "
"properties."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2169"
msgstr ""
"Swords and bows may be good against the goblins, but magic also has its "
"benefits. I was given the opportunity by Aidan the Councillor to cast twenty "
"mana missile against the goblins that were attacking Heart of Eanna. It "
"would seem that the goblins, like many of the monsters of Agon, have an "
"innate fear of magic and this is something that we must take full advantage "
"of."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2177"
msgstr ""
"I successfully killed three windlords, and passed the test given to me by "
"the Voice of Ymir. However, according to Garin Silvervault, there is one "
"more test I must face, to fully prove my worth to the Voice of Ymir."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2178"
msgstr ""
"I have proven my worth to Garin Silvervault and the Voice of Ymir, after "
"entering the dragon's cave and killing two Windgraives. I believe I have "
"gained their trust."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2179"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Thargal Thorsland. A group of pirates have "
"been attacking the trade ships along Dvergheim's northern coast."

msgid "diary_text_quest_218"
msgstr ""
"I have completed the bloody task of extracting four teeth from the slain "
"goblins. It seems that teeth are one of the many materials that can by used "
"in the art of imbuing items with magical properties."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2180"
msgstr ""
"Six Svartdvergir have been freed from the influence of Sahul. Death was "
"their only salvation. Sadly all the inhabitants of the mining community in "
"Skogul, have fallen under the influence of Sahul. They all need to the set "
"free."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2181"
msgstr ""
"I have removed three units of  Staunt Heart from the bodies of the tainted "
"svartdvergir, as instructed by Thargal Thorsland. Thargal informed me that "
"the Staunch Heart will be destroyed in a ritual of cleansing."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2182"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the good news to Garin Silvervault of the Voice of Ymir, "
"that Leengate will be very soon open once more for trade."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2183"
msgstr ""
"I have discovered a strange mural that depicts a striding lion with a "
"monstrous head, inside the mysterious pyramid in {$n10}. This symbol might "
"offer clues to the nature and heritage or the pyramid. I shall have to "
"return to Wintercrown and report this finding to Garin Silvervault."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2184"
msgstr ""
"I have returned to Wintercrown and reported my find about the symbol "
"discovered within the strange pyramid in {$n10} to Garin Silvervault. "
"According to Garin, the symbol is the Lion Deformed, an ancient symbol of Ur-"
"Khamset, an immortal tyrant whose long-sleeping hordes recently rose from "
"the sands and laid waste to the continent of Rubaiyat."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2185"
msgstr ""
"It is obvious that the pyramid structure is the cause of the rotting of the "
"lands in {$n10}. I have killed six of the pyramid's guardians, Slaves of "
"Khamset, to allow the Voice of Ymir to thoroughly investigate the pyramid, "
"and to eventually learn what it is exactly we are dealing with."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2186"
msgstr ""
"Three Dull Sparkstones have been gathered from the Slaves of Khamset, and "
"delivered to Vestri the Blacksmith."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2187"
msgstr ""
"Four Ghouls have been removed from the Tomb of the First Knights, located "
"directly underneath Stonevault, the chief stronghold of the Order of the "
"Axe. Perhaps the Order's first knights, can now rest in peace."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2188"
msgstr ""
"Four of the Undead Dwarves of Veilron Hall have been put to sleep, and have "
"finally rested. Unfortunately, there are many more of these lost souls that "
"need to be taken care of."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2189"
msgstr ""
"I have found Arduin Blackpeak's last blade in the ruins of Veilron Hall. All "
"that remains is to return to Stonevault, and deliver the sword to Thain "
"Strongforge."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2190"
msgstr ""
"Ardin Blackpeak's last blade has been delivered to Thain Strongforge. Now, "
"it is up to the blacksmiths of the Order of the Axe, to complete the "
"master's last work."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2191"
msgstr ""
"A crippling blow has been dealt to the Fire Standard hobgoblins. Five of the "
"Fire Standard hobgoblins died by my hand today. And if they continue their "
"raids against dwarven communities, many more will follow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2192"
msgstr ""
"I have killed four ogres as instructed by the Order of the Axe. A  military "
"expedition against the ogres is soon to begin, and the Order of the Axe has "
"been asked to weaken the ogres by killing as many as possible."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2193"
msgstr ""
"I have recovered the DeQuincey family signet ring, from was seems to be the "
"remains of the missing DeQuincey son. All that remains it to deliver it to "
"Thain Strongforge."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2194"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the DeQuincey signet ring to Thain Strongforge, so he may "
"return it to the DeQuincey family. Unfortunately, the same cannot be said "
"for the son of the DeQuincey family."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2196"
msgstr ""
"Six Troll Lords and two Swamp Hags have been removed from the Waneride "
"Mountains pass. It is vital to keep the pass through Waneride open, and to "
"not allow it to be controlled by raiders again."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2197"
msgstr ""
"I accepted to save eight of the dwarves of Silverbound, who have been "
"infected with Sahul's dark taint. Eight Svartdvergir found peace today. Only "
"death can remove Sahul's taint from a dwarf, once he has become infected."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2198"
msgstr ""
"Trade in Leengate, should slowly start to flow again. I have managed to kill "
"five of the undead pirates that have been attacking the merchant vessels. "
"The bonecrew pirates are many, but it is possible to eradicate them with a "
"proper organized attack."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2199"
msgstr ""
"Like many undead, bonecrew pirates have bones proven to be potent in "
"enchanting. I have gathered 10 units of Darktaint, as requested by Thargal "
"Thorsland."

msgid "diary_text_quest_220"
msgstr ""
"I was given the task by Uzrok the Councillor to cast twenty mana missile "
"against the escapee slave goblins. The goblins have an innate fear of magic, "
"and this is something that we must take full advantage of."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2200"
msgstr ""
"The arctic bears were doomed to a slow death, with no way of returning "
"north. I accepted to put three of the arctic bears out of their misery, as "
"instructed by Garn Runeshield of the Five Beards Trading Company."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2201"
msgstr ""
"Four svartdvergir have been removed from the mining village of Blacktrove. "
"The Five Beards Trading Company plan to eradicated the svartdvergir "
"completely, before replacing the current inhabitants of Blacktrove with "
"settlers who are wiling to resume production."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2202"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully located and destroyed one Basalt Golem in the village of "
"Blacktrove, before it can do any more damage to the local smithies and "
"mining operations."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2203"
msgstr ""
"After destroying their lifeless bodies, four of the undead dwarves that have "
"been haunting the abandoned dwarven mine of Nordakyst, have been set free."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2204"
msgstr ""
"I have helped clear out Icespear Ridge by killing three Frostwalkers and one "
"Windgraive. Icespear Ridge is an important site to many dwarves, since upon "
"its tallest peak stands a shrine which commemorates the second lesson of "
"Ymir the Mastersmith."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2205"
msgstr ""
"Many of the Five Beards Trading Company's operations, do not find support "
"among the local inhabitants of the surrounding lands, as with the logging "
"operations in the Whitebough forest. Unfortunately, three Ciel Fey and five "
"Centaurs had to die, so the Five Beards may continue to provide Dvergheim "
"with the much needed timber."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2206"
msgstr ""
"Three Timeless Blood have been extracted form the centaurs of Whitebough "
"forest, as requested by  Gardar Stonevalley. The centaurs have declared war "
"on the Five Beards logging operation in the forest of Whitebough, a war they "
"cannot win."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2207"
msgstr ""
"The path through Waneride Edge must be kept open at all costs. I have "
"removed five of the Oathbound that have been ambushing merchants along the "
"path. These trading routes are vital to the Five Beards Trading Company."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2208"
msgstr ""
"I located inside the Nithron ruins near Waneride Edge, a book which matches "
"the description of the Occluded Mirror. All that remains is to deliver the "
"book to Gardar Stonevalley."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2209"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the Occluded Mirror to Gardar Stonevalley. He seems sure of "
"its authenticity, and informed me that he will hand it over to the Five "
"Beards so they may study it, since it is written in Nithron."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2210"
msgstr ""
"Gardar Stonevalley instructed me to report to Garn Runeshield at the "
"headquarters of the Five Beards Trading Company. Arriving in Gemstone Reach, "
"I found a large reward waiting for me, for all the work I have done with the "
"Five Beads."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2211"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Vestri the Blacksmith of the Voice of Ymir. "
"Apparently my success in dealing with the undead guardians of the pyramid "
"has somewhat impressed him."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2212"
msgstr ""
"I have reported to Garin Silvervault, only to receive a healthy reward as a "
"token of appreciation from the Voice of Ymir, for helping them with many of "
"the issues they are dealing with."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2213"
msgstr ""
"I have extracted two units of Staunch Hearts from the bodies of the slain "
"Svartdvergir, and delivered them to Garn Runeshield in Gemstone Reach. "
"Drinking Staunch Hearts, is how the dwarves are transformed into "
"Svartdvergir."

msgid "diary_text_quest_222"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully killed four goblins as requested by Bosork the "
"Councillor. Apparently goblin groups wandering nearby Metal Heart, have been "
"staging raids against local farms and villages."

msgid "diary_text_quest_224"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered two goblin axes from the slain goblins. These axes will by "
"used as tools by the goblin slaves in Metal Heart."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2247"
msgstr ""
"I killed two Lesser Fire Elementals as instructed by Krushar Breakskull, and "
"completed the first part of the Iron Orks test."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2248"
msgstr ""
"After killing two raptors, and therefor completing the second part of the "
"Iron Orks's test, I should next be given my first real assignment by the "
"Iron Orks."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2249"
msgstr ""
"I have completed my first assignment wit the Iron Orks. Four Doom Spiders "
"and two Sarlids have been removed from the mining town of Stone Wall in "
"{$u11}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2250"
msgstr ""
"Pain have been brought to those the destroyers of the mining town of Stone "
"Wall. I extracted two Baleful Venom Sac from the Spiders and two units of "
"Caustic Bile from the Sarlid, as instructed by Krushar Breakskull."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2251"
msgstr ""
"I have found a book that matches the description of the Endemoniad, the "
"legendary Nithron book which described much of the ancient world, as seen by "
"the Nithron. All that remains is to deliver the book to Krushar Breakskull "
"in Iron Maiden."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2252"
msgstr ""
"Krushar Breakskull was extremely pleased to see the copy of the Endemoniad, "
"and especially since the book was in almost perfect condition. Now it is up "
"to the scholars of Nithron history to study it."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2253"
msgstr ""
"I have destroyed the Nithon guardians as instructed by the Iron Orks. Three "
"Snake Revenants and three Oathbound. Truly, is assemble in large numbers, "
"these guardian could pose a considerable threat to the stability of Morak"

msgid "diary_text_quest_2254"
msgstr ""
"I have found an ancient book titled the Tome of Legend in the sadavel "
"village of Silmah, that could possibly be the source of the sadayels new "
"found magical powers. I shall bring this book to Krushar Breakskull, to "
"verify the any magical properties this book might have."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2255"
msgstr ""
"Krushar Breakskull believes that the Tome of Legend I found in the sadayel "
"village of Silmah, could actually be the source of their new found magical "
"powers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2256"
msgstr ""
"The sadayel city of Silmah is doomed to fall in the near future. After the "
"six Sadayel Guardians, two Sadayel Shamans and two Sadayel Chieftains I "
"killed, once the orkish army pounds through their city, Silmah will be "
"destroyed once and for all."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2257"
msgstr ""
"How foolish were the Hill Giant Sluggers to march fearlessly towards Morak "
"and the Iron Orks. Four Hill Giant Sluggers died by my hand as instructed by "
"Krushar Breakskull, and if they continue their stupid march, many more will "
"die."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2258"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully killed seven hobgoblins. Apparently there is a growing "
"hobgoblin presence in {$t11}, almost the size of a small army. Who is "
"assembling this army, is yet to be discovered."

msgid "diary_text_quest_226"
msgstr ""
"Strongar the Blacksmith has instructed everybody to gather basic building "
"material for the construction of the Small Stair in Metal Heart. I have "
"gathered five units of stone as requested by Strongar the Blacksmith."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2269"
msgstr ""
"Four Swamp Hags have been removed from the tar lake near Swampton, the chief "
"stronghold of the Defenders of the Swamp. Swamp Hags are truly revolting "
"creatures."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2270"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Sir Bonehard the Cruel, a knight of the "
"Defenders of the Swamp, who is based in Elfkill Keep in {$t15}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2271"
msgstr ""
"Five half-horse freaks have been removed from {$t15} forest. If the "
"Defenders of the Swamp are to claim the forests, first the centaurs who seem "
"to be the protectors of the sylvan creatures of the forest must fall."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2272"
msgstr ""
"I have found the Sacred Bough, the powerful elven artifact that is rumored "
"to be the power of the ciel fey village's surprising defensive strength. All "
"that remains is to deliver it to Sir Bonehard the Cruel in Elfkill Keep."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2273"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the Sacred Bough to Sir Bonehard the Cruel. Although "
"nothing more than an insignificant-looking twig, it is rumored to be a "
"powerful ancient elven artifact, to hold great magical power. No longer in "
"the possession of the ciel fey, {$t15} forest should now be easily claimed."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2274"
msgstr ""
"{$t15} forest should be cleared of the annoying ciel fey very soon. Six have "
"died by my hand today, and more are to follow. I have delivered the news to "
"Sir Bonehard the Cruel."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2275"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Hardzkul Warmaster in {$v15}, to receive more "
"assignments from the Defenders of the Swamp."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2276"
msgstr ""
"Three Sadayel Guardians and three Sadayel Shamans have been killed and "
"removed from the entrance of the House of Memory, an ancient site built be a "
"race of humans known as the Thaelicians."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2277"
msgstr ""
"The path from the waterfall to the Shrine of Memory should now be relatively "
"clear, after disposing of those four Sadayel Chieftains."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2278"
msgstr ""
"The Shrine of Memory has been destroyed, as instructed by the Defenders of "
"the Swamp. It was  Big Head Uzrok Deathfist's wish to remove the last "
"remnant of the ancient Thaelicians."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2279"
msgstr ""
"Five Hill Giants have been removed from the region of {$v16}, therefor "
"making way for the ork army to move against the human mining city of {$v17}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_228"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered and delivered five units of timber to Strongar the "
"Blacksmith in Metal Heart. This timber will be used as firewood for the "
"sacrificial pyres."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2280"
msgstr ""
"I have defiled the human statue in Trinwood as instructed by Bigclubs "
"Trollmangler, by carving an unspeakable insult into its side. Nothing sacred "
"to the humans is safe from the Defenders of the Swamp."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2292"
msgstr ""
"The raiding days of the ork bandits are at their end. I have located and "
"killed several ork bandits, as instructed by Bigork Blacktongue of the "
"Dragonbound."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2293"
msgstr ""
"I have located the Banegrail, as instructed by Bigork Blacktongue, hidden "
"inside a chest in the city of the undead dwarves of  Selengard."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2294"
msgstr ""
"The Banegrail has been delivered to Bigork Blacktongue of the Dragonbound. "
"It will become one more of the many artifacts, piled up in the Fire Dragon's "
"treasure."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2295"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Slayor Strongork in Itak Laurgul. I am to "
"assist the Dragonbound agent's search of the ruins in {$x11} for lost "
"treasures."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2296"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully destroyed seven of the Nithron guardians in {$x11}, four "
"Hawk Revenants and three Leopard Revenants. The Dragonbound may now continue "
"their excavations of the ruins, for the artifacts which the Fire Dragon "
"craves."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2297"
msgstr ""
"I have located the Amber Harp, the artifact that the Fire Dragon craves the "
"most, within the sunken Nithron ruins of {$x11}.  All that remains is to "
"deliver the harp to Bigork Blacktongue in Emberhall."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2298"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the Amber Harp to Bigork Blacktongue, after locating it in "
"Nithron ruins of {$x11}. Another artifact to be added to the Fire Dragon's "
"treasure."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2299"
msgstr ""
"The sadayel shrine and egg in {$v11}, have been destroyed. The sadayel "
"shamans have prophesied that the legendary sadayel warlord Antares will be "
"reborn from one of these eggs. By destroying these eggs, the morale of the "
"sadayel will diminish, together with and any hopes of the rebirth of the "
"sadayel warlord Antares."

msgid "diary_text_quest_230"
msgstr ""
"It amazes me how a simple herb such a mandrake, is used to cast spells. "
"After gathering and delivering the five mandrake herbs to Manglar the Mage, "
"stretching my back a little will help to recover from all that scrounging "
"about in the undergrowth."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2300"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Stranglar Bloodaks in the village of Bad Dog "
"in {$u12}. I am to assist the Dragonbound agent's search for book called the "
"Fecund Leaf, somewhere in the {$u12} region."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2301"
msgstr ""
"I have located the book called the Fecund Leaf. Despite its relatively poor "
"condition, large sections of the book appear to be legible. All that remains "
"is to deliver the book to Stranglar Bloodaks."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2302"
msgstr ""
"Although the poor conditions the book was in, Stranglar Bloodaks was pleased "
"to see that I was successful in locating the Fecund Leaf. One more book, for "
"the libraries of the Dragonbound in Emberhall."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2303"
msgstr ""
"I have found the Orb of Decay, an orb that is wet to the touch with a deep "
"emerald color, as described in the pages of the Fecund Leaf. To complete my "
"mission, I must bring this orb to Bigork Blacktongue in Emberhall."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2304"
msgstr ""
"I have handed the Orb of Decay to Bigork Blacktongue in Emberhall, after "
"locating it in the swampland of {$u12}. One more powerful artifact to be "
"added to the Fire Dragon's hoard."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2305"
msgstr ""
"I have found the artifact known as the Mark of Morneid. All that remains is "
"to bring it to Bigork Blacktongue in Emberhall."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2306"
msgstr ""
"The necklace that was found in the possession of the Kobold Strongman camps "
"of Laurgul, is indeed the Mark of Morneid. According to Bigork Blacktongue, "
"it is one of the many demonic artifacts given by the demon Morneid for his "
"officers, before departing Agon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2317"
msgstr ""
"The Gullhorn centaurs will think twice before listening to the Dark Arannog "
"druids again, attacking and raiding Mercian communities. Four centaurs have "
"died by my hand, as instructed by Jeremiah Grace of the Knights of Malregard."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2318"
msgstr ""
"I've assisted the Knights of Malregard in putting an end to the Wychwater "
"rebellion. Five Human Renegades are dead, and hopefully the rest will have "
"learned there lesson."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2319"
msgstr ""
"The Dark Arannog druids will not have their way. The waters of the Wychwode "
"spring should soon be clear again, now that the trolls are being removed "
"from the spring. I have successfully removed four trolls."

msgid "diary_text_quest_232"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered four teeth as requested by Bosork the Councillor. These "
"simple teeth will be used to craft magical items. Incredible."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2320"
msgstr ""
"The Dark Arannog druids will be crushed, and so will the rebellion. After "
"destroying the Air Elementals upon the floating island in {$t21}, "
"Cloudhenge's energy should diminish, and together with that so should the "
"power of the Dark Arannog druids."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2321"
msgstr ""
"I have assisted the Knights of Malregard in locating and killing the dark "
"creature known as the Greater Below, within the cave system of {$s21}. Know "
"we must free the people from the Malaut's shadow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2322"
msgstr ""
"Five Malaut Acolytes and two Human Highwaymen, all who had fallen into the "
"shadow of the Twilight Kingdom, have been saved. Death was their only "
"salvation."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2323"
msgstr ""
"I have become the instrument of cleansing for the Knights of Malregard. I "
"traveled to Snowthorpe and killed three Malaut Beguilers and three Human "
"Highwaymen. The light of Auros will shine again on the village of "
"Snowthorpe. Malaut will not win."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2324"
msgstr ""
"A powerful blow has been dealt to Malaut and his worshipers. I successfully "
"killed four Below and three Malaut Beguilers, and exposed their base within "
"the hidden valley in {$s20}. All that remains is for the Knights of "
"Malregard to shine the light of Auros upon them, and to destroy them once "
"and for all."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2333"
msgstr ""
"Five skeletons and five zombies have been destroyed, in order to help the "
"White Order contain the undead outbreak in {$u18}, as requested by Maria "
"Hawksgate."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2334"
msgstr ""
"I have stopped the shadow-tree from tainting the sacred river, by casting a "
"mana drain spell on it, as instructed by Maria Hawksgate. Let us hope that "
"this will stop the dead from rising."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2335"
msgstr ""
"Four of the dire zombies that are responsible for the appearance of the "
"shadow-tree which tainted the sacred river in {$u18}, have been destroyed."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2336"
msgstr ""
"The White Order plans to gain control of {$v16}, once the Hill Giant "
"Sluggers that have been placed there by the orks, have all been removed. I "
"have killed four of the Hill Giant Sluggers that guard the shattered region "
"of {$v16}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2337"
msgstr ""
"Whatever plans the hobgoblin in {$w18} had, are soon to be over. I returned "
"from their camp with a full report of their strengths and weaknesses, after "
"successfully killed four of them. Soon the White Order will launch a "
"campaign against them."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2338"
msgstr ""
"I have assisted the White Order in their efforts to drive the evil melechar "
"out of mercia, and specifically the region of Thelassa. Five of the Melechar "
"that have settle in Thelassa, have died by my hand."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2339"
msgstr ""
"In order to rid the region of Thelassa of the Melechar, first the Flesh "
"Golems that guard the narrow stone bridge which joins the Thelaessa to the "
"rest of the world must be destroyed. I have managed to destroy two of the "
"Flesh Golems in Thelaessa."

msgid "diary_text_quest_234"
msgstr ""
"The goblins fear of the ork has definitely grown after the barrage of mana "
"missiles cast against them. Since the goblins fear magic, we must use every "
"trick available to us in our attempt to expel the them from Metal Heart."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2340"
msgstr ""
"Four of the giant skeletons in {$u17} have been put to rest, and more are "
"soon to follow. The giants that were slaughtered by Skuld Snowfeather, shall "
"not continue to haunt the old battlefield in {$u17} much longer."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2349"
msgstr ""
"Three Sarlids and five of their pet Spiders have been removed from the "
"forests of {$u21}. The strange and sinister Sarlid must be removed as soon "
"as possible from {$u21}, before their beloved pet spiders cause serious "
"damage to the local communities."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2350"
msgstr ""
"The Diadem of Dawn, the legendary ancient crown that belonged to the nithron "
"queen Iyarthessa, has been found. All that remains is for me to deliver the "
"crown to Iain Deepwode in {$u21}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2351"
msgstr ""
"The Diadem of Dawn has been delivered to Iain Deepwode of the Sons of Riada, "
"and seems very pleased that I found it."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2352"
msgstr ""
"Four of the Undead Dwarves that have risen in Theyril Hall, have been put "
"back to sleep. Now, Sons of Riada's archaeologists should be able to "
"continue their excavation work within Theyril Hall."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2353"
msgstr ""
"I have traveled to {$w19}, to meet Eva Rainbird. Apparently Eva has a book "
"called the Wainfold Tapestry, which will help the Sons of Riada to determine "
"if the nithron crown that was found in {$u22}, is the legendary Diadem of "
"Dawn."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2354"
msgstr ""
"In order obtain the Wainfold Tapestry from Eva Rainbird, Eva requested that "
"I help her remove the salamanders that migrated into {$w19}. I managed to "
"kill six of the salamanders."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2355"
msgstr ""
"After killing six lizardmen in {$w19}, the herbalists of {$w19} should be "
"able to return to their work."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2356"
msgstr ""
"Eva Rainbord handed me the Wainfold Tapestry, after helping her deal with a "
"few minor problems in {$w19}. The Wainfold Tapestry has been delivered to "
"Iain Deepwode of the Sons of Riada."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2357"
msgstr ""
"I have located the Dragontorc, an ancient nithron artifact, hidden well "
"among the {$t22} ruins. Iain Deepwode of the Sons of Riada should be pleased "
"once I deliver it to him."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2358"
msgstr ""
"The Dragontorc has been delivered to Iain Deepwode of the Sons of Riada, and "
"I have received my reward. The Sons of Riada are already researching the "
"artifact for its magical abilities."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2359"
msgstr ""
"The enchantment ingredients that Iain Deepwode requested, have been "
"collected and delivered. Ingredients to be used to manufacture magical "
"equipment, enough to wage a successful military campaign against the undead "
"hordes of the Red Pharaoh in Rubaiyat."

msgid "diary_text_quest_236"
msgstr ""
"Vilethug the Councillor was pleased to hear that I had successfully killed "
"four of the escapee goblins from New Flayed Elf. The goblins had to be "
"hunted down and killed, before they could become an inspiration to other "
"slaves."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2369"
msgstr ""
"The goblin hordes might have been pushed away from Sanguine, but that is not "
"the end of them. A campaign into {$t18} is soon to begin against the goblin "
"strongholds. I have reported for duty with Arduin Strayshadow who is "
"coordinating the Mercian government's efforts in {$t18}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2370"
msgstr ""
"{$t18} is definitely the most goblin infested region within Mercia. My first "
"mission for White Order's campaign against the local goblins has been "
"successful. I have killed four Goblin Fighters and four Goblin Scouts."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2371"
msgstr ""
"It is hard to believe that some goblins have enough intelligence to become "
"spellcasters known as shamans. In numbers, the goblin shamans can truly "
"become a serious problem to Mercia. I have successfully killed three goblin "
"shamans and two goblin marauders, as part of the White Order's campaign "
"against the goblin tribes in {$t18}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2372"
msgstr ""
"A serious blow has been delivered to the goblin warlord leader Archduke "
"Stabby XII. Although  Archduke Stabby XII himself has not been located yet, "
"the White Order has orders us to locate and kill Archduke Stabby's strongest "
"units, the goblin warlords and marauders. I have successfully killed one "
"goblin warlord and two goblin marauders in {$t18}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2373"
msgstr ""
"The White Order's campaign against the goblin tribes of {$t18} continues, "
"and is bound to end in successes. Arduin Strayshadow conducted a detailed "
"report letter of the campaign, and instructed me to deliver it to Maria "
"Hawkgate of the White Order."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2379"
msgstr ""
"The hivekin are doing a excellent job stripping the lands of all vegetation. "
"I can see why Sir Jeremiah Grace of the Knights of Malregard has requested "
"that the hivekin be moved immediately. I have completed the task of killing "
"six Hivekin Foragers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_238"
msgstr ""
"I have recovered two of the axes, that were stolen by the escapee goblin "
"from New Flayed Elf. No one steals from the orks."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2380"
msgstr ""
"It is good to know that the hivekin are useful for one thing. Their claws "
"can be used for crafting magical items. I have completed the task of "
"extracting five hivekin claws, just as William the Councillor instructed me."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2381"
msgstr ""
"The hivekin queen, that useless bag of flesh, along with four of her "
"broodguards are dead.  According to William the Councillor, the only way to "
"by sure we can rid the lands of the hivekin plague is to kill the hivekin "
"queen."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2382"
msgstr ""
"I have located the Noonday Moon. All that remains is to bring it to Sir "
"Jeremiah Grace."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2383"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully recovered the Noonday Moon, a lapis lazuli gemstone that "
"is sacred to the Mirdain, and delivered it to Sir Jeremiah Grace of the "
"Knights of Malregard."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2388"
msgstr ""
"I have agreed to participate in the campaign against the Unseen Hand and the "
"rebel bandits of {$v20}. I have already reported for duty with Maren "
"Winterspar who is organizing the campaign."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2389"
msgstr ""
"I have destroyed part of the Unseen Hand's undead army in {$v20} by "
"destroying four zombies and four skeletons."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2390"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully killed three Human Brawlers and three Human Outlaws, all "
"members of the Unseen Hand. The King's message has been delivered to the "
"bandits in {$v20}, and {$v20} shall return to Mercia. The Unseen Hand and "
"its members have no place in Mercia!"

msgid "diary_text_quest_2391"
msgstr ""
"My skinning knife was put to good use by harvesting three units of skeleton "
"bone and one unit of corpseflesh, from the Unseen Hand's undead army."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2392"
msgstr ""
"I gathered and delivered an Baleful Venom Sac to Iain Deepwode in "
"Hildershall, only to find out that is was part of a bet that Maren "
"Winterspar had lost to Iain Deepwode."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2398"
msgstr ""
"I have completed the task for removing three units of Bile from the bodies "
"of the dead gnolls. Isenda the Clever suggested that I put the gnolls to "
"good use by harvesting from their bodies feral lifeforce, a material that "
"can be used by the Circle of Neith for crafting magical items."

msgid "diary_text_quest_240"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered five units of stone for the construction of the new "
"breakwater, which will help protect New Flayed Elf against the savage winter "
"storms."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2400"
msgstr ""
"Two units of Bile has been harvested for the gnolls, just to reminded of "
"what is means to interfere with the Longclaw. Setting up a camp in {$j10}, "
"was not a smart decision. I am sure that more pain will be inflicted upon "
"the gnolls in the near future."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2402"
msgstr ""
"The recent goblin attacks have made it quite obvious that Sanguine needs to "
"improve its defenses. I have reported for duty with Talaod the Blacksmith, "
"to assist with the improvement of the town walls."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2404"
msgstr ""
"All the building materials needed for the strengthening of the Sanguine's "
"walls have been gathered, and work is soon to begin. Talaod the Blacksmith "
"instructed me to deliver the news to Allan the Councillor, which of course I "
"did."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2406"
msgstr ""
"To kill seven goblins in less that an hour, is what Allan the Councillor "
"requested from all in Monkfield. The goblin numbers have increased, and are "
"dangerously approaching Monkfield. I hope this counter attack has "
"significantly weakened the goblin hordes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2408"
msgstr ""
"It has been decided that the spellcasters of Sanguine are to join the battle "
"against the goblin hordes. I have reported for duty with Jonn the Mage to "
"assist with preparing the spellcasters, by gathering specific materials that "
"will be used to power their spells."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2410"
msgstr ""
"More materials for spells. I have gathered five units of sulfur for Jonn the "
"Mage. Sulfur is also another of the reagents used in the art of "
"spellcasting. Now it is up to Sanguine's spellcasters to put the sulfur to "
"good use against the goblins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2412"
msgstr ""
"Resin can become quite a powerful item in the hands of an experienced "
"spellcaster. It is one of the reagents used in the art of spellcasting. I "
"have gathered five units of resin for Jonn the Mage as requested."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2414"
msgstr ""
"Sanguine's spellasters will soon be ready to join the battle against the "
"goblin hordes. I have delivered the news to Allan the Councillor, after "
"having completed collecting all the ingredients Jonn the Mage requested for "
"the spellcasters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2416"
msgstr ""
"The goblin attacks have made it obvious that Sandbrook needs to strengthen "
"its defenses. I have reported for duty with Anton the Blacksmith, to assist "
"him with the strengthening of the town's walls."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2418"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the good news to William the Councillor, that all the "
"building materials needed for repairing and strengthening Sandbrook's towns "
"walls have been gathered. Work should begin very soon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_242"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered five units of timber for the construction of a new ship, as "
"requested by the merchants of New Flayed Elf."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2420"
msgstr ""
"I have returned to Sandbrook after killing seven more goblins in less than "
"an hour, as instructed by William the Councillor. The goblins are growing "
"more arrogant and more violent every day, to the point that they seem not to "
"fear us anymore. Something is not right."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2422"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Carrad the Mage, to assist collect the "
"materials Sandbook's spellcasters need, to support the battle against the "
"goblin hordes. I shall do the best I can."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2424"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered the five units of sulfur that Carrad the Mage requested. If "
"sulfur is what Sandbrook's spellcasters need in the fight against the goblin "
"hordes, then sulfur I shall collect."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2426"
msgstr ""
"Who would have thought that resin could be so important. I have just handed "
"to Carrad the Mage five units of resin. Resin is one of the reagents that "
"spellcasters use for casting spells."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2428"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered Carrad's message to William the Councillor, that "
"Sandbrook's spellcasters will soon be ready to do battle against the goblin "
"hordes. I am very interested to see what kind of support our spellcasters "
"can provide."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2430"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty at Jeremiah the Blacksmith, to assist with the "
"construction of the new guard towers and guard houses. The latest goblin "
"attacks have forced Heart of Eanna to strengthen its defenses."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2432"
msgstr ""
"The construction of Heat of Eanna's new guard towers and guard houses is to "
"begin very soon. I have delivered the good news to Aidan the Councillor, as "
"Jeremiah the Blacksmith asked of me to do."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2434"
msgstr ""
"I have returned from the battlefield, after successfully killing seven "
"goblins in less than an hour as requested by Aidan the Councillor. It would "
"seem that our previous efforts to repel the goblins were not enough, and the "
"goblins had return to Heart of Eanna in greater numbers. These goblins are "
"proving to be resilient and many. The fight go on."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2436"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Caradwen the Mage, to assist with preparing "
"Heart of Eanna's spellcasters. All help is needed, especially that of the "
"spellcasters, if Heart of Eanna is to succeed in eradicating the goblin "
"menace."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2438"
msgstr ""
"I have completed gathering the five units of sulfur that Caradwen the Mage "
"requested. Now all that remains is for Heart of Eanna's spellcasters to use "
"the sulfur for their spells, and put an end to the goblin threat."

msgid "diary_text_quest_244"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered the five mandrake herbs that Skullgor the Mage requested. "
"Mandrake is one of the reagents used by spellcasters for casting spells."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2440"
msgstr ""
"According the Caradwen the Mage, resin is one of the reagents the "
"spellcasters need to cast many of their spells. I hope those five units of "
"resin that I gathered, will be put to good use by the spellcasters in the "
"battle against the goblin hordes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2442"
msgstr ""
"Caradwen the Mage is pleased with the amount of magical ingredients that has "
"been collected, and very soon Heart of Eanna's spellcasters will be ready to "
"take part in the battle against the goblin hordes. I have delivered the news "
"to Aidan the Councillor."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2444"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Bigthug the Blacksmith to assist with the "
"construction of the Small Stair in Chopping Necks. The Small Stair is an "
"altar were dozens of sacrifices will be made every day to please the Fire "
"Dragon's hunger for death."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2446"
msgstr ""
"Construction on Chopping Neck's sacrificial alter, the Small Stair, will "
"soon begin. I have delivered the good news to Uzrok the Councillor as "
"Bigthug the Blacksmith requested. The Fire Dragon will surely be pleased."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2448"
msgstr ""
"I have completed the task of killing seven goblins in under an hour. "
"Chopping Necks is stocking up on goblins, ready for the sacrificial pyres "
"when they start to burn."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2450"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Bloodzkul the Mage, to assist with preparing "
"Chopping Necks spellcasters. A military campaign against the Humans of "
"Mercia is been planned, and everybody must do their part."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2452"
msgstr ""
"I have completed gathering five units of sulfur, as requested by Bloodzkul "
"the Mage. All that remains is for the spellcasters of Chopping Necks to put "
"the sulfur to good use, and destroy the humans of Mercia once and for all."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2454"
msgstr ""
"According the Bloodzkul the Mage, resin is one of the reagents our "
"spellcasters need to cast many of their spells. I have gathered and "
"delivered five units of resin to Bloodzkul."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2456"
msgstr ""
"Bloodzkul the Mage is pleased with the amount of magical ingredients that "
"has been collected in Chopping Necks, and very soon our spellcasters will be "
"ready to take part in the campaign against the humans of Mercia. I have "
"delivered the news to Urzok the Councillor."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2458"
msgstr ""
"Metal Heart is planning to build a sacrificial altar, to add to the number "
"sacrifices made to please the Fire Dragon. I have reported for duty with "
"Strongar the Blacksmith to assist with the construction of the Small Stair."

msgid "diary_text_quest_246"
msgstr ""
"I have extracted four teeth from the slain goblins, as instructed by "
"Vilethug the Councillor. Who would have known that simple teeth can be used "
"for crafting items imbued with magical properties."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2460"
msgstr ""
"Construction on Metal Heart's sacrificial alter will soon begin. I have "
"delivered the good news to Bosork the Councillor as Strongar the Blacksmith "
"requested."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2462"
msgstr ""
"Today was a good day, and many goblins died by my hand. Metal Heart is "
"stocking up on goblins, ready to be thrown into the sacrificial pyres."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2464"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Manglar the Mage, to assist with preparing "
"Metal Heart's spellcasters. A military campaign against the Humans of Mercia "
"is been planned, and all help is needed."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2466"
msgstr ""
"More materials for spells. I have gathered five units of sulfur for Manglar "
"the Mage. Sulfur is another of the reagents used in the art of spellcasting. "
"Now it is up to the spellcasters to put the sulfur to good use against the "
"humans."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2468"
msgstr ""
"Resin is a powerful item in the hands of an experienced spellcaster. It is "
"one of the reagents used in the art of spellcasting. I have gathered and "
"delivered five units of resin to Manglar the Mage as requested."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2470"
msgstr ""
"The spellcasters will soon be able to support Metal Heart in the campaign "
"against the humans. I have delivered the news to Bosork the Councillor, "
"after having completed collecting all the ingredients Manglar the Mage "
"requested for the spellcasters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2472"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Wolfork the Blacksmith. After the goblin "
"mutiny, it seems everybody in New Flayed Elf is eager to begin repairing."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2474"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Vilethug the Councillor as instructed by "
"Wolfork the Blacksmith. It seems that New Flayed Elf has trouble with the "
"goblins once again."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2476"
msgstr ""
"I have returned to New Flayed Elf, after killing seven goblins in less than "
"an hour as instructed by Vilethug the Councillor. The escapee goblins are "
"growing more arrogant and violent, and have begun attacking caravans along "
"our trade routes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2478"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Skullgor the Mage, to help collect magical "
"ingredients the spellcasters need to support New Flayed Elf in the upcoming "
"campaign against the Humans of Mercia."

msgid "diary_text_quest_248"
msgstr ""
"Goblins seem to have a great fear of magic. I have complete the strange task "
"of casting twenty mana missiles against the goblins that had escaped New "
"Flayed Elf. The goblins need to be reminded who is their master."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2480"
msgstr ""
"The spellcasters of New Flayed Elf have requested sulfur, which is one of "
"the reagents used to cast spells. I have gathered five units of sulfur."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2482"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered five units of resin to Skullgor the Mage. Resin is one of "
"the reagents used for casting spells. Who would have thought that resin "
"could be so special."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2484"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered Skullgor's message to Vilethug the Councillor, that the "
"spellcasters of New Flayed Elf will soon be ready to do battle against the "
"humans of Mercia. I am very interested to see the kind of support our "
"spellcasters can provide us with."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2486"
msgstr ""
"The goblin attacks have made it obvious that Eirhjelm needs to improve its "
"defenses. I have reported for duty with Ragneid the Blacksmith, to assist "
"with the construction of the new defenses."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2488"
msgstr ""
"All the building materials needed to strengthen Eirhjelm's defense walls "
"have been gathered, and  work is soon to begin. I delivered the good news to "
"Skuldvard the Councillor."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2490"
msgstr ""
"Seven goblins in less that an hour is what Skuldvard the Councillor "
"requested from all. The goblin numbers had increased, and are dangerously "
"approaching Eirhjelm."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2492"
msgstr ""
"It has been decided that Eirhjelm's spellcasters are to join the battle "
"against the goblin hordes. I have reported for duty with Steingrima the "
"Arcanist to assist with preparing the spellcasters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2494"
msgstr ""
"More materials for spells. I have gathered and delivered five units of "
"sulfur to Steingrima the Arcanist. Sulfur is also another of the reagents "
"used in the art of spellcasting. Now it is up to Eirhjelm's spellcasters to "
"put the sulfur to good use against the goblins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2496"
msgstr ""
"Resin can become a powerful item in the hands of an experienced spellcaster. "
"It is one of the reagents used in the art of spellcasting. I have gathered "
"and delivered five units of resin to Steingrima the Arcanist in Eirhjelm."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2498"
msgstr ""
"The spellasters will soon be able to support Eirhjelm in the fight against "
"the goblin hordes. I have delivered the news to Skuldvard the Councillor, "
"after having completed collecting all the ingredients Steingrima the "
"Arcanist requested for the spellcasters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2500"
msgstr ""
"The goblin attacks have made it obvious that Hammerdelve needs to strengthen "
"its defenses along the trade routes. I have reported for duty with Tordar "
"the Blacksmith, to assist with the construction of the new defenses."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2502"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the good news to Arngard the Councillor, that all the "
"building materials needed for construction of the guard houses and guard "
"towers along the trade routes have been gathered. Work on Hammerdelve's new "
"defenses should begin very soon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2504"
msgstr ""
"I returned to Hammerdelve after killing another seven goblins in less than "
"an hour, as instructed by Arngard the Councillor. The goblins are growing "
"more arrogant and violent every day, to the point that they seem not to fear "
"us anymore. Something must be done."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2506"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Gormfinn the Arcanist, to help collect the "
"materials the spellcasters need, materials to support Hammerdelve's fight "
"against the goblin hordes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2508"
msgstr ""
"I have gathering the five units of sulfur that Gormfinn the Arcanist "
"requested. If sulfur is what Hammerdelve's spellcasters need in the fight "
"against the goblin hordes, then sulfur I shall collect."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2510"
msgstr ""
"Who would have thought that resin could be so important. I gathered five "
"units of resin for Gormfinn the Arcanist in Hammerdelve. Resin is one of the "
"reagents that spellcasters use for casting spells."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2512"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered Gormfinn's message to Arngard the Councillor, that "
"Hammerdelve's spellcasters will soon be ready to battle the goblin hordes. I "
"am very interested to see what kind of support the spellcasters can provide."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2514"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Alvmund the Blacksmith to assist with the "
"strengthening of the town's walls, and the construction of the guard towers. "
"The latest goblin attacks have forced Valfather's Edge to strengthen its "
"defenses."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2518"
msgstr ""
"The construction of the guard towers and the repairs the defense walls in "
"Valfather's Edge, are soon to begin. I have delivered the good news to Aidan "
"the Councillor, as Alvmund the Blacksmith asked of me to do."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2520"
msgstr ""
"I have returned to Valfather's Edge after successfully killing seven goblins "
"in less than an hour as instructed by Hrafnid the Councillor. It would seem "
"that our previous efforts against the goblins were not enough, and the "
"goblins had return in greater numbers. These goblins are proving to be "
"resilient and many."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2522"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Yngfell the Arcanist, to assist with preparing "
"Valfather's Egde's spellcasters. All help is needed, especially that of the "
"spellcasters the goblin menace is to be completely eradicated."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2524"
msgstr ""
"I have completed gathering the five units of sulfur that Yngfell the "
"Arcanist requested. Now all that remains is for the spellcasters of "
"Valfather's Edge to use this sulfur for their spells, and put an end to the "
"goblin threat."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2526"
msgstr ""
"According the Yngfell the Arcanist, resin is one of the reagents the "
"spellcasters need to cast many of their spells. Let us hope that the five "
"units of resin that we all have collected will be put to good use by the "
"spellcasters in our battle against the goblin hordes in Valfather's Edge."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2528"
msgstr ""
"Yngfell the Arcanist is pleased with the amount of magical ingredients that "
"has been collected, and very soon the spellcasters of Valfather's Edge will "
"be ready to take part in the battle against the goblin hordes. I delivered "
"the good news to Hrafnid the Councillor."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2530"
msgstr ""
"The recent goblin attacks have made it quite obvious that Onghral needs to "
"improve its defenses. I have reported for duty with Nirgan the Blacksmith, "
"to assist with the improvement of the town walls, and the construction of "
"the guard towers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2532"
msgstr ""
"According to Nirgan the Blacksmith, all the building materials needed for "
"the strengthening of the town's walls and the construction of the guard "
"towers has been gathered. Construction of both has begun and I have "
"delivered the good news to Taelis the Councillor. Onghral will soon be well "
"fortified."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2534"
msgstr ""
"Seven goblins in less that an hour is exactly what the elders demanded from "
"all. The goblin numbers have increased and are dangerously approaching "
"Onghral. This organized counter attack of ours must surely have weakened the "
"goblin hordes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2536"
msgstr ""
"It has been decided that the spellcasters of Onghral should join the battle "
"against the goblin hordes. I have reported for duty with Kalshar the "
"Arcanist to assist with preparing the spellcasters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2538"
msgstr ""
"More materials for spells. I have gathered  five units of sulfur for Kalshar "
"the Arcanist. Sulfur is also another of the reagents used in the art of "
"spellcasting. It is now up to Onghral's spellcasters to put the sulfur to "
"good use against the goblins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2540"
msgstr ""
"Resin can become quite a powerful item in the hands of an experienced "
"spellcaster, according to Kalshar. It is one of the reagents used in the art "
"of spellcasting. I have gathered and delivered five units of resin to "
"Kalshar the Arcanist as instructed."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2542"
msgstr ""
"Onghral's spellasters will soon be ready to join the battle against the "
"goblin hordes. I have delivered the news to Taelis the Councillor, after I "
"had completed collecting all the ingredients Kalshar the Arcanist requested "
"for the spellcasters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2544"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Mardahan the Blacksmith to assist with the "
"construction of guard towers and guard houses. The latest goblin attacks "
"have forced Deep Yishku to strengthen it's defenses."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2546"
msgstr ""
"The construction Deep Yishku's new guard towers and guard houses is coming "
"along well. I have delivered the good news to Nirgash the Councillor as "
"Mardahan the Blacksmith instructed me to do."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2548"
msgstr ""
"The goblin continue to push hard, but so do we. I have returned from the "
"battlefield after successfully killing seven goblins in less than an hour. "
"It would seem that our previous efforts against the goblins were not enough, "
"and the goblins had return to Deep Yishku in greater numbers. These goblins "
"are proving to be quite resilient, not to mention quite numerous. The fight "
"continues."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2550"
msgstr ""
"A military campaign against the mirdain of Mirendil is being planned. I have "
"reported for duty with Ilrak the Arcanist to help prepare Deep Yishkus's "
"spellcasters as best as possible. All help is needed, especially that of the "
"spellcasters if we are to succeed crushing the mirdain vermin."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2552"
msgstr ""
"I have gathering the five units of sulfur as instructed by Ilrak the "
"Arcanist. Sulfur is a reagent used by spellcasters to cast their powerful "
"spells."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2554"
msgstr ""
"According the Ilrak the Arcanist, resin is one of the reagents spellcasters "
"need to cast many of their spells. I hope those five units of resin that I "
"gathered will be put to good use by DeepYishku's spellcasters in the battle "
"against the hateful mirdain."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2556"
msgstr ""
"Ilrak the Arcanist is pleased with the amount of magical ingredients that "
"has been collected, and soon Deep Yishku's spellcasters will be ready to "
"take part in the campaign against the mirdain. I have delivered the news to "
"Nirgash the Councillor."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2558"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Neissur the Blacksmith, after Irshanta the "
"Councillor informed me that Neissur had put in a request for an extra pair "
"of hands to assist him with his work."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2560"
msgstr ""
"I have report for duty at Irshanta the Councillor, once Neissur informed me "
"that Irshanta wishes to speak to me. This sounds quite important. Good thing "
"that Neissur the Blacksmith no longer required my assistance."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2562"
msgstr ""
"I have returned back to Akathos and Irshanta the Councillor, after killing "
"seven of the goblins that have been attacking and looting caravans along "
"Akathos's trade routes. The goblins are growing more violent and arrogant, "
"to the point that they seem not to fear us anymore. Something is not right."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2564"
msgstr ""
"A military campaign against the Mirdain of Mirendil is being planned. "
"Irshanta the Councillor has ordered me to report to Thielit the Arcanist, "
"and assist in preparing Akathos's spellcasters for the upcoming battles. I "
"shall do everything I can to see the mirdain fall."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2566"
msgstr ""
"I have gathering the five units of sulfur that Thielit the Arcanist asked "
"for. Sulfur is also one of the reagents used in the art of spellcasting."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2568"
msgstr ""
"In the campaign against the mirdain, Akathos's spellcaster will need many "
"ingredients to cast their spells, such as resin. Thielit the Arcanist "
"instructed me to gather five units of resin."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2570"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered Thielit's message to Irshanta the Councillor, that "
"Akathos's spellcasters will soon be ready to partake in the campaign against "
"the mirdain. What kind of support the spellcasters will provide, is yet to "
"be seen."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2572"
msgstr ""
"The recent goblin attacks have made it quite obvious that Silverspear needs "
"to improve its defenses. I have reported for duty with Sa-Imdor the "
"Blacksmith, to assist with the improvement of the town walls and the "
"construction of the guard towers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2574"
msgstr ""
"All the building materials needed for the strengthening of the Silverspear's "
"walls and the construction of the guard towers have been gathered. "
"Construction of both is soon to begin. Sa-Imdor the Blacksmith instructed me "
"to deliver the news to Ialynna the Councillor, which of course I did."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2576"
msgstr ""
"Seven goblins in less that an hour is what the elders demanded from all of "
"us. The goblin numbers have increased, and are dangerously approaching "
"Silverspear. I hope this counter attack of ours has significantly weakened "
"the goblin hordes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2578"
msgstr ""
"It has been decided that the spellcasters of Silverspear are to join the "
"battle against the goblin hordes. I have reported for duty with Murion-tai "
"to assist with preparing the spellcasters, by gathering specific materials "
"that are needed for them to cast their spells."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2580"
msgstr ""
"More materials for spells. I have gathered five units of sulfur for Murion-"
"tai the Arcanist. Sulfur is also another of the reagents used in the art of "
"spellcasting. Now it is up to Silverspear's spellcasters to put the sulfur "
"to good use against the goblins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2582"
msgstr ""
"Resin can become quite a powerful item in the hands of an experienced "
"spellcaster, according to Murion-tai. It is one of the reagents used in the "
"art of spellcasting. I have gathered five units of resin for Murion-tai the "
"Arcanist as requested."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2584"
msgstr ""
"Our spellasters will soon be ready to partake in Silverspear's battle "
"against the goblin hordes. I have delivered the news to Ialynna the "
"Councillor, after I had completed collecting all the ingredients Murion-tai "
"the Arcanist requested for the spellcasters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2586"
msgstr ""
"Arkelia the Councillor has asks me to report to Molangar the Blacksmith in "
"Leenglow. Apparently Molangar is having a hard time with the amount of work "
"he has at the moment. I am curious to see how exactly it is that I can help."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2588"
msgstr ""
"I have report for duty with Arkelia the Councillor after Molangar informed "
"me that Arkelia wishes to speak to me. This sounds quite important. Good "
"thing that Molangar the Blacksmith no longer required my assistance in "
"gathering more construction materials for Leenglow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2590"
msgstr ""
"I have returned back to Leenglow and Arkelia the Councillor, after killing "
"seven of the goblins that have been attacking and looting caravans along "
"Leenglow's trade routes. The goblins are growing more arrogant and more "
"violent every day, to the point that they seem not to fear us anymore. "
"Something is not right."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2592"
msgstr ""
"Amauron the Arcanist has requested that I help him collect the ingredients "
"the spellcasters need, ingredients to support Leenglow's battle against the "
"goblin hordes. I shall do the best I can, as long as it is for the good and "
"safety of Leenglow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2594"
msgstr ""
"I have gathering the five units of sulfur that Amauron the Arcanist asked "
"for. If sulfur is what the spellcasters of Leenglow need in the fight "
"against the goblin infestation, then sulfur I shall collect."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2596"
msgstr ""
"Who would have thought that resin could be so important. I have just handed "
"to Amauron the Arcanist five units of resin. Apparently resin is one of the "
"reagents that spellcasters use for casting spells."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2598"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered Amauron's message to Arkelia the Councillor, that "
"Leenglow's spellcasters will soon be ready to do battle against the goblin "
"hordes. I am very interested to see what kind of support the spellcasters "
"can provide."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2600"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Felalon the Blacksmith to assist with the "
"construction of guard towers and guard houses. The latest goblin attacks "
"have forced Hunter's Moon to strengthen it's defenses."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2602"
msgstr ""
"The construction of the guard towers and guard houses in Hunter's Moon is "
"progressing well. Felalon the Blacksmith instructed me to deliver the good "
"news to Andor-Kai the Councillor, and that I did."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2604"
msgstr ""
"I have returned from the battlefield after successfully killing seven "
"goblins in less than on hour, as requested by Andor-Kai the Councillor. It "
"would seem that our previous efforts to repel the goblins from Hunter's Moon "
"were no enough, and now the goblins had return in greater numbers. These "
"goblin are proving to by very resilient, not to mention quite numerous. The "
"fight continues."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2606"
msgstr ""
"I am to assist Celene the Arcanist with preparing Hunter's Moon's "
"spellcasters as best as possible. All help is needed, even that of the "
"spellcasters if Hunter's Moon is to completely eradicate the goblin menace."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2608"
msgstr ""
"I have completed gathering the five units of sulfur that Celene the Arcanist "
"asked for. If sulfur is what the spellcasters of Hunter's Moon need in the "
"fight against the goblin infestation, then sulfur I shall collect."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2610"
msgstr ""
"According the Celene the Arcanist, resin is one of the reagents spellcasters "
"need to cast many of their spells. I hope that the five units of resin I "
"collected will be put to good use by Hunter's Moon's spellcasters in the "
"battle against the goblin hordes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2612"
msgstr ""
"Celene the Arcanist is pleased with the amount of magical ingredients that "
"has been collected, and soon the spellcasters will be ready to take part in "
"Hunter's Moon's war against the goblin threat. I have just delivered the "
"good news to Andor-Kai the Councillor."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2614"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Ciredan the Blacksmith to assist with the "
"construction of several defensive projects. The latest goblin attacks have "
"forced Leafhelm to strengthen its defenses."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2616"
msgstr ""
"Leafhelm's wall improvements are progressing as planned, and the "
"construction of the guard towers is soon to begin. I have delivered the good "
"news to Silawen the Councillor, as Ciredan the Blacksmith requested. "
"Leafhelm will surely be defended much better in the future."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2618"
msgstr ""
"I have returned from the battlefield after successfully killing seven "
"goblins in less than an hour as instructed by Silawen the Councillor. It "
"would seem that our previous efforts to repel the goblins from Leafhelm were "
"not enough, and now the goblins have returned in greater numbers. The fight "
"continues."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2620"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Eredil the Arcanist, to assist with preparing "
"Leafhelm's spellcasters. All help is needed, especially that of the "
"spellcasters, if Leafhelm is to completely eradicate the goblin menace."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2622"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered the five units of sulfur as requested by Eredil the "
"Arcanist. All that remains, is for the spellcasters to put the sulfur to "
"good use, and rid Leafhelm of the goblin bands."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2624"
msgstr ""
"According the Eredil the Arcanist, resin is one of the reagents spellcasters "
"need to cast many of their spells. I have gathered and delivered five units "
"of resin to Eredil the Arcanist in Leafhelm."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2626"
msgstr ""
"Eredil the Arcanist is pleased with the amount of magical ingredients that "
"have been collected, and very soon Leafhelm's spellcasters will be ready to "
"take part in the battle against the goblin hordes. I have delivered the news "
"to Silawen the Councillor."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2628"
msgstr ""
"The recent goblin attacks have made it quite obvious that King's Holdfast "
"needs to improve its defenses. I have reported for duty with Dinuil the "
"Blacksmith, who has already begun working on several defensive projects."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2630"
msgstr ""
"The building materials needed for King's Holdfast defense projects have been "
"gathered, and construction has begun. Dinuil the Blacksmith instructed me to "
"deliver the news to Elvallie the Councillor, which I gladly did."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2632"
msgstr ""
"To kill seven goblins in less that an hour, is what Elvallie the Councillor "
"requested from all. The goblin numbers have increased, and are dangerously "
"approaching King's Holdfast. I hope this counter attack of ours will "
"significantly weakened the goblin hordes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2634"
msgstr ""
"It has been decided that the spellcasters of King's Holdfast are to join the "
"battle against the goblin hordes. I have reported for duty with Aergeir the "
"Arcanist to assist with preparing the spellcasters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2636"
msgstr ""
"More materials for spells. I have gathered  five units of sulfur for Aergeir "
"the Arcanist. Sulfur is another of the reagents used in the art of "
"spellcasting. Now it is up to the spellcasters of King's Holdfast to put the "
"sulfur to good use against the goblins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2638"
msgstr ""
"Resin is a powerful item in the hands of an experienced spellcaster. It is "
"one of the reagents used in the art of spellcasting. I have gathered and "
"delivered five units of resin to Aergeir the Arcanist as requested."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2640"
msgstr ""
"Our spellasters will soon be able to support King's Holdfast in the battle "
"against the goblin hordes. I have delivered the news to Elvallie the "
"Councillor, after having completed collecting all the ingredients Aergeir "
"the Arcanist requested for the spellcasters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2642"
msgstr ""
"The goblin attacks have made it obvious that Beladin's Rest needs to "
"strengthen its defenses. I have reported for duty with Tiyawen the "
"Blacksmith, to assist him with the construction of the new guard towers and "
"guard houses."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2644"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the good news to Lysandir the Councillor, that all the "
"building materials needed for the construction of the new defenses for "
"Beladin's Rest has been gathered. Work should begin very soon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2646"
