"Back for duty with Vilethug the Councillor, after helping Azog recover some "
"of her stolen merchandise. I also informed the Councillor that the caravans "
"have been spotted, and should soon by arriving in New Flayed Elf."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2884"
msgstr ""
"The caravans that Arinthu the Merchant had been expecting to arrive in "
"Onghral, have been attacked by goblins and therefor delayed. I have reported "
"for duty with Arinthu to see if there is anyway to help recover any of the "
"stolen merchandise."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2886"
msgstr ""
"I have managed to retrieve four of the leather pieces that were part of "
"Arinthu's stolen merchandise. First attacking Onghral and now stealing from "
"the caravans, those goblin are truly becoming annoying. The goblins must be "
"stopped."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2888"
msgstr ""
"After recovering some of Arinthu's stolen merchandise, Arinthu promised to "
"teach me some basic cooking skills. Interesting enough, I managed to cook "
"for myself a trout after following Arinthu's instructions from how to fish, "
"to using the oven in Onghral."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2890"
msgstr ""
"Word has arrived that the caravans have been spotted and are on their way to "
"Onghral. Arinthu the Merchant has asked me to deliver the good news to "
"Taelis the Councillor."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2892"
msgstr ""
"I have reached Kaelit the Merchant to assist her with a problem. It would "
"seem that some of the merchandise that Kaelit has been expecting, has yet to "
"arrive in Deep Yishku."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2894"
msgstr ""
"I have recovered four of the leather pieces that the goblins stole from "
"Kaelit the Merchant in Deep Yishku. It wasn't a difficult task, but why "
"would the goblins steal the leather pieces? Now that I have recovered that "
"stolen leather, Kaelit has promised to teach me some basic cooking skills."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2896"
msgstr ""
"I have carefully followed all of Kaelit's steps from fishing to using the "
"oven in Deep Yishku, and successfully cooked a basic meal for myself, a "
"cooked cod fish. Although not as exiting a fighting the goblin hordes, it is "
"a skill I am sure to find handy in the future."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2898"
msgstr ""
"I have reported back to Nirgash the Councillor after helping Kaelit the "
"Merchant recover some of her stolen goods. Something tells me that this "
"won't be the last time that Deep Yishku's caravans will be attacked by "
"thieving goblins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2900"
msgstr ""
"I have been informed by Irshanta the Councillor, that the caravans Talduk "
"the Merchant has been expecting in Akathos, have not yet arrived. I have "
"report for duty with Talduk the Merchant to help with the situation."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2902"
msgstr ""
"Talduk the Merchant was correct in speculating that the goblins are the "
"cause of the delayed caravans in Akathos. I managed to recover four pieces "
"of leather from the annoying goblins as requested by Talduk."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2904"
msgstr ""
"I carefully followed all of Talduk's steps from fishing to using the oven in "
"Akathos, and successfully cooked a basic meal for myself, a cooked cod. I am "
"sure this is a skill I am to find useful in the future."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2906"
msgstr ""
"Back for duty with Irshanta the Councillor, after helping Talduk recover "
"some of his stolen merchandise. I also informed the Councillor, that the "
"caravans have been spotted, and should soon be arriving in Akathos."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2908"
msgstr ""
"I doesn't matter where and how far an enemy is located from the Alfar, that "
"enemy will be hunted down and killed. I have return from the far north, "
"after killing two Mahirim player characters, two Dwarf player characters and "
"two Ork player characters. All weak and pathetic!"

msgid "diary_text_quest_2910"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Ordgrim the Councillor in the dwarven capital "
"city of Ymir's Tear. I was informed by Sylanae the Councillor that our "
"allies the dwarves are in need of our help."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2912"
msgstr ""
"I have done our allies the dwarves proud, by helping them in their battle "
"against the barbaric orks. Four Ork player characters are dead."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2914"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Sylanae the Councillor in the mirdain capital "
"city of Charybdis. I was informed by Allen the Councillor that our allies "
"the mirdain are in need of our help."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2916"
msgstr ""
"I have done our allies the mirdain proud, by helping them in their battle "
"against the mahirim beasts. Four Mahirim player characters are dead."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2918"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Allan the Councillor in the human capital city "
"of Sanguine. I was informed by Ordgrim the Councillor that our allies the "
"humans are in need of our help."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2920"
msgstr ""
"I have done our allies the humans proud, by helping them in their battle "
"against the evil alfar. Four Alfar player characters are dead."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2922"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Tivasta the Councillor in the mahirim capital "
"city of Red Moon. I was informed by Izkruul the Councillor that our allies "
"the mahirim are in need of our help."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2924"
msgstr ""
"I have made our allies the mahirim proud, by successfully helping them in "
"their battle against the weak and pathetic mirdain. Four Mirdain player "
"characters are dead, and many more are surely to follow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2926"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Izkruul the Councillor in the ork capital city "
"of Flaming Skull. I was informed by Tivasta the Councillor that our allies "
"the orks are in need of our help."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2929"
msgstr ""
"After fighting the mirdain, Tivasta the Councillor requested that I help the "
"mahirim deal with another enemy, the alfar. Once more I assisted our allies "
"by killing five Alfar player characters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2931"
msgstr ""
"After fighting the mirdain, Izkrull the Councillor requested that I help the "
"ork deal with another enemy, the dark and sinister alfar. Once more I "
"assisted our allies by killing five Alfar player characters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2933"
msgstr ""
"I have made our allies the ork proud, by successfully helping them in their "
"battle against the weak and pathetic humans. Four Human player characters "
"are dead, and many more are surely to follow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2934"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Arinlit Icethrone, in the {$l23} region. I am "
"to assist the Radiant Circle search for the legendary Demon Hand."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2936"
msgstr ""
"I have extracted revenge for the patrol officers that were killed by the "
"windlords. Three Wind Shadowcrests have been harvested from the windlords, "
"as requesrted by Arinlit Icethrone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2938"
msgstr ""
"The legendary Demon Hand that the Radiant Circle so desires, has been found. "
"It was hidden in the windlords lair near the Velmuna Outpoast, as Arinlit "
"Icethrone suggested."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2939"
msgstr ""
"The legendary Demon Hand has been delivered to Arinlit Icethrone. All that "
"remains is to verify that this is indeed the real demon hand that supreme "
"general Velmuna severed from the once formidable Demon Warlord of the region."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2941"
msgstr ""
"It has been verified. The demon hand I delivered to Shulazu Nightshade in "
"Dun Amsharra, is the real one. The Legendary Demon Hand, the one that was "
"removed from the Demon Warlord by supreme general Velmuna, over three "
"centuries ago."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2943"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Kaldahan Deepshadow, and delivered orders "
"regarding the traitorous Melechar."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2945"
msgstr ""
"Seven Melechar died by my hand today, for disobeying Shoal and betraying the "
"Alfar. The Melechar will never find peace, for betraying Nagast. This is the "
"will of Melek. This is the way of the aflar!"

msgid "diary_text_quest_2947"
msgstr ""
"I have retrieved the Holy Symbol of Melek from the village of the traitorous "
"Melechar. Now all that remains to complete this mission, is to return the "
"symbol to Kaldahan Deepshadow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2948"
msgstr ""
"I successfully retrieved the Holy Symbol of Melek from the Melechar village "
"in {$q23}. The traitorous Melechar  have been stripped of their only "
"connection to Melek and Shoal. Let it be clear to them, they are enemies of "
"the alfar!"

msgid "diary_text_quest_2950"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered another of Kaldahan's report to Nathar Blackorb, after "
"punishing the traitorous Melechar."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2952"
msgstr ""
"An old weather-torn tombstone with strange symbols has been discovered "
"within the old abandoned severii stronghold in {$n20}, that might have "
"something to do with the appearance of the serpentines."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2954"
msgstr ""
"Three of the Serpentines that have {$n20}, have been killed. The Harn "
"Mandean will not risk having these creatures dwell at Nagast's doorstep."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2956"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered a letter with the ancient writings that were discovered "
"upon the mysterious tombstone in {$n20}, to Ninnah the Mage in Shoal. "
"According to Aeshanta Darkspire, Ninnah is an expert in deciphering ancient "
"texts."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2958"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered and delivered three units of elemental cinder to Ninah the "
"Mage in Shoal, to be used in the deciphering of some mysterious ancient "
"texts."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2960"
msgstr ""
"I have traveled to the city of Espanhal to meet Ninseri the Mage. Apparently "
"she too has discovered a similar tombstone with demonic writing upon it, and "
"I am to convince her to give me a copy to bring back to Ninnah in Shoal."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2962"
msgstr ""
"It was as Ninnah had told me. That for Ninseri the Mage to hand me a copy of "
"the demonic texts she had found, I would have to give her something in "
"return. I accepted to gather for her ten Cursed Darktaint."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2964"
msgstr ""
"After gathering the tainted hearts for Ninseri, Ninseri kept her word and "
"handed me a copy of the demonic writings. I returned to Shoal, and delivered "
"the text to Ninseri the Mage."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2967"
msgstr ""
"The Shadow Salient scouts were correct. The dungeon complex in {$o25} is "
"being used by gray orks as a stronghold. I successfully entered the dungeon, "
"kill three gray orks, and return Dekazu Fearweaver with an assessment of the "
"gray orks strengths and the layout of the dungeon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2969"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Elena the Mage of the Sons of Riada. "
"Apparently, after finding the Dragontorc, Elena believes that I may be able "
"to help her locate another lost nithron artifact."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2971"
msgstr ""
"Before the Sons of Riada are able to investigate the nithron ruins in "
"{$x20}, the ancient site had to be cleared of the Oathbound, magical "
"guardians left behind by the nithron. After destroying five of the "
"oathbound, I returned to Elena theMage in {$u21} with my evaluation the "
"oathbounds capabilities."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2973"
msgstr ""
"Elena the Mage was correct. In the old libraries of the abandoned nithron "
"city in {$x20}, I did find the ancient nithron book called the Chronicles of "
"the Firstborn. Now to deliver it to her."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2974"
msgstr ""
"The Chronicles of the Firstborn have safely been delivered to Elena the Mage "
"in {$u21}. With this book, the Sons of Riada will be able to learn more "
"about the nithron artifacts they discover."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2976"
msgstr ""
"I have traveled from {$u21} to {$u19}, and deliver Elena's report to Allan "
"the Councillor. Elena believes that a prophecy regarding the nithron and "
"their return to Agon, could turn out to be true."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2978"
msgstr ""
"After assisting the Knights of Malregard in their battle against the Malaut "
"and the Twilight Empire, I was summoned to Sanguine to report to Allan the "
"Councillor. Apparently, there is more work to be done."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2980"
msgstr ""
"The torture chamber within the Malaut stronghold in {$s19} has been located, "
"and so has the unholy book of Malaut. All that remains is to exit the "
"dungeon, and deliver the book to Allan the Councillor in Sanguine."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2981"
msgstr ""
"I entered the hidden Malaut dungeon stronghold in {$s19} and stole the "
"unholy book of Malaut, as instructed by Allan the Councillor. This unholy "
"book will provide valuable information in the battle against Malaut and the "
"Twilight Empire."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2983"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Oona Fern in Silverley, after a letter by Oona Fern "
"had arrived at the White Order requesting help."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2985"
msgstr ""
"The four gray ork I killed should be enough to scare the rest of them out of "
"{$v17}, and to allow the enchanters of Silverley to do their job collecting "
"materials that are needed for the crafting of magical weapons."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2987"
msgstr ""
"With the support of the White Order, I have killed three Guildmasters, three "
"Outlaws and three Highwaymen hiding in Highmoore. The time of the thugs and "
"thieves of Highmoore terrorizing northwest mercia is soon to end."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2989"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Aurmon the Brave in {$k11}. Aurmon has be "
"gathering information about the dangerous behavior of the centaurs in Wolf "
"Run. I am to assist his work."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2991"
msgstr ""
"Until it has been detected, that which is responsible for the wild and "
"aggressive behavior of the centaurs in Wolf Run, the centaurs must be "
"stopped. I have killed six centaurs as instructed by Aurmon the Brave."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2993"
msgstr ""
"After helping Aurmon stop some of the wild centaurs in Wolf Run, I returned "
"to Stonehold and delivered Aurmon's report to Yaleria-Sai. What is driving "
"the centaurs mad, has yet to be found."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2995"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered all the proof needed that Lesser Fire Elemental do exist in "
"Meldanyr dungeon. One unit of Elemental Cinder."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2997"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the materials that Yaleria-Sai had prepared for Katila the "
"Arcanist of the Circle of Neith in Moonclaw. Katila was extremely please to "
"receive the Elemental Cinder, which had something to do with deciphering an "
"ancient scroll."

msgid "diary_text_quest_2999"
msgstr ""
"I have killed four of the Bonecrew, that are responsible for tainting the "
"waters of Fang Lake. Until the Wolfmasks discover why the Bonecrew have "
"appeared, all they can do is to keep destroying them."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3001"
msgstr ""
"The Wolfmask discovered that the humans who were hiding in the ruins in "
"{$l14}, were actually working for a secretive group. For now, communication "
"between the two group has been halted, after destroying the marked "
"gravestone in{$l15}, that was used to leave messages."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3003"
msgstr ""
"I completed the Wolfmasks mission of evaluating the strength of the gray "
"orks in {$m13}. It seems that Gray Orks throughout Agon have been attacking "
"surface orks, the Orks of Morak. Why this is happening I do not know, but it "
"is good to see the Woflmasks helping the orks."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3005"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Tivasta the Councillor in Red Moon. It seems "
"that my success in finding the lost half of the sacred stone tablet, has "
"impressed Red Moon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3007"
msgstr ""
"The resting place of Ammuran's faithful general Larren-Tai, has been found "
"within the Larethain dungeon. At last, the name of this quite hero, and and "
"lawful servant of the mahirim people, will be restored. Larren-tai's story "
"will be told, and her name never again forgotten."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3009"
msgstr ""
"The appearance of the mysterious menhir in Moonclaw, has caused a lot of "
"recruitment among the ranks of the Circle of Neith. So, to assist them in "
"their quest for knowledge, I accepted to harvest a Tribal Lifeforce, for "
"their researchers to study."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3011"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Levynna the Arcanist of the Elders of Red "
"Moon. I am to study the  Akathars that Levynna had located, on behalf of the "
"Circle of Neith."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3013"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully harvest three Wind Shadowcrest from the Akathars, as "
"suggested by Levynna the Arcanist of the Elders of Red Moon, and delivered "
"them to Celetia the White."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3015"
msgstr ""
"I have found the Book of Bad Magic that was magically hidden in the "
"graveyard near the ruin tower of the wizard Siritos. All that remains is to "
"bring it to Caradial Elmheart in Imathir."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3016"
msgstr ""
"The Book of Bad Magic, the life's work of the renowned wizard Siritos, is "
"now in the possession of the Emerald Throne. All the knowledge that Siritos "
"had acquired about the time of Bad Magic, is now in the disposal of the "
"scholar of the Emerald Throne."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3018"
msgstr ""
"I have helped the Emerald Throne clear the tower of Siritos in Inarith from "
"the undead. I successfully destroyed four ghouls as instructed by Caradial "
"Elmheart."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3020"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Sylanae the Councillor in Charybdis, after "
"killing four gray orks as requested by the Emerald Throne. Groups of gray "
"orks have been seen lurking close to the mirdain borders throughout "
"Mirendil, and Charybdis had requested all factions to send agents to remove "
"as many as possible."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3022"
msgstr ""
"Apparently the hobgoblins were not working alone. Arrowhead agents "
"discovered that gray ork mercenaries were hired by the hobgoblins to do "
"their dirty work. I killed four gray orks as instructed by Eredethil "
"Swiftarrow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3024"
msgstr ""
"Four melechar have been killed, as instructed by Eredethil Swiftarrow. "
"Charybdis was correct in suspecting that the Baradron dungeon was being used "
"as a hideout by the evil melechar."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3026"
msgstr ""
"After I successfully completed my mission into the melechar stronghold in "
"the Baradron dungeon, Eredethil conducted a report letter with all the "
"information the Arrowhead had gathered on the activities of the melechar. I "
"then accepted to deliver Eredethil's report letter to Sylanae the Councillor "
"in Charybdis."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3028"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Theila Brightstar in Lower Eredras. I will be "
"receiving my next orders form Theila, regarding my mission about the "
"melechars main stronghold in {$k18}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3030"
msgstr ""
"I have found the unholy book of Melek with the main melechar stronghold in "
"{$k18}. All that remains is to deliver the book to Sylanae the Councillor in "
"Charybdis."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3031"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the unholy book of Melek to Sylanae the Councillor in "
"Charybdis. According to  Sylanae, the thieving of the unholy book of Melek "
"should create enough chaos among the melechar, to provide Charybdis with the "
"opportunity to launch an attack against all melechar in and near the mirdain "
"lands."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3033"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Naianir Treedancer in Mir Gelien, to assist "
"with the search of the Rod of Bad Magic."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3035"
msgstr ""
"I have found the Rod of Bad Magic, hidden away in one of the many tombs at "
"the base of the Crystal Green Tower in {$j16}. All that remains is to "
"deliver to rod to Aelathil Silverleaf in Iriendir."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3036"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the Rod of Bad Magic to Aelathil Silverleaf. The Serene "
"Spire will have to discover how the wizard Damanthel did manage to create "
"this item of Bad Magic, and what it can actually do."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3038"
msgstr ""
"I successfully destroyed six of the oathbound inside {$i16} dungeon, and "
"bought enough time for the researchers of the Serene Spire, to enter the "
"dungeon and explore the Nithron ruins within. These are the first Nithron "
"ruin that the Spire has encounters inside any underground dungeon complex."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3040"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered three units of Putrid Corpseflesh for Aelathil Silverleaf. "
"The Serene Spire will analyze these samples, in an attempt to try to "
"understand how the Nithron managed to create the Revenants."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3042"
msgstr ""
"Sylanae the Councillor asked me to report to Nairath the Mage, to help him "
"with is tasks. I accepted."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3044"
msgstr ""
"I have managed to gather four units of Timeless Blood and two Tainted Hearts "
"in less than three hours, as requested by Nairath the Mage. Apparently these "
"will be used to create magical item."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3046"
msgstr ""
"It was a bloody job, but worth it. Three Barbed Claw have be extracted for "
"the beastman, and delivered to Nairath the Mage in Charybdis."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3048"
msgstr ""
"I delivered a package to Riathen the Mage in Imathir, that Nairath the Mage "
"had prepared earlier. A simple package with some enchanting materials."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3050"
msgstr ""
"I have report for duty with Kanute Wayfarer in {$o08}. Garin Silvervault "
"informed me that my next mission will have something to do with the "
"legendary Aegin's Hall."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3052"
msgstr ""
"Although the Ice Demon Aegin was slain long ago by dwarven heroes, the "
"demon's ice fortress in {$o07}, has become the base of a monster army led by "
"ogres. To eliminate any future threat to nearby dwarven communities, I "
"accepted and killed three Hobgoblins, one Windgraive and two Ogre Bosses."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3054"
msgstr ""
"I have located Aegin's Scepter, hidden inside a chest in {$o07}. Apparently "
"the Ogre Bosses hadn't yet figured out how to activate it. All that remains "
"is to deliver the scepter to Garin Silvervault in Wintercrown."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3055"
msgstr ""
"After locating the legendary scepter of Aegin, I returned to Wintercrown, "
"and handed the scepter to Garin Silvervault. A powerful artifact like this, "
"should not be left in the hands of stupid ogres."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3057"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Nidstein the Mage. According to Garin "
"Silvervault, Nidstein is interested in researching the once powerful "
"Nithron, and the many secrets they have left behind."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3059"
msgstr ""
"I have found Eiradan's amulet, hidden inside a chest in the Nithron city in "
"{$n11}. All that remains is to deliver the amulet to Nidstein the Mage."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3060"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the powerful artifact called the amulet of Eiradan to "
"Nidstein the Mage, after successfully locating it, in the Nithron city in "
"{$n11}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3062"
msgstr ""
"I have killed four of the oathbound guardians of the Nithron city in {$n11}, "
"and delivered my opinion of their strengths and weaknesses to Nidstein the "
"Mage. Only in large numbers could the oathbound pose a threat to Dvergheim's "
"safety."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3064"
msgstr ""
"I entered the svartdvergir stronghold dungeon in Svartvann, and hunted down "
"five svartdvergir summoners. It is the summoners who carry out the horrid "
"rituals that transforming dwarves into svartdvergir, the dark servants of "
"Sahul. Destroying the summoners could be the key to destroying the "
"svartdvergir."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3066"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Eyvind the Merchant in Evignanger. There seems "
"to been a growing hivekin problem in the region, one that is threatening the "
"trade."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3068"
msgstr ""
"Although the hivekin are not that dangerous, in large number they can pose a "
"great threat to the trade. I have managed to kill eight hivekin soldiers in "
"Evigvanger as instructed by Eyvind the Merchant."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3070"
msgstr ""
"After helping Eyvind the Merchant confine the hivekin problem in Evigvanger, "
"I return to Gemstone Reach to deliver the good news to the Five Beards "
"Trading Company."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3072"
msgstr ""
"I discovered a shrine dedicated to the svartdvergir deity Sahul, with a "
"skeleton magically floating above it. Perhaps this evil shrine is "
"responsible for the undead dwarves that keep rising withing the Otredale "
"mines. I must report this finding to Garn Runeshield."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3073"
msgstr ""
"Garn Runeshield has been informed of the mysterious Sahul shrine with the "
"skeleton floating above it, located inside the Otredale mines. The Five "
"Beards will now investigate to see if this shrine is somehow raising the "
"undead dwarves inside the mines over and over again."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3075"
msgstr ""
"There is a sudden uprising in gray orks across the lands. The alliance has "
"decided to attack all gray ork camps, before the gray orks start attacking "
"the alliance I successfully killed three of the gray orks that have "
"fortified themselves in Istind, as instructed by Thain Strongforge."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3077"
msgstr ""
"I have found a letter in the Fire Standard hobgoblin camp in {$q11}, which "
"might reveal information about the Fire Standard hobgoblins leaders."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3078"
msgstr ""
"It is as Thain Strongforge suspected. The letter I delivered to him has "
"revealed that the hobgoblin grunts would have never acted on their on and "
"attacked the dwarven communities, but were definitely carrying out orders. "
"And now the Order of the Axe knows from who."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3080"
msgstr ""
"While ending the life of the third Hobgoblin Veteran of the Fire Standard "
"Hobgoblin leaders in {$n12}, as instructed by the Order of the Axe, I "
"discovered a letter.  A letter containing orders sent by the Raven Standard "
"hobgoblins. Thain Strongforge must be informed of this find immediately."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3081"
msgstr ""
"Things are getting complicated. We discovered that the hobgoblins of the "
"Fire Standarded are just a cover for the Raven Standard hobgoblins, after "
"the letter that was found in their camp. This find has puzzled the Order of "
"the Axe, since it has been many years since anybody has heard of the "
"hobgoblins of the Raven Standard. Is this return of the fierce Raven "
"Standard Army?"

msgid "diary_text_quest_3083"
msgstr ""
"The Raven Standard Army has returned. Where, and in what size, is yet to be "
"discovered. What I did manage was to locate one of the Raven Standard Camps, "
"and killed three Raven Standard Hobgoblin Grunts. My assessment for the "
"Order of the Axe is, that in large numbers, the Rave Standard Army will "
"surely be a force to reckon with."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3085"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Frostinn the Mage. Frostinn believes she has "
"discovered the location of a legendary artifact, and has requested my help "
"in locating it."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3087"
msgstr ""
"I have located the legendary artifact known as Durganon's Brazier within "
"Fire Hall dungeon. All that remains is to report this find to Frostinn the "
"Mage."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3088"
msgstr ""
"I delivered the good news to Frostinn the Mage, that I have successfully "
"located the legendary dwarven artifact Durganon's Brazier, inside Fire Hall "
"dungeon. Unfortunately, it is the possession of the svartdvergir. Now the "
"Order of the Axe must find a way to recover the artifact."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3090"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Ninnah the Mage, as a representative of the "
"Radiant Circle. I am to examine the strange creatures sighted in the Zahnal "
"dungeon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3092"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully verified the existence of the elusive Nalaeds and "
"Darkweavers within the Zahnal dungeon, by gathering one unit of Ichor and "
"one unit of Numen from their bodies. The Radiant Circle will be pleased with "
"this finding."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3094"
msgstr ""
"I have fought the Nalaeds and the Sarlid Darkweavers within the Zahnal "
"dungeon, and delivered my verdict to Ensharra the Councillor, on the "
"creatures strengths and weaknesses. One thing is clear. These creature pose "
"no threat to the alfar, if confined to the dungeon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3096"
msgstr ""
"I have decided to continue to provide my services to the Radiant Circle. I "
"have traveled to Castle Obad, to meet Sriva Ghostweb of the Radiant Circle, "
"and assist Castle Obad's activities anyway possible."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3098"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered five Vile Horn for Sriva Ghostweb at Castle Obad, and thus "
"helped the castle's young mages continue their studies in the art of "
"enchanting."

msgid "diary_text_quest_31"
msgstr ""
"I successfully killed ten goblins, and now the farmers of Sanguine can get "
"back to work feeding the refugees.  It sounds like there is more "
"investigating to be done to find out how Goblins got this close to the "
"Mercian capital."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3100"
msgstr ""
"Six Gloomy Darktaint have been gathered and delivered to Sriva Ghostweb of "
"the Radiant Circle at Castle Obad."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3102"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Shulgan Shadowscream, head of security at "
"Castle Obad. Apparently hobgoblins have appeared near the castle, and could "
"become a major threat for the castle in the near future."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3104"
msgstr ""
"A possible future raid against the Castle Obad by the hobgoblins has been "
"stopped. Four hobgoblins have been killed, as instructed by Shulgan "
"Shadowscream, head of security at Castle Obad."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3106"
msgstr ""
"The Nahdruk are truly sad creatures. Not able to accept Melek's blessing, "
"the Nahruk have been driven to total madness. I have ended the pain of three "
"Nahdruk, and brought peace to their troubled existence."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3108"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Tialanta the Fighter. Apparently my success in "
"killing many of our enemies had not go unnoticed, and Tialanta the Fighter "
"requested to speak with me."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3110"
msgstr ""
"I successfully passed Tialanta's test, and killed five Human player "
"characters in less than four hours. The humans are truly pathetic."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3112"
msgstr ""
"I successfully passed Tialanta's second trail, and killed five Mirdain "
"player characters in less than four hours. There can never be enough dead "
"mirdain."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3114"
msgstr ""
"Tialanta's mission was challenging, but in the end the mahirim were just not "
"good enough. I passes Tialanta's test, which was to kill five Mahirim player "
"characters in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3116"
msgstr ""
"Big, stupid and ugly. The orks are doomed to vanish as a race. I "
"successfully completed another of  Tialanta's trails, that of killing five "
"Ork player characters in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3118"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with the mage Hanthar Blackfrost in {$k22}, after "
"Aeshanta Darkspire received a letter about groups of Nahdruk been seen "
"within Nagast."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3120"
msgstr ""
"Six weak Nahdruk hiding in the Moradar regions, have been put out of their "
"misery. The Nahdruk are are insult to the alfar, and do not deserve to live."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3122"
msgstr ""
"I gathered five units of Mystical Eye for Hanthar Blackfrost. Not an easy "
"task."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3124"
msgstr ""
"I completed a very dangerous task for Hanthar Blackfrost, the harvesting of "
"eight elemental quartz."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3126"
msgstr ""
"Hanthar Blackfrost's package has been delivered safely to Shulazu Nightshade "
"in Dun Amsharra."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3128"
msgstr ""
"Gnoll Butchers are one of the toughest of the gnoll family. I successfully "
"killed two Gnoll Butchers as requested by Hanthar Blackfrost."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3130"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Hildr the Fighter. Apparently my success in "
"battling the orks had not go unnoticed, and Hildr the Fighter requested to "
"speak with me."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3132"
msgstr ""
"I successfully completed Hildr's test, which was to kill five Mahirim player "
"characters within a four hour time limit."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3134"
msgstr ""
"I traveled from Ymir's Tear to the human capital city Sanguine to meet "
"Torgard the Fighter. Hildr thought it would be good to meet her human friend "
"Torgard, after I had successfully passed her test. Time to be tested by "
"Torgard it seems."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3136"
msgstr ""
"Torgard's mission was difficult, but in the end the orks were just not good "
"enough. I passes Torgard's test which was to kill five Ork player characters "
"in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3138"
msgstr ""
"Torgard needed to see more of my abilities. His next test was also "
"difficult, but again just like the orks, the alfar proved too little. I "
"passes Torgard's second test, which was to kill five Alfar player characters "
"in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3140"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Galien the Fighter. Apparently my success in "
"battling the mahirim had not go unnoticed, and Galien the Fighter requested "
"to speak with me."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3142"
msgstr ""
"I successfully completed Galien's test, which was to kill five Alfar player "
"characters within a four hour time limit."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3144"
msgstr ""
"I traveled from Charybdis to the dwarven capital city Ymir's Tear to meet "
"Hildr the Fighter. Galien thought it would be good to meet his good friend "
"Hildr, after I had successfully passed his test. Time to be tested by Hildr "
"it seems."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3146"
msgstr ""
"Hildr's mission was quite difficult, but in the end the orks were just not "
"good enough. I passes Hildr's test which was to kill five Ork player "
"characters in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3148"
msgstr ""
"Hildr needed to see more of my abilities. Her next test was also difficult, "
"but again just like the orks, the mahirim proved too little. I passes "
"Hildr's second test, which was to kill five Mahirim player characters in "
"less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3150"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Torgard the Fighter. Apparently my success in "
"battling the alfar had not go unnoticed, and Torgard the Fighter requested "
"to speak with me."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3152"
msgstr ""
"I successfully completed Torgard's test, to kill five Ork player characters "
"within a four hour time limit."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3154"
msgstr ""
"I traveled from Sanguine to the mirdain capital city Charybdis to meet "
"Galien the Fighter. Torgard thought it would be good to meet his good friend "
"Galien, after I had successfully passed his test. Time to be tested by "
"Galien it seems."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3156"
msgstr ""
"Galien's mission was quite difficult, but in the end the mahirim were just "
"not good enough. I passes Galien's test which was to kill five Mahirim "
"player characters in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3158"
msgstr ""
"Galien needed to see more of my abilities. His next test was also difficult, "
"but again just like the mahirim, the alfar proved to be very little. I "
"passes Galien's second test, which was to kill five Alfar player characters "
"in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3160"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Cyreia the Fighter. Apparently my success in "
"battling the alfar and the mirdain had not go unnoticed, and Cyreia the "
"Fighter requested to speak with me."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3162"
msgstr ""
"I completed Cyreia's test, which was to kill five Dwarven player characters "
"within a four hour time limit."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3164"
msgstr ""
"I successfully passed Cyreia's second trail, and killed five Mirdain player "
"characters in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3166"
msgstr ""
"After helping our allies the mahirim, and successfully completing all of "
"Cyreia's tests, I returned to Flaming Skull and report for duty with "
"Aksmaster the Fighter. Cyreia though it would be good to be put to the test "
"by Aksmaster himself."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3168"
msgstr ""
"Aksmaster's mission was quite difficult, but in the end the humans were just "
"not good enough. I passes Aksmaster's test, which was to kill five Human "
"player characters in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3170"
msgstr ""
"Aksmaster needed to see more of my abilities. His next test was also "
"difficult, but again just like the humans, the alfar proved too little. I "
"passes Aksmaster's second test, which was to kill five Alfar player "
"characters in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3172"
msgstr ""
"I reported for duty with Aksmaster the Fighter. Apparently my success in "
"battling the alfar and the humans had not go unnoticed, and Aksmaster the "
"Fighter requested to speak with me."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3174"
msgstr ""
"I completed Aksmaster's test, which was to kill five Dwarven player "
"characters within a four hour time limit."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3176"
msgstr ""
"I successfully passed Aksmaster's second trail, and killed five Human player "
"characters in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3178"
msgstr ""
"After helping our allies the orks, and successfully completing all of "
"Aksmaster's tests, I returned to Red Moon and report for duty with Cyreia "
"the Fighter. Aksmaster though it would be good to be put to the test by "
"Cyreia herself."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3180"
msgstr ""
"Cyreia's mission was quite difficult, but in the end the mirdian were just "
"not good enough. I passes Cyreia's test, which was to kill five Mirdian "
"player characters in less than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3182"
msgstr ""
"Cyreia needed to see more of my abilities. Her next test was also difficult, "
"but again just like the mirdain, the alfar proved too little. I passes "
"Cyreia's second test, which was to kill five Alfar player characters in less "
"than four hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3184"
msgstr ""
"Six Gloomy Darktaint have been gathered and delivered to Brehan Thornbrook, "
"which he needs to complete the research of a new spell."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3186"
msgstr ""
"Brehan Thornbrook kept his word, and rewarded me well for gathering those "
"two units of Ghostly Darktaint for him. It seems that researchers and "
"enchanters like Brehan Thornbrook are prepared to pay well for rare "
"enchanting materials."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3188"
msgstr ""
"The Sons of Riada have been having trouble trying to decipher an ancient "
"scroll, and seem they need the help of an expert, that of Brehan Thornbook. "
"I have delivered the ancient scroll to Brehan Thornbook, hoping he will be "
"the one to decipher the ancient scroll."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3190"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered two units of Elemental Cinder, one of the materials needed "
"by Brehan Thornbrook to decipher the ancient scroll sent to him by the Sons "
"of Riada."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3192"
msgstr ""
"I traveled to {$u19}, and deliver a package Brehan Thornbrook had prepared "
"for Niane the Arcanist. By now Brehan should have deciphered the ancient "
"text. Time to return to {$u21}, and see what he has discovered."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3193"
msgstr ""
"I have just return back from {$u19} and Niane the Arcanist, after delivering "
"Brehan's package to her. Brehan informed me that he has also completed the "
"deciphering of the ancient scroll."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3195"
msgstr ""
"Brehan Thornbrook deciphered as much as he could of the ancient scroll, and "
"discovered information about an ancient artifact called the Ring of Power. "
"The Ring of Power was made combining two other artifacts, that of the Demon "
"Ring and the Healing Gem.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"In the wittings Brehan Thornbrook discovered some information on how to "
"located the Healing Gem. Following Brehan Thornbrook's instructions I "
"traveled to the nithron ruins in {$x20}, searched far a statue referred to "
"as the King, and activated it by casting a mana missile spell upon it. The "
"King revealed to me the next step in finding the Healing Gem. To acquire "
"Healing Gem , I must seek the Defender, and battle him."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3196"
msgstr ""
"I have found the statue referred to as the Defender, and battle him. The "
"Defender instructed me to seek the Scholar, and to drain him of his power. "
"To acquire Healing Gem, I must now seek the Scholar, and drain him of his "
"power."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3197"
msgstr ""
"One step closer to finding the Healing Gem. I have located the statue "
"referred to as the Scholar, and by casting a mana drain spell upon him, I "
"have successfully drained him of his power. The Scholar instructed me to "
"return the King, and the Healing Gem will be mine."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3198"
msgstr ""
"I have acquired the Healing Gem for the King. Now all that remains is for me "
"to return to {$u21}, and to deliver the gem to  Brehan Thornbrook."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3199"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully located the Healing Gem in {$x20}, through a series of "
"steps given to me by the three statue guardians of the gem. Brehan "
"Thornbrook was definitely overwhelmed to hold the gem in his hands, and to "
"feel its healing powers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3201"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Colman Ashbourne in {$u17}, a retired member "
"of the White Order. Ashbourne has informed the White Order that groups of "
"Ogres have been attacking and robbing people traveling through Brockmoore."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3203"
msgstr ""
"Four of the bandit Ogres terrorizing {$t17} have been killed, and with the "
"help of other heroes {$t17} will soon be safe again for travel."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3205"
msgstr ""
"Colman's had his revenge. I killed four of the revenants in {$u16}, one for "
"each of his murdered friends. I hope he can find peace now."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3207"
msgstr ""
"According to Ashbourne, hunting and killing orks should provide me with the "
"blessings of Auros. I accepted Ashbourne's quest and killed three Ork Player "
"Characters."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3209"
msgstr ""
"I assisted Colman Ashbourne collect enchanting materials to be used by the "
"enchanters of Silverley. I gathered five Baleful Venom Sacs."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3211"
msgstr ""
"I have collect more enchanting materials for Colman Ashbourne, three Tainted "
"Hearts. It seems that Colman is working very closely with Oona Fern of "
"Silverley."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3213"
msgstr ""
"After all the enchanting materials I gathered for Colman Ashbourne, it was "
"obvious he would ask me to deliver some kind of package to the enchanters in "
"Silverley. I delivered a package to Oona Fern in Silverley."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3215"
msgstr ""
"I have found the body of the fallen Sanguine agent, and recovered the signet "
"ring. All that remains is to exit the {$v15} Malaut dungeon, and deliver the "
"ring to Allan the Councillor in Sanguine."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3216"
msgstr ""
"I successfully completed the White Order's dangerous mission, of entering "
"the Malaut stronghold in {$v15}, and recovering the signet ring from "
"Sanguine's fallen agent. The ring has been delivered to Allan the Councillor "
"in Sanguine."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3218"
msgstr ""
"No enemy of Morak can hide form the Defenders of the Swamp, especially if "
"the enemy ai a group of traitorous orks. I have killed  four Ork Warmongers "
"as instructed by Bigclubs Trollmangler."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3220"
msgstr ""
"I have found the Book of Malaut within the Malaut stronghold in the {$v15} "
"dungeon. All that remains is to bring it to Bigclubs Trollmangler in "
"Swampton, before the Malaut worshiper it is missing."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3221"
msgstr ""
"The Book of Malaut is now in the possession of the Defenders of the Swamp, "
"after successfully stealing it from the Malaut dungeon in {$v15}. Soon the "
"Defenders of the Swamp will send agents to attack the Malaut stronghold, "
"while to Malaut worshipers franticly try to discover what has happened."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3223"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with  Amhard the Arcanist, to assist her with her "
"work."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3225"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered units of Putrid Corpseflesh for Amhard the Arcanist of the "
"Defenders of the Swamp."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3227"
msgstr ""
"I have found an idol representing some unknown god, that match the "
"descriptions given to me by Bigork Blacktongue. All that remains is to bring "
"the idol to Bigork Blacktongue."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3228"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully found the idol of the unknown lesser god, as demanded by "
"the Fire Dragon."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3230"
msgstr ""
"While ending the life of the third goblin warlord as instructed by Bigork "
"Blacktongue, I discovered a letter with orders sent to the warlords. This "
"letter could reveal information on who is commanding the warlords. I must "
"bring this find to Bigork Blacktongue."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3231"
msgstr ""
"Not only did I kill four Goblin Warlords as instructed by Bigork "
"Blacktongue, but I also discovered a letter with orders  in their "
"possessions. A letter that will reveal who is truly commanding the Goblin "
"Warlord, and the goblin hordes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3233"
msgstr ""
"While Dragonbound agents are searching for any signs of the legendary "
"hobgoblin Raven Standard Army, it seems they have decided to attack all "
"hobgoblins found within Morak. I killed four  hobgoblins that were fortified "
"in {$v11}, as instructed by the Dragonbound."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3235"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Marganak the Arcanist, to help gather "
"important materials that are use for creating magical items."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3237"
msgstr ""
"I gathered and delivered three Tainted Hearts to Marganak the Arcanist. The "
"Tainted Hearts had been requested by one of the Dragonbound enchanters, as "
"one of the materials to be used to create magical items."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3239"
msgstr ""
"I gathered more of the materials that the Dragonbound enchanters have "
"requested, this time two Foul Venom Sacs, which I delivered to Marganak the "
"Arcanist."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3241"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with the Dragonbound agent Bigork Blacktongue in "
"{$x13}, where I will be receiving my next Dragonbound assignments."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3243"
msgstr ""
"Six bonecrew pirates killed, as instructed by Bigaks Stonesmasher. According "
"to Bigaks, these undead pirates had decided to built camps along the eastern "
"shores of Morak, something not tolerated by the Dragonbound or Flaming Skull."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3245"
msgstr ""
"Attack the orks of Morak, and die. The same applies for the gray orks. And "
"although related to the surface ork of Morak, the gray orks had crossed the "
"line. Bigaks Stonesmasher instructed me to kill three gray orks, for "
"attacking caravans and raiding the outer villages."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3247"
msgstr ""
"I have found the Horn of Pain, one of the three parts of the Spear of "
"Darkness. All the remains to complete this mission, is to deliver the Horn "
"of Pain to Bigork Blacktongue in Emberhall."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3248"
msgstr ""
"The Horn of Pain has been delivered to Bigork Blacktongue in Emberhall. "
"Although the Horn of Pain is only one of the three parts of the Spear of "
"Darkness, Bigork could not hide his joy while holding it tight in his hands."

msgid "diary_text_quest_325"
msgstr ""
"Arngard the Councillor was pleased to hear about the four goblins I killed. "
"Apparently the goblins which reside in the mountains, have migrated down "
"from their mountain and begun creating problems for the local communities "
"near Hammerdelve."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3250"
msgstr ""
"I killed four Ogres and two Hill Giants that were roaming the region of "
"{$x14}, before they would decide to move west and begin attacking the "
"villages of  New Flayed Elf and Metal Heart."

msgid "diary_text_quest_327"
msgstr ""
"According to Arngard the Councillor, the majority of goblins are not smart "
"enough to craft any weapons. By looting the axes from the fallen goblins "
"before others can retrieve them, we are in fact disarming the goblins. I "
"managed to loot two goblin axes from the dead goblins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_329"
msgstr ""
"One of the tasks that Tordar needed help with was the gathering of stone, "
"which will be used as the primary building material for the new guard houses "
"in Hammerdelve. I successfully gathered five units of stone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3294"
msgstr ""
"I completed Tialanta the Fighter's challenge, and gained the my first "
"strength achievement title, the title of The Brawny."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3296"
msgstr ""
"I traveled to Dulguna to meet Akamush the Fighter, to compete for more "
"strength achievement titles."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3298"
msgstr ""
"I have gained the achievement title of The Muscular, after completing the "
"task given to me by Akamush the Fighter."

msgid "diary_text_quest_33"
msgstr ""
"William the Councillor was pleased to hear about the four goblins I killed. "
"Apparently the goblins which reside in the badlands to the north, have grown "
"aggressive and begun raiding the local farms near Sandbrook."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3300"
msgstr ""
"The title of The Strong, the third of the strength achievement titles is now "
"mine."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3302"
msgstr ""
"I successfully passed Ensharra the Councillor's trial, and claimed the "
"achievement title of The Limber."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3304"
msgstr ""
"Ensharra the Councillor suggested that I report to Nathar Blackorb of the "
"Temple of the God King in Sorgom, to be tested for more dexterity "
"achievement titles."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3306"
msgstr ""
"I have been rewarded with the achievement title of The Agile, the second of "
"the dexterity achievement titles, after completing Nathar Blackorb's "
"challenge."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3308"
msgstr ""
"The third of the dexterity achievement titles has been claimed, that of The "
"Dextrous."

msgid "diary_text_quest_331"
msgstr ""
"Timber is the basic building material needed for the construction of the "
"guard towers along the trade routes from Hammerdelve to Ymir's Tear and "
"Frostgap. I did my part and gathered five units of timber as requested by "
"Tordar the Blacksmith."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3310"
msgstr ""
"After completing Kalrash the Arcanist's challenge, I gained the the first of "
"the vitality achievement titles, the title of The Stout."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3312"
msgstr ""
"I reported to Haneksur the Arcanist in Sorgom, where I may be able to attain "
"more vitality achievement titles."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3314"
