msgid "diary_text_quest_3575"
msgstr ""
"After gaining the first of the intelligence achievement title from Foulgar "
"the Mage, I traveled to Dragrenoth where more titles are waiting to be given "
"out by Agdarul the Mage of the Dragonbound."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3577"
msgstr ""
"Agdarul the Mage rewarded me with the title of The Sharp, the second of the "
"intelligence achievement titles."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3579"
msgstr ""
"Agdarul the Mage was impressed to see me complete the challenge, and handed "
"me the third of the intelligence achievement titles, the title of The Smart."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3581"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Reiknir the Merchant, to assist with the "
"strange issue of the bear attacks along the trading routes near {$p11}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3583"
msgstr ""
"I managed to local a group of brown bears, and kill three as instructed by "
"Reiknir the Merchant. I'm not sure if these were the same brown bears "
"responsible for the attacks upon the trading caravans in {$p11}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3585"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Argok the Merchant, to assist with the strange "
"issue of the bear attacks along the trading routes near {$u15}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3587"
msgstr ""
"I managed to local a group of brown bears, and kill three as instructed by "
"Argok the Merchant. Neither I or Argok were sure if these were the same "
"brown bears responsible for the attacks upon the trading caravans in {$u15}. "
"It seems that killing any bears would do, as long as it kept the merchants "
"pleased."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3589"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Omar the Merchant, to assist with the strange "
"issue of bear attacks along the trading routes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_359"
msgstr ""
"Alvmund the Blacksmith had requested of all to gather enough timber for the "
"construction of guard towers. After the goblin attacks, it was obvious that "
"Valfather's Edge's defenses along the trade routes needed something more."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3591"
msgstr ""
"I managed to locate a group of brown bears, and kill three as instructed by "
"Omar the Merchant. I wasn't sure if these were the same bears that had been "
"attacking the trading routes, but killing any bears seemed to please the "
"damaged merchants."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3593"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Srilanda the Merchant, to assist with the "
"strange issue of bear attacks along the trading routes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3595"
msgstr ""
"I managed to local a group of brown bears, and kill three as instructed by "
"Srilanda the Merchant. Srilanda didn't really seem to care, if I had killed "
"the same bears that were attacking the merchants. Any bears would do fine, "
"just as long as it kept the merchants happy."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3597"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Anith the Merchant, to assist with the strange "
"issue of the bear attacks along the trading routes near {$j19}."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3599"
msgstr ""
"I managed to locate a group of brown bears, and kill three as instructed by "
"Anith the Merchant. Neither I or Anith were sure if these were the same "
"brown bears responsible for the attacks upon the trading caravans near "
"{$j19}. It seems that killing any bears would do, as long as it kept the "
"merchants pleased."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3601"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Moarlon the Merchant, to assist with the "
"strange issue of the bear attacks along the trading routes near Amurranyr."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3603"
msgstr ""
"I managed to locate a group of brown bears, and kill three as instructed by "
"Moarlon the Merchant. Neither I or Moarlon were sure if these were the same "
"brown bears that have been attacking the merchant caravans near {$j19}. It "
"seems that killing any bears would do, as long as it kept the merchants "
"pleased."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3606"
msgstr ""
"I have completed the Longclaw's first expedition to the ice continent of "
"Niflheim, and engaged the  Snowclan Dwarves. After battling the Snowclan "
"Dwarves, and killing three of them, I returned to  Yaleria-sai, and "
"delivered my full assessment for their strengths and weaknesses. The "
"Snowclan Dwarves are very dangerous."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3608"
msgstr ""
"I agreed to assist Katila the Arcanist and Samalon-tai the Mage,complete the "
"deciphering of an ancient scroll, by gathering to unit of Elemental Quartz."

msgid "diary_text_quest_361"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered five units of mandrake to Yngfell the Arcanist in "
"Valfather's Edge. Mandrake is to be used by our spellcasters against the "
"goblin hordes."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3610"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered a pacakage to Salaman-tai the Mage, that Katila the "
"Arcanist had prepared for him. Inside it are all the ingredients that "
"Samalon-tai needs, to complete the deciphering of the ancient scroll."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3612"
msgstr ""
"I have located the fallen mahirim scholar within the Larethain dungeon, and "
"retrieved the scholar's diary. All that remains is to deliver the diary to "
"Samalon-tai in Moonclaw."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3613"
msgstr ""
"The diary of the fallen mahirim scholar I located in {$j13} dungeon, has "
"been handed to Samalon-tai of the Circle of Neith. Although a strong "
"character, Samalon-tai could not hide his sadness."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3615"
msgstr ""
"I have successfully activated the first guardian statue, the King, by "
"casting a mana missile. Now I must battle the Defender, the second guardian, "
"in my quest to locate the Demon Ring."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3616"
msgstr ""
"I have battled the second guardian statue, the Defender, and am one step "
"closer to finding the Demon Ring. Now I must find for the Scholar, and drain "
"him of his power."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3617"
msgstr ""
"I have beaten the last of the guardians of the Demon Ring, the Scholar, by "
"casting a mana drain spell upon him, and therefor draining him of his power. "
"Now all that remains, is to return to the King before thirty minutes have "
"passed, and the ring will be mine."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3618"
msgstr ""
"I have retrieved the Demon Ring from the King, the first of the guardian "
"statues, after successfully passing all the guardians trials. All that "
"remains is to deliver the Demon Ring to Samalon-tai in Moonclaw."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3619"
msgstr ""
"The Demon Ring has been found and delivered to Samalon-tai the Mage of the "
"Circle of Neith. A powerful but dangerous artifact, not one that anybody can "
"posses. It will be a while until the Circle of Neith, will truly understated "
"the Demon Ring's powers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3621"
msgstr ""
"I have found the Book of Heroes, inside the sarcophagus in {$i16} dungeon, "
"just as Symyr-dan the Firm described it to me. Now all that remains, is to "
"return the book to the Symyr-dan the Firm, and to mahirim people."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3622"
msgstr ""
"The heroes have returned home. The Book of Heroes is now in the possession "
"of the Elders of Red Moon, and the names and acts of all the brave mahirim "
"heroes, will be known to all. The mahirim a truly a proud race."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3624"
msgstr ""
"Three arthain have been removed from the ancient site in {$f15}, as "
"instructed by Symyr-dan of the Elders of Red Moon. Now the Elders may begin "
"their exploration of the ancient ruins."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3626"
msgstr ""
"I have reported for duty with Naticia the Mage of the Elder of the Red Moon. "
"I am to assist her gather information about the new creatures that have "
"recently migrated into the surrounding lands."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3628"
msgstr ""
"I gathered three unit of Greenleaf from the Sarnakh, to assist Naticia the "
"Mage in her work to learn more about these strange creatures."

msgid "diary_text_quest_363"
msgstr ""
"I have extracted four teeth from the slain goblins in Valfather's Edge. It "
"seems that teeth are one of the many materials that can by used in the art "
"of imbuing items with magical properties."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3630"
msgstr ""
"Brownies have to be one of the smallest, if not smallest creatures I have "
"encounters. Unfortunately for the tiny Brownies, I had to harvest their "
"bodies for Cloudy Quartz, to assist Naticia the Mage with her research."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3632"
msgstr ""
"Why some soul cannot be put to rest, will always be a mystery. Unfortunately "
"for these souls, some seem to have something that many mages desire. Such as "
"the Ghosts and Elfshades in {$i15}, which I harvested their ghostly bodies "
"for Ghostly Darktaint, as instructed by Naticia the Mage."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3634"
msgstr ""
"I have traveled to the rogue city Hintenfau, to meet with the human called "
"Sister Lyrissa. Apparently this human has valuable information that the "
"Wolfmasks seek."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3636"
msgstr ""
"I have found the list of name that Sister Lyrissa has requested, in exchange "
"for the information Mardem-kai seeks. All that remains is to deliver the "
"list to Sister Lyrissa in Hintenfau."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3637"
msgstr ""
"Sister Lyrissa was very please to hold the List of Names I stole for her, "
"from {$i11} dungeon. She even spoke about some kind of revenge. Must be a "
"list with very important name I guess."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3639"
msgstr ""
"Sister Lyrissa kept her word, and handed me all the information that Marden-"
"kai had requested. It seems that although it is as the Woflmasks had "
"suspected, that the Cult of the Moon-Beast is behind the humans attacks with "
"the Tribelands, there is a new darker power, behind the cult. A new power "
"that has emerged in the heart of the central plains, the so called Dark Lord."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3641"
msgstr ""
"I have discovered a strange weather-torn tombstone, with strange symbols "
"carved upon it, located in the center of the cultist village in {$m12}. "
"Could this be a possible connection between the cult and the Dark Lord of "
"the central plains? I have copied the symbols on a piece of parchment. Now I "
"must report this find to Mardem-kai the Loyal."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3642"
msgstr ""
"I have returned to Nightspire and handed to Mardem-kai the piece of "
"parchment with the strange symbols I discovered upon the tombstone in the "
"cultist village in {$m12}. Now, it is for Mardem-kai to decide what to do "
"with them."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3644"
msgstr ""
"As Mardem-kai said, enough with the Cult of the Moon-Beast. They somehow "
"seem to be involved with all the problems that occur within the Tribelands. "
"Mardem-kai instructed me to kill ten members of the Cult of the Moon-Beast "
"within three hours, something I gladly accepted."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3646"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered Mardem-kai's detailed report letter to Tivasta the "
"Councillor in Red Moon. From what Mardem-kai explained to me, it is a full "
"report about the human activities within the Tribelands, the Cult of the "
"Moon-Beast, but mostly about the Dark Lord of the central plains."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3648"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered three units of Cloudy Quartz for Seirinna the Mage. "
"According to the notes left behind by the powerful mage Siledin, Cloudy "
"Quartz is one of the materials needed to destroy the Orb of Disease."

msgid "diary_text_quest_365"
msgstr ""
"Swords and bows may be good against the goblins, but magic also has its "
"benefits. I was given the opportunity by Hrafnid the Councillor to cast "
"twenty mana missile against the goblins that were attacking Valfather's "
"Edge. It would seem that the goblins, like many of the monsters of Agon, "
"have an innate fear of magic and this is something that we must take full "
"advantage of."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3650"
msgstr ""
"As requested by Seirinna the Mage, I collected three units of Caustic Bile. "
"The Caustic Bile is one of the materials needed to cast the powerful spell "
"that will destroy the Orb of Disease."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3652"
msgstr ""
"I gathered two units of Gloomy Darktaint for Seirinna the Mage. Gloomy "
"Darktaint is the final ingredient that is needed for the spell that will "
"destroy the Orb of Disease."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3654"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered the Orb of Disease to the Serene Spire in Iriendir, "
"together with all the materials and notes needed for its destruction. "
"Aelathil Silverleaf who I handed the package to, insured me that the Serene "
"Spire will do all it can to destroy the foul orb."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3656"
msgstr ""
"I found the missing Arrowhead agent Annabell Lightheart in the Ciel Fey "
"village in {$l17}, but unfortunately too late. She was already dead, and "
"from what I could tell, brutally tortured. I have managed to retrieve her "
"Arrowhead signet ring, which I shall return to Eredethil Swiftarrow in "
"Krisathel, together with the dire news of her death."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3657"
msgstr ""
"Eredethil's fears were confirmed, as I handed him the Arrowhead signet ring "
"that once belonged to Annabell Lightheart, together with the awful news of "
"her horrid death."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3659"
msgstr ""
"I located one of the so called demonic tombstones within the beastman "
"village in {$l18}. At first it seemed like an simple old tombstone, but upon "
"closer inspection I discovered strange symbols carved upon it. I copied the "
"symbols onto a piece of parchment, and gave it to Eredethil Swiftarrow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3661"
msgstr ""
"I have delivered a copy of the ancient demonic writings found on the "
"tombstone in the beastman village in {$l18}, to Nairath the Mage in "
"Charybdis. According to Eredethil Swiftarrow, Nairath the Mage is an expert "
"in deciphering ancient texts."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3663"
msgstr ""
"While Nairath the Mage studies the demonic symbols from the strange "
"tombstone I brought to him earlier, I accepted to travel to Imathir to "
"retrieve one of his books that Riathen the Mage has forgotten to return to "
"him."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3665"
msgstr ""
"Nairath the Mage was pleased to when I returned his book that Riathen had "
"borrowed from him, and had forgotten to return."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3667"
msgstr ""
"Nairath the Mage completed the deciphering of the demonic writing, and the "
"news was not good. He talked about the coming of the Dark Lord, possibly a "
"powerful demon, one that will conquer all of Agon. After that, I delivered a "
"letter to Eredathil Swiftarrow at the Arrowhead headquarters in Krisathel, a "
"letter written by Nairath. The letter contained in detail all the bad news "
"Nairath had discovered, from deciphering the demonic symbols and writings."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3669"
msgstr ""
"I have traveled to Hintenfau to speak with Sister Lyrissa, in the hopes of "
"acquiring any useful information about the Dark Lord."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3671"
msgstr ""
"I accepted to do Sister Lyrissa's dirty work, in exchange for acquiring "
"later on the information that I seek about the Dark Lord. I traveled to the "
"small town of Serpenton, and killed three Shroud Knight."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3672"
msgstr ""
"A strange fire pillar within the once powerful severii stronghold in {$j23} "
"has been discovered, possibly responsible for the appearance of the fire "
"creatures withing the severii fortress. Hanthar Blackfrost was puzzled about "
"this find. Could the skeleton dragon god Cyriacus be recruiting new allies?"

msgid "diary_text_quest_3674"
msgstr ""
"I found Ninnah's missing apprentice, but unfortunately too late. The "
"apprentice was already dead. What i did find was the apprentice's diary, "
"which I must now return to Ninnah the Mage in Shoal."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3675"
msgstr ""
"After recovering the diary from the body of the Ninnah's dead apprentice in "
"{$p22}, I return to Shoal and delivered the diary to Ninnah."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3677"
msgstr ""
"Ninnah the Mage has completed the deciphering of the demonic text, and the "
"news is not good. She talks about the coming of a Dark Demon Lord, one that "
"will conquer all of Agon. I delivered Ninnah's letter to Aeshanta Darkspire "
"of the Harn Mandean, with all that Ninnah has discovered from the demonic "
"writings."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3679"
msgstr ""
"I have traveled to Hindefau to meet Sister Lyrissa, hoping to learn any "
"useful information about the Dark Lord."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3681"
msgstr ""
"I have located Sister Lyrissa's magic box in the Ciel Fey village in {$n17}. "
"Now I must return it to Sister Lyrissa, if I am to collect any information "
"she might have on the Dark Lord."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3682"
msgstr ""
"I returned to Hintefau and delivered to Sister Lyrissa her stolen magical "
"box. Now I must wait and see if she will give me any information she might "
"have about the Dark Lord."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3684"
msgstr ""
"Sister Lyrissa kept her word, and handed me a letter with all the "
"information she and her men had gathered about the Dark Lord. I have "
"returned to Dulguna, and delivered the letter to Aeshanta Darkspire."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3686"
msgstr ""
"In my quest to find the hidden artifact in {$p22}, I successfully activated "
"the Nithron Scholar statue, as Ninnah instructed me, by blasting him with "
"five mana missiles. Now the Scholar demands I bring him five of each that a "
"spellcaster might need."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3687"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered and delivered all that the Scholar asked for. Now I must "
"search for the Shrine of the Dragons, and drain it of its power. Only then "
"will it be revealed to me who is the keeper of the rod."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3688"
msgstr ""
"After draining the Shrine of the Dragons of its power, it has been reveal to "
"me that the keeper of the rod is he who faces the golden spire."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3689"
msgstr ""
"I have found the keeper of the rod, and retrieved the Rod of Dragon Fire. "
"All that remains is to return to Shoal, and deliver the rod to Ninnah the "
"Mage."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3690"
msgstr ""
"I located the Rod of Dragon Fire in {$p22}, through a series of riddles. "
"Ninnah the Mage was surprised by the existence of the rod, since the search "
"was based on the notes left behind by her now dead apprentice."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3692"
msgstr ""
"I have executed the first step of many written by Ninnah the Mage, in "
"possibly disabling the powers of the demon tombstone, by placing seven units "
"of sulfur and seven units of resin upon the demon tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3693"
msgstr ""
"The second step in disabling the demon tombstone has been executed. The rend "
"has been cast upon the tombstone, which should bring out and expose the "
"tombstone's powers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3694"
msgstr ""
"Step three in disabling the tombstone is completed. Seven units of blood, "
"five bones and one heart have been placed upon the demon tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3695"
msgstr ""
"Step four completed. The Flesh Curse spell did its work and had definitely "
"weakened the powers of the tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3696"
msgstr ""
"Ten units of ash have been placed upon the demon tombstone, to complete the "
"fifth step in disabling the magical properties of the demon tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3697"
msgstr ""
"After casting the Mana Drain spell upon the demon tombstone, the sixth and "
"final step, the tombstone has been successfully disabled. I returned to "
"Aeshanta Darkspire in Dulguna, and reported our success in disabling the "
"powers of the demon tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3700"
msgstr ""
"Sister Lyrissa kept her word, and handed me a letter with all the "
"information she and her men had gathered about the Dark Lord. I returned to "
"Krisathel, and handed the letter to Eredathil Swiftarrow."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3702"
msgstr ""
"I have executed the first of many steps written by Nairath the Mage, in "
"disabling the powers of the demon tombstone. Seven units of sulfur and seven "
"units of resin have been placed upon the demon tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3703"
msgstr ""
"The second step in disabling the demon tombstone has been executed. The rend "
"has been cast upon the tombstone, which should bring out and expose the "
"tombstone's powers."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3704"
msgstr ""
"Step three in disabling the tombstone is complete. Seven units of blood, "
"five bones and one heart have been placed upon the demon tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3705"
msgstr ""
"Step four completed. The Flesh Curse spell did its work and had definitely "
"weakened the powers of the tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3706"
msgstr ""
"Ten units of ash have been placed upon the demon tombstone, to complete the "
"fifth step in disabling the magical properties of the demon tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3707"
msgstr ""
"After casting the mana drain spell upon the demon tombstone, the sixth and "
"final step, the tombstone has been successfully disabled. I returned to "
"Eredathil Swiftarrow in Krisathel, and reported our success in disabling the "
"powers of the demon tombstone."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3709"
msgstr ""
"It seems that I have completed all of Tialanta's trails, with this last one, "
"the killing of five Dwarven player characters in less than five hours."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3711"
msgstr ""
"I gathered six units of meat for Thora the Merchant, who is in charge of "
"organizing the hunters in Sandbrook. Thora was pleased with my performance, "
"and has offered to reward me each time I accept to hunt twelve units of meat "
"for her. Not bad."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3713"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered and delivered five shortbows and twenty arrows to Catherine "
"the Fighter. These bows and arrows will be used for training Sandbrook's new "
"archers by Catherine the Fighter. Sandrook has learned a lot from the goblin "
"attacks."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3715"
msgstr ""
"I accepted to have my archery skills put to the test by Catherine the "
"Fighter. I succeeded in hitting the goblins twenty times with my arrows, and "
"of course collected my reward from Catherine."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3717"
msgstr ""
"I have taken part in the organized meat hunt in Monkfield, and delivered six "
"units of meat to Siemon the Merchant who was responsible for organizing the "
"hunt. Simeon has offered to reward me each time I accept to hunt six units "
"of meat for her."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3719"
msgstr ""
"Five shortbows and twenty arrows have been delivered to Torgard the Fighter. "
"Torgard will need as much equipment as possible, to properly train the new "
"archers in Sanguine."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3721"
msgstr ""
"Torgard the Fighter challenged me, to score twenty successful hits against "
"the goblins only by using archery. A challenge I gladly accepted, and "
"successfully passed."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3723"
msgstr ""
"I have taken part in the annual meat hunt in Heart of Eanna, and "
"successfully gathered six units of meat for Isabel the Merchant. I must have "
"done well, since Isabel has offered to reward me each time I accept to hunt "
"twelve units of meat for her."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3725"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered five shortbows and twenty arrows for Kai the Fighter. Kai "
"the Fighter is training Heart of Eanna's young archers, and will need plenty "
"of bows and arrows to complete their training."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3727"
msgstr ""
"I managed to score twenty successful hits against the goblins only by using "
"archery. This was the challenge put to me by Kai the Fighter."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3729"
msgstr ""
"I gathered six units of meat for Talduk the Merchant, who is in charge of "
"organizing the hunters in Akathos. Talduk was pleased with my performance, "
"and has offered to reward me each time I accept to hunt twelve units of meat "
"for him. Not bad."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3731"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered and delivered five shortbows and twenty arrows to Gaelshek "
"the Fighter. These bows and arrows will be used for training Akathos's new "
"archers by Gaelshek the Fighter."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3733"
msgstr ""
"I accepted to have my archery skills put to the test by Gaelshek the "
"Fighter. I succeeded in hitting the goblins twenty times with my arrows, and "
"of course collected my reward from Gaelshek."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3735"
msgstr ""
"I have taken part in the organized meat hunt in Onghral, and delivered six "
"units of meat to Arinthu the Merchant who was responsible for organizing the "
"hunt. Arinthu has offered to reward me each time I accept to hunt twelve "
"units of meat for him."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3737"
msgstr ""
"Five shortbows and twenty arrows have been delivered to Zulgal the Fighter. "
"Zulgal will need as much equipment as possible, if he is to train Onghral's "
"young warriors."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3739"
msgstr ""
"Zulgal the Fighter challenged me, to score twenty successful hits against "
"the goblins only by using archery. A challenge I gladly accepted, and "
"successfully passed."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3741"
msgstr ""
"I have taken part in the annual meat hunt in Deep Yishku, and successfully "
"gathered six units of meat for Kaelit the Merchant. I must have done well, "
"since Kaelit has offered to reward me each time I accept to hunt twelve "
"units of meat for her."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3743"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered five shortbows and twenty arrows to Raenthar the Fighter. "
"Raenthar the Fighter is training Deep Yishku's young archers, and will need "
"plenty of bows and arrows to complete their training."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3745"
msgstr ""
"I managed to score twenty successful hits against the goblins only by using "
"archery. This was the challenge put to me by Raenthar the Fighter."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3747"
msgstr ""
"I gathered six units of meat for Miradan the Merchant, who is in charge of "
"organizing the hunters in Beladin's Rest. Miradan was pleased with my "
"performance, and has offered to reward me each time I accept to hunt twelve "
"units of meat for her. Not bad."

msgid "diary_text_quest_3749"
msgstr ""
"I have gathered and delivered five shortbows and twenty arrows to Delian the "
"Fighter. These bows and arrows will be used for training Beladin's Rest's "
"new archers by Delian the Fighter."

