msgid "end_text_quest_236"
msgstr ""
"That was quite easy, wasn't it? Goblins are pathetic little creatures, and "
"no match for a fully grown ork."

msgid "end_text_quest_2369"
msgstr "Welcome to {$t18} Abbey, traveler."

msgid "end_text_quest_2370"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for helping us contain the goblin outbreak. Thanks to the efforts "
"of adventurers such as yourself, we are now slowly getting the situation "
"under control."

msgid "end_text_quest_2371"
msgstr ""
"Without the magic wielded by those shamans, the local goblins will be easier "
