"definitely proven you loyalty to the alliance, and surely made your race "
"proud. Here, accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2914"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. I am Sylanae the Councillor. I am glad my dear friend Allan the "
"Councillor has send help in these troublesome times."

msgid "end_text_quest_2916"
msgstr ""
