"definitely proven you loyalty to the alliance, and surely made your race "
"proud. Here, accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2922"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. I am Tivasta the Councillor. I am glad our allies the orks have "
"answered our call in these troublesome times."

msgid "end_text_quest_2924"
msgstr ""
"Excellent, I see you have returned victorious. #PlayerName#, you have "
"definitely proven you loyalty to the alliance, and surely made your race "
"proud. Here, accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2926"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. I am Izkruul the Councillor. I am glad our allies the mahirim have "
"answered our call in these difficult times."

msgid "end_text_quest_2929"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Truly you are a strong and powerful ork. I as a mahirim, am "
"pleased to have the orks as our allies. #PlayerName#, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2931"
msgstr ""
"Impressive. You have proven yourself once more #PlayerName#. You truly are a "
"capable warrior, and a vital part to our alliance. I am pleased the the "
"mahrim are our allies. Here, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2933"
msgstr ""
"Excellent, I see you have returned victorious. #PlayerName#, you have "
"definitely proven you loyalty to the alliance, and surely made your race "
"proud. Here, accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2934"
msgstr ""
"Yes? Hmmm, a orders from the Radiant Circle. Hmmm, I see. So it is the "
"legend of the demon hand this time."

msgid "end_text_quest_2936"
msgstr ""
"You have done well. If those Windlords ever mess with any of our patrols "
"again, I'll just burn them all to the ground."

msgid "end_text_quest_2939"
msgstr ""
"I see you have returned. Could this be the legendary Demon Hand the Radiant "
"Circle so desires?"

msgid "end_text_quest_2941"
msgstr ""
"This is it! The legendary Demon's Hand! The power within it, I... I can feel "
"it. #PlayerName#, you have done well. Accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2943"
msgstr ""
"So my friend, we meet again. What is this? Orders from Shoal to punish the "
"traitorous Melechar! Yes, long have I been waiting for this!"

msgid "end_text_quest_2945"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have performed well. Once more you have proven your worth to "
"the Temple of the God King. Here, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2948"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. Without the holy symbol in their possession, the Melechar "
"have nothing  to connect them to Melek. Now they will underastand, that they "
"are no longer in the favor of Melek."

msgid "end_text_quest_2950"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName#, once again you have successfully completed your mission. I am "
"pleased to hear that the Melechar have been punished. Here is your well "
"earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2952"
msgstr ""
"What is this? Ancient texts of unknown origin. #PlayerName#, you have done "
"well bringing to us this find. We will need help in deciphering these texts. "
"Here, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2954"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. I see you have successfully completed your mission. Accept this "
"reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2956"
msgstr ""
"Greetings. What is this? Some kind of ancient writings. Very interesting. I "
"will try to decipher it. The Harn Mandean has done well bring this to our "
"attention."

msgid "end_text_quest_2958"
msgstr ""
"I see you have returned with the elemental cinders. Your timing could not "
"have been any better. Now, we are able to complete the deciphering of the "
"demonic writings."

msgid "end_text_quest_2960"
msgstr ""
"Yes? What is this? A letter from Ninnah. So, Shoal asking for me help. Hmmm, "
"I might help you, but only if you do something for me first."

msgid "end_text_quest_2962"
msgstr ""
"Well done. I can see why Ninnah chose you for this mission. Here is "
"something for your effort."

msgid "end_text_quest_2964"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have managed to retrieve a copy of the demonic writings from "
"Ninseri in Espenhal. I will immediately begin deciphering these demonic "
"writings, and see what else I may discover about this new unknown powerful "
"figure which has risen within the central plains. #PlayerName#, you have "
"done well. Accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2967"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Truly, the Shadow Masters will be most pleased with you. Here, "
"accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2969"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. I am Elena the Mage, and you must be #PlayerName#, the one that "
"found the Dragontorc. I say, I am impressed."

msgid "end_text_quest_2971"
msgstr ""
"I see… It seems that the oathbound are quite formidable. If the trickle of "
"these creatures becomes a flood, the Mercian army will have a serious "
"problem on his hands. We must research further to be as prepared as possible "
"for this eventuality."

msgid "end_text_quest_2974"
msgstr ""
"Magnificent! Equipped with a complete copy of the Chronicles, we should be "
"able to learn more about the artifacts you have brought us."

msgid "end_text_quest_2976"
msgstr ""
"A report from the Sons of Riada, you say. Most interesting. I will read "
"through it, and present it to the king should it prove to be of interest."

msgid "end_text_quest_2978"
msgstr ""
"So, you are #PlayerName#. I have read the reports from the Knight of "
"Malregard, and I must admit, I am impressed. I am sure will be of great help "
"in our battle against Malaut and his so called Twilight Kingdom."

msgid "end_text_quest_2981"
msgstr ""
"This is it. The unholy book of Malaut. Although is pains me to bring such a "
"dark and evil item into Sanguine, it is vital that we gain knowledge of our "
"enemy, if we are to destroy them. #PlayerName# you have been of great "
"service to Sanguine and all Mercians. Here, please do accept this well "
"earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2983"
msgstr ""
"Ah, you say my dear friend Maria Hawksgate has sent you. May the light of "
"Auros bless you both."

msgid "end_text_quest_2985"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful. Thank you for driving those filthy orks out of our lands. Please "
"accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2987"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName# you have done well. With brave heroes like yourself, it is a "
"matter of time to return Highmoore into the guiding light of Auros."

msgid "end_text_quest_2989"
msgstr "Yes? Ah, at last a little help to deal with these annoying centaurs."

msgid "end_text_quest_2991"
msgstr ""
"You have done well. Until we discover the source of the centaurs madness, we "
"will have to stop their rage with any means possible. Here, accept this "
"reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2993"
msgstr ""
"I see. Aurmon will continue to monitor this unusual behavior of the "
"centaurs, until we discover the cause of this madness."

msgid "end_text_quest_2995"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have gathered all the proof we need, that these Lesser Fire "
"Elemental do exist. The Circle of Neith will be pleased to hear about this."

msgid "end_text_quest_2997"
msgstr ""
"Elemental Cinder, from the elusive Lesser Fire Elemental. Wonderful, is "
"seems we will be able to decipher this ancient scroll. Here, please accept "
"this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_2999"
msgstr ""
"We will have to keep an eye out, if anymore of these Bonecrew return. "
"Keeping Fang Lake clear is vital to all of us. Here is the reward I had "
"promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3001"
msgstr ""
"You have done well. We will cut off all means of communication between the "
"human bandits and their leaders. We will force them to panic and make "
"mistakes, and then we will crush them."

msgid "end_text_quest_3003"
msgstr ""
"So, it would seem that these Gray Orks do possess some strength. You have "
"done well. Accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3005"
msgstr ""
"Ah, you must be #PlayerName#. Yes. On behalf of Red Moon I thank you for "
"recovering the lost half of the sacred stone tablet."

msgid "end_text_quest_3007"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName#, I thank you. You have been of great service to Red Moon. We "
"will do all we can to restore Larren-Tai's name, and inspire all mahirim "
"with the story of this faithful guardian. Larren-Tai's name will not be lost "
"or forgotten."

msgid "end_text_quest_3009"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful. You have managed to bring us a Tribal Lifeforce. Yes, you have "
"done well. Please accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3011"
msgstr ""
"Greeting. I see my report regarding the elusive Akathars has reached the "
"Circle of Neith.."

msgid "end_text_quest_3013"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. I see you have returned with the Wind Shadowcrest. Here, please "
"accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3016"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful. You have found Siritos's life's work into the time of Bad Magic. "
"The Book of Bad Magic. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3018"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. We will continue our efforts in cleaning Inarith of its many "
"undead. Please, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3020"
msgstr ""
"So, you have encounters the gray ork mercenaries, and managed to kill four "
"of them. Yes, you have lived up to your reputation #PlayerName#. The Emerald "
"Throne ranks you amount its best agents, and I can see why."

msgid "end_text_quest_3022"
msgstr "I thank you. You have done well. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3024"
msgstr ""
"So, melechar are using the Baradron dungeon are a hideout. This is most "
"worrying. I will send a report to Charybdis. You have done well. Accept this "
"reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3026"
msgstr ""
"Ah, I see that the Arrowhead have also discovered another melechar hideout. "
"This is not good news. We must discover why have the melechar chosen to move "
"near Mirendil. Still, I thank you for delivering this information to us. "
"There is much to be done."

msgid "end_text_quest_3028"
msgstr ""
"The melechar must be stopped at any cost. We cannot allow them to carry out "
"whatever evil plans they might be preparing."

msgid "end_text_quest_3031"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. #PlayerName#, you have done a great good to us. While the "
"melechar are in disarray and chaos, and try to uncover what has gone wrong "
"with their plans, our agents will launch an attack against all melechar."

msgid "end_text_quest_3033"
msgstr ""
"The crystal green tower you say. Yes, I am aware of it, but why would you "
"want to go there?"

msgid "end_text_quest_3036"
msgstr ""
"The Rod of Bad Magic. Yes, I can feel the power of the artifact, as if the "
"wizard Damanthel is inside it himself. This is very strange indeed. Our "
"researchers will slowly study the hidden powers of this rod. #PlayerName#, "
"accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3038"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. As we speak, a team of researchers is preparing to venture into "
"the Kaerdan dungeons. #PlayerName#, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3040"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful. I see you have successfully gathered three units of Putrid "
"Corpseflesh. Here is the reward I had promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3042"
msgstr ""
"Ah, a little help at last. I thank you. I am Nairath, Nairath the Mage."

msgid "end_text_quest_3044"
msgstr "Wonderful. You have returned with the ingredients I have asked for."

msgid "end_text_quest_3046"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Three Barbed Claw just as I asked for. The last of the "
"ingredients I needed. I hope you enjoyed pulling those claws off those "
"Beastmen. Here is the reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3048"
msgstr ""
"Oh, what is this? A package from Nairath you say. Yes yes, I've been "
"expecting this. Thank you very much."

msgid "end_text_quest_3050"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. I am Kanute Wayfarer. So, the Voice of Ymir have decided it is time "
"to clear out and claim Aegin's Hall."

msgid "end_text_quest_3052"
msgstr ""
"You have proven yourself to be a valuable asset to the Voice of Ymir. Here "
"is your well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3055"
msgstr ""
"So, the ogres had somehow stumbled upon Aegin's legendary scepter? The Voice "
"of Ymir wishes to thank you for finding it and bringing it to Wintercrown."

msgid "end_text_quest_3057"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. I am Nidstein the Mage, and you must be #PlayerName#. Yes, I have "
"heard all about you, and I believe you might help me with something."

msgid "end_text_quest_3060"
msgstr "It is indeed magnificent. Here is the reward I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_3062"
msgstr ""
"I see... in large numbers, these creatures may well pose a threat to "
"Dvergheim's safety. Here is your well-earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3064"
msgstr ""
"If we are to eradicate the Svartdvergir, it is these summoners and their "
"stronghold we need to get rid of. You have done well. Accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3066"
msgstr ""
"The hivekin have become quite aggressive lately, and we could use and help "
"to protect the travelers."

msgid "end_text_quest_3068"
msgstr "Thank you. Your help is most appreciated. Please, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3070"
msgstr "Ah, this is good news. Accept this reward for all you have done."

msgid "end_text_quest_3073"
msgstr ""
"A complete skeleton figure somehow magically floating above a svartdvergir "
"shrine dedicated to Sahul. This is most worrying. We will investigate more "
"closely, and try to discover what exactly it is the svartdvergir are "
"planning."

msgid "end_text_quest_3075"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. I hope our mirdain allies have the same luck dealing with the "
"Gray Orks as you did. Here is the reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3078"
msgstr ""
"Yes, it is as I suspected. These hobgoblin grunts would have never acted on "
"their on. Now we know who is giving out the orders. You have done well. "
"Accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3081"
msgstr ""
"So, this is more complicated than we believed. It has been many years since "
"anybody heard of the Hobgoblins of the Raven Standard. You have done well in "
"discovering this information. Ymir's Tear must be informed immediately."

msgid "end_text_quest_3083"
msgstr ""
"According to your report, these Raven Standard Hobgoblin Grunts seem to "
"possess some skills. #PlayerName#, your help has been most valuable to us. "
"Our agents will continue to monitor the Raven Standard camp."

msgid "end_text_quest_3085"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. Ah, so you are one that found Blackpeak's last blade. I'm hoping "
"that you might help me find another item."

msgid "end_text_quest_3088"
msgstr ""
"This is most wonderful news. You have found Durganon's Brazier. I am most "
"please. Now we must find a way to bring it back to Stanevault. #PlayerName#, "
"please accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3090"
msgstr ""
"From the Radiant Circle you say. Yes, about the inhabitants of the Zahnal "
"dungeon. I am pleased I can be of service to the Radiant Circle."

msgid "end_text_quest_3092"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. This is the first step in verifying the existence of these "
"creatures. There is more that is needed to be done, but this will do for "
"now. Here is your well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3094"
msgstr ""
"It would seem that the Nalaeds and the Sarlid Darkweavers are both quite "
"formidable, but if confined to the Zahnal dungeons, I believe that they will "
"pose no threat whatsoever. Here is the reward that was promised to you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3096"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. I am Sriva Ghostweb, and member of the Radiant Circle and in charge "
"of Castle Obad."

msgid "end_text_quest_3098"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful. Our researchers and younger mages can continue to experiment with "
"the art of enchanting. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_31"
msgstr ""
"Great work, I will inform our farmers that they can head back out.  Not sure "
"what sort of weapons and armor you use, but you can craft some from these "
"materials."

msgid "end_text_quest_3100"
msgstr ""
"Ah, how wonderful. Did you enjoy removing the Gloomy Darktaint from the "
"arthain? Of course you did! Here is the reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3102"
msgstr "Yes? So, the time has come to deal with these hobgoblins. Excellent!"

msgid "end_text_quest_3104"
msgstr ""
"Your skills and determination in dealing with the hobgoblins was quite "
"amazing. Yes, I can do with more like you. Here, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3106"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have done well. Death is the only salvation for the Nahdruk. "
"Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3108"
msgstr "You must be #PlayerName#. Let's see what you are really made of."

msgid "end_text_quest_3110"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Did you happen to see Auros anywhere trying to save his beloved "
"humans while you were killing them? No! A pathetic god for a pathetic race. "
"Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3112"
msgstr ""
"Hunting down mirdain, hearing their pathetic screams while watching them "
"slowly die, is always pleasing. You have done well #PlayerName#. Here, "
"accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3114"
msgstr ""
"So, you succeeded in killing four of those beasts in the four hour time "
"limit. Yes, you are good. Very good. Accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3116"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Four less stinking orks, in under four hours. You continue to "
"impress me. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3118"
msgstr "Excellent. A little help from my dear friend Aeshanta Darkspire."

msgid "end_text_quest_3120"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. You do understand that killing these Nahdruk was the correct "
"thing to do? Of course you do. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3122"
msgstr ""
"You have returned with the Mystical Eye I requested. A very rare material "
"indeed. Here is the reward I had promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3124"
msgstr ""
"Very well done #PlayerName#. You have done as I asked of you. Eight "
"Elemental Quartz. Here, accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3126"
msgstr ""
"Ah, a package with enchanting ingredients from out dear friend Hanthar "
"Blackfrost."

msgid "end_text_quest_3128"
msgstr ""
"Hopefully this means that the gnolls will calm down, and I can continue my "
"research without any interruptions."

msgid "end_text_quest_3130"
msgstr ""
"It is an honor to meet you #PlayerName#. I heard of how you dealt with the "
"ork, but I would like to see for myself what you are really made of if you "
"don't mind."

msgid "end_text_quest_3132"
msgstr ""
"Well done. You truly are all they say you are. #PlayerName#, please accept "
"this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3134"
msgstr ""
"So, my dear friend Hildr wants me to put you to the test. Very well, let's "
"see what you can do."

msgid "end_text_quest_3136"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. I see that the orks are no match for you my friend. Here is "
"your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3138"
msgstr ""
