msgid "end_text_quest_3186"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. I thank you for gathering these materials for me. Here, please "
"accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3188"
msgstr ""
"Yes? Ah, and what do we have here? Of course I with help the Sons of Riada "
"decipher this scroll."

msgid "end_text_quest_3190"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have done well my friend. I will begin deciphering the "
"ancient writings very soon."

msgid "end_text_quest_3192"
msgstr "Oh, from Brehan you say. Thank you very much."

msgid "end_text_quest_3193"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for delivering the enchanting ingredients to Niane the Arcanist. I "
"have completed the deciphering of the ancient writings. We have work to do."

msgid "end_text_quest_3195"
msgstr ""
"Three are we the guardians of the Healing Gem. I am the King, the first of "
"the guardians. You who searches for the Healing Gem, must now seek out the "
"Defender. Battle him, and he will lead you closer to the gem."

msgid "end_text_quest_3196"
msgstr ""
"I am the Defender, the second guardian of the Healing Gem. You have battled "
"me, and are now a step closer to the gem.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"If it is the Healing Gem you want, seek out the last of us, the Scholar. "
"Drain him of his power, and he will lead you to the gem."

msgid "end_text_quest_3197"
msgstr ""
"I am the Scholar, and the third of the guardians of the Healing Gem. You "
"have drained me of my power, and successfully passed all three of the "
"guardians. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Return to the King, the first of us, and the gem will be yours."

msgid "end_text_quest_3198"
msgstr ""
"The Healing Gem is now yours mortal. Use it wisely, of else the consequences "
"will be dire!"

msgid "end_text_quest_3199"
msgstr ""
"The Healing Gem. What a marvelous artifact! Yes, I can feel the healing "
"powers with in it. #PlayerName# you have done me and the Sons of Riada a "
"great service. Here is the reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3201"
msgstr "We must put an end to the bandit Ogres of Brockmoore."

msgid "end_text_quest_3203"
msgstr ""
"You have done well. The light of Auros surely shines upon you my friend. "
"Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3205"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName# I thank you! Although I know that this alone will not brings my "
"dear friends back, I feel that justice has been served. Here is the reward I "
"promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3207"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName# you have done well. The evil orks must eventually be removed "
"from Agon for once and for all. Here is your well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3209"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. These materials will definitely be of great use to the "
"enchanters of Silverley."

msgid "end_text_quest_3211"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for helping collect these ingredients. I am sure that Oona Fern "
"will be pleased."

msgid "end_text_quest_3213"
msgstr "How wonderful of Colman to send us these ingredients."

msgid "end_text_quest_3216"
msgstr ""
"Ah, you have successfully recovered the signet ring from our fallen agent. I "
"am grateful, but also deeply saddened for the loss of our dear friend. I "
"will give the ring to his family. Accept this reward for all you have done."

msgid "end_text_quest_3218"
msgstr ""
"Well done. We cannot allow traitorous elements like these, to stir up "
"problems among us ork. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3221"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Very soon our agents and many other warriors will attack these "
"outcast humans. Our scholars will study this Book of Malaut, and see what we "
"can learn from it to use against the pathetic humans of mercia."

msgid "end_text_quest_3223"
msgstr ""
"The gathering of magical ingredients that are used by our enchanters, is a "
"very important and difficult task, that very few actually appreciate."

msgid "end_text_quest_3225"
msgstr "Very well done. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3228"
msgstr ""
"You have done well. The Fire Dragon is surely to be pleased with our "
"success. #PlayerName#, once more the Dragonbound are honored to have worked "
"with you. Accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3231"
msgstr ""
"What is this? A letter with orders. I see. We will study this letter, and "
"carefully plan our next move. You have done well. #PlayerName#, your "
"dedication continues to impress me. Here is the reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3233"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName#, your help has been most valuable to us. Our agents will "
"continue to search for clues of the Raven Standard Army. Here is your well "
"earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3235"
msgstr ""
"So you are here to help with the gathering of enchanting materials. Let us "
"get to work."

msgid "end_text_quest_3237"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. I will give these hearts to our enchanters. Here, accept "
"this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3239"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. I am pleased you were able to help us gather there materials. "
"Here, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3241"
msgstr ""
"Yes? Who are you? And what brings you here? Ah, so Bigork Blacktongue has "
"sent you. Very well."

msgid "end_text_quest_3243"
msgstr ""
"The only place these undead pirates belong, is at the bottom of the sea. You "
"have done well. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3245"
msgstr "Excellent. Here is the reward I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_3248"
msgstr ""
"You have found the Horn of Pain. Yes, I can feel the dark power with it. "
