"your assessment of the situation. Excellent. You have done well. Here is "
"your well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3608"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. #PlayerName#, you have done well. Here is your well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_361"
msgstr "Thank you. Here is a small reward for your efforts."

msgid "end_text_quest_3610"
msgstr ""
"Ah, excellent. At last, we have all the ingredients needed so I may begin "
"the last stage of the deciphering of the ancient scroll."

msgid "end_text_quest_3613"
msgstr ""
"You've return with the diary. This can only mean that our fellow scholar has "
"fallen in the {$j13) dungeon. Thank you for finding the diary."

msgid "end_text_quest_3615"
msgstr ""
"Three are we the guardians of the Demon Ring. I am the King, the first of "
"the guardians. Seek out the Defender, the second of the guardians, and "
"battle him."

msgid "end_text_quest_3616"
msgstr ""
"I am the Defender, the second guardian of the Demon Ring. You have battled "
"me, and are now closer to the gem. Seek out the last of us, the Scholar, and "
"drain him of his power."

msgid "end_text_quest_3617"
msgstr ""
"I am the Scholar, and the third of the guardians of the Demon Ring. You have "
"drained me of my power, and successfully passed all three of the guardians. "
"Return to the King, the first of the guardian statues before thirty minutes "
"have passed, and the ring will be yours."

msgid "end_text_quest_3618"
msgstr "Mortal! The Demon Ring is now yours. Use it wisely."

msgid "end_text_quest_3619"
msgstr ""
"The Demon Ring. What a marvelous artifact! Yes, I can feel the Demon's "
"powers with in it. #PlayerName#, you have have been of great help to the "
"Circle of Neith. Here is the reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3622"
msgstr ""
"The Book of Heroes. At last, our heroes have returned home where they "
"belong. Once more #PlayerName#, you have been of great help to the Elders of "
"Red Moon. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3624"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. The Elders of Red Moon will be most pleased to hear that the site "
"will be soon ready for our researchers to visit. You have done well. Here is "
"your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3626"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. It is good to see that Symyr-dan has sent somebody to help me with "
"my work."

msgid "end_text_quest_3628"
msgstr "Ah, the Greenleaf. Excellent. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_363"
msgstr "Thank you. These teeth will be prove useful to our enchanters."

msgid "end_text_quest_3630"
msgstr ""
"So, you managed to catch the rare tiny Brownies and gather for my three "
"Cloudy Quartz. Excellent."

msgid "end_text_quest_3632"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have proven to be quite a capable and reliable individual. "
"Here, accept this well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3634"
msgstr ""
"And what do we have here? A Wolfmask agent. So, my dear friend Mardem-kai "
"seeks my help once more."

msgid "end_text_quest_3637"
msgstr ""
"Yes, this is it. The List of Names. The time has come for my revenge! "
"#PlayerName#, here s a small reward for your services. I am sure once you "
"return to Mardem-kai, you will be well rewarded."

msgid "end_text_quest_3639"
msgstr ""
"So, a new dark threat has emerged within the central plains, using the Cult "
"of the Moon-Beast and the outcast humans to to distract and weaken us. We "
"must immediately send this information to Red Moon. You have done well "
"#PlayerName#. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3642"
msgstr ""
"A tombstone with strange symbols carved upon it, probably of a demonic "
"origin. You have done well bringing this find to us. #PlayerName#, you have "
"done well, Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3644"
msgstr ""
"When it comes to killing Moon-Beast worshipers, no number is enough. It "
"looks like you could have managed to kill many more. Here is your well "
"earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3646"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for bringing this information to us. Here is something for all the "
"work you have done."

msgid "end_text_quest_3648"
msgstr "Well done. #PlayerName#, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_365"
msgstr "Thank you for giving the goblins that magical reminder."

msgid "end_text_quest_3650"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful. The second of the materials need to destroy the Orb of Disease. "
"Here is the reward I had promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3652"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Now we have all the materials we need to destroy the Orb of "
"Disease. #PlayerName#, here is your well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3654"
msgstr ""
"Ah, the Orb of Disease, and all that is needed to destroy it. #PlayerName#, "
"I thank you for delivering this foul object to us. We of the Serene Spire "
"will do all we can to destroy it."

msgid "end_text_quest_3657"
msgstr ""
"It is as I feared. Annabell Lightheart is dead. I should have never sent her "
"alone on that mission. #PlayerName#, I thank you for delivering Annabell's "
"ring back to us."

msgid "end_text_quest_3659"
msgstr ""
"Yes? You have located one of these tombstones and successfully copied the "
"symbols carved upon it. #PlayerName#, you have done well bringing to us this "
"find.  Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3661"
msgstr ""
"Greetings. What is this? Some kind of ancient writings and symbols. Very "
"interesting. I will try to decipher it. The Arrowheads has done well in "
"locating these strange tombstones."

msgid "end_text_quest_3663"
msgstr ""
"Oh dear. Nairath's book! I had forgotten all about it. I'll go and get it "
"right away."

msgid "end_text_quest_3665"
msgstr ""
"Ah wonderful. I do not like it when Riathen forgets to return my book. Here "
"is a something for returning my book."

msgid "end_text_quest_3667"
msgstr ""
"This is indeed dark news you bring to us my good friend #PlayerName#. I will "
"prepare our agents to gather all information they can about this Dark Lord."

msgid "end_text_quest_3669"
msgstr "If it is information you seek, you have come to the right place."

msgid "end_text_quest_3671"
msgstr ""
"Well done. You have done all that I asked for, and I am pleased. Here is the "
"reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3672"
msgstr ""
"A stone structure with a flame, possibly creating a connection to the fire "
"creatures! Could this actually be the work of the skeleton dragon god "
"Cyriacus? Could Cyriacus be trying to recruit new allies to his cause. You "
"have done well discovering this. Accept this reward. I will inform Shoal "
"about this."

msgid "end_text_quest_3675"
msgstr ""
"It is as I expected. How foolish of my apprentice to venture alone into the "
"Nithron city. This should be a lesson to all the others. Ah, the diary. Let "
"us see what my foolish apprentice had discovered."

msgid "end_text_quest_3677"
msgstr ""
"You have returned with news from Shaol. A dire letter you say, from Ninnah. "
"Let us see."

msgid "end_text_quest_3679"
msgstr ""
"So, the great Aeshanta Darkspire of the Harn Mandean has sent one of her "
"lackeys to me, asking for help. How interesting."

msgid "end_text_quest_3682"
msgstr ""
"Ah, you have returned with my magic box. Very well done. Aeshanta has chosen "
"well in trusting you. Here is a little something for your services."

msgid "end_text_quest_3684"
msgstr ""
"Have you returned with any useful information from Hintenfau? Ah, a letter "
"you say, from Sister Lyrrisa. Let us see what she has to say about this Dark "
"Lord."

msgid "end_text_quest_3686"
msgstr ""
"Seeker of the rod. Bring me five of each that a spellcaster needs. Then I "
"shall guide you one step closer to that which you seek."

msgid "end_text_quest_3687"
msgstr ""
"High in the sky, is the domain of the dragons. Search for the Shrine of the "
"Dragons, and drain it of its power. Only then will it be revealed to you who "
"is the keeper of the rod."

msgid "end_text_quest_3688"
msgstr ""
"He who faces the golden spire is the keeper of the rod. Find him, and you "
"will find the rod."

msgid "end_text_quest_3689"
msgstr "The Rod of Dragon Fire is now yours. Use it wisely."

msgid "end_text_quest_3690"
msgstr ""
"So, there was a hidden artifact with the nithron city. It would seem that my "
"apprentice was actually right. Oh, what a shame she can't be here to enjoy "
"this moment. Here, accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_3692"
msgstr ""
"You have placed seven units of sulfur and seven units of resin upon the "
"demon tombstone, and completed the first step to disabling the magical "
"properties of the demon tombstone. Now you must cast a Rend spell upon the "
"tombstone to bring out its powers."

msgid "end_text_quest_3693"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully cast the Rend spell onto the demon tombstone, brought "
"out its powers, and completed the second step to disabling the magical "
"properties of the demon tombstone. Now you must place seven units of blood, "
"five bones and one heart upon the tombstone."

