"fifth step to disabling the magical properties of the demon tombstone. Now "
"you must cast the Mana Drain spell onto the tombstone to remove all magical "
"properties from it."

msgid "end_text_quest_3697"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. This is good news. It would seem that the sequence of steps that "
