msgid "end_text_quest_3910"
msgstr ""
"Orders from the council you say. I see. It is about the new recruits. They "
"have no need to worry. I will have them all ready on time."

msgid "end_text_quest_3912"
msgstr ""
"And what is this? A weapons list from Catherine the Fighter. Weapons for our "
"new recruits. Tell Catherine I will begin manufacturing the weapons as soon "
"as I get the materials I need delivered to me."

msgid "end_text_quest_3913"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for delivering the weapons list to Anton the Blacksmith. Here is "
"your reward as promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_3915"
msgstr "Excellent. Iron ore, and lots of it. Good. Now I can get back to work!"

msgid "end_text_quest_3917"
msgstr ""
"Ah yes, the weapons crate. I have it right here. Deliver these weapons back "
"to my friend Anton. Sandbrook can use all the weapons it can get."

msgid "end_text_quest_3918"
msgstr ""
"Well done. We can always rely on Talaod for the extra help, in difficult "
"times like these."

msgid "end_text_quest_3920"
msgstr ""
"A first aid box for my good friend Leen in Sandbrook. Of course I can spare "
"one. Here you go."

msgid "end_text_quest_3921"
msgstr ""
"Thank you very much. I really didn't want to tell Catherine the Fighter that "
"I had run out of first aid equipment, and couldn't spare a box for her. Here "
"is the reward I had promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3923"
msgstr "My bag! You found it! Thank you very much."

msgid "end_text_quest_3925"
msgstr ""
"And what does my dear friend Simeon want this time? Tools. How interesting. "
"Alright then. Tell him I'll have them ready by tomorrow."

msgid "end_text_quest_3926"
msgstr ""
"Talaod will have the tools ready by tomorrow. Excellent. Here is the reward "
"I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_3928"
msgstr "Excellent. Iron ore, and lots of it. Good. Now I can get back to work!"

msgid "end_text_quest_3930"
msgstr ""
"You have done well my friend. I know I could rely on you to bring me those "
"weapons."

msgid "end_text_quest_3931"
msgstr ""
"From Sanguine you say. I have been expecting you. Here are the weapons that "
"I have prepared for my friend Talaod the Blacksmith."

msgid "end_text_quest_3933"
msgstr ""
"Jonn needs the Book of Ancient Magic? Alright, he can have it, but tell him "
"to be extra careful with it. There aren't many copies of the book left."

msgid "end_text_quest_3934"
msgstr ""
"Ah, the Book of Ancient Magic. Thank you for bringing it to me. Now I might "
"be able to discover what this scroll really is."

