msgid "end_text_quest_449"
msgstr "Well done. Here is the reward I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_4500"
msgstr ""
"Ah, hahaha. That's what I want to see. Brave fearless warriors. You did  it. "
"You killed 2 Cave Hags.  Good. If you ever feel like hunting Cave Hags "
"again, you know where to find me."

msgid "end_text_quest_4502"
msgstr ""
"Good work. As agreed, here is your reward for killing 15 Cave Hags. The "
"Banegorge Dungeon Cave Hag Hunt will be available again in 21 hours."

msgid "end_text_quest_4504"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You seem able enough to assist the Simiran Order in clearing out "
"the Mabria Dungeon. If you wish to assist us, not do hesitate to speak to me "
"again."

msgid "end_text_quest_4506"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Here is the reward as promised, for destroying 30 Crypt Guards. "
"The Mabria Dungeon Crypt Guard Hunt will be available again in 21 hours."

msgid "end_text_quest_4508"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful. I see that we will definitely be doing more work together in the "
"future. Here is your well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_451"
msgstr ""
"Thank you. Soon the people of Silverspear may sleep safer behind improved "
"walls."

msgid "end_text_quest_4510"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. I am sure the Sisterhood will be pleased with your success. "
"The Larethain Dungeon Darkweaver Hunt will be available again in 21 hours."

msgid "end_text_quest_4513"
msgstr ""
"Ah, well done. You managed to kill one of the ferocious Tomb Iklits. I am "
"impressed. Here is your agreed payment for the good work. Speak to me again "
"if you would like to continue hunting Tomb Iklits."

msgid "end_text_quest_4515"
msgstr ""
"Well done. It takes a lot of courage and strength to hunt Tomb Iklits, "
"especially in large numbers. Here is your well earned reward. The Ahu Ishtra "
"Dungeon Tomb Iklit Hunt will be available again in 21 hours."

msgid "end_text_quest_4517"
msgstr ""
"So, you killed one Tomb Iklit. Well done. Now, if you believe that you could "
"kill many more of these creatures, I am more that willing to hear about it."

msgid "end_text_quest_4519"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Not only are you brave and foolish, but also very lucky. Exactly "
"want the hunt needs. Here is your reward as promised. The Istind Dungeon "
"Tomb Iklit Hunt will be available again in 21 hours. Until then, try "
"something a little less dangerous."

msgid "end_text_quest_4521"
msgstr ""
"Hah, those Crypt Guard were nothing for you. If you enjoyed hunting Crypt "
"Guards and are interested in earning a few rewards, I believe I have an "
"offer for you that you might find interesting."

msgid "end_text_quest_4523"
msgstr ""
"Hahaha. Excellent. You Destroyed those Crypt Guards as if they were just a "
"pile of bone to you. Hahahaha. Well done my friend. If you wish to destroy "
"more Crypt Guards for the right fee, the  Meldanyr Dungeon Crypt Guard Hunt "
"will be available again in 21 hours."

msgid "end_text_quest_4525"
msgstr ""
"Good work. That's what the White Hunters want to see, and I am sure we can "
"do work again in the future. If you are interested, just speak to me again."

msgid "end_text_quest_4527"
msgstr ""
"A job well done. And as agreed, here is your pay. The Otredale Dungeon "
"Undead Dwarf Hunt will be available again in 21 hours."

msgid "end_text_quest_4529"
msgstr ""
"Hey! Not bad. You sure showed those Cave Trolls who's the boss, didn't you! "
"And, here is your reward as agreed. Good thing you decided to work with the "
"Silverswords my friend. Heh, if you feel like a little more Cave Troll "
"Hunting, I am very interested in hearing so."

msgid "end_text_quest_453"
msgstr ""
"You have accumulated five units of timber. Return to Sa-Imdor the Blacksmith "
"in Silverspear to claim a reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_4531"
msgstr ""
"Hey! You completed the hunt. Well done. And here is your reward. Let me "
"inform you that the Scarbourne Dungeon Cave Troll Hunt will be available "
"again in 21 hours. Until then, take care."

msgid "end_text_quest_4533"
msgstr ""
"Ha! You managed to kill 2 Cave Hags. Not as weak as I thought. Hmmm, you "
"might actually be able to pull of the job. If you're interested, speak to me "
"again. I'll be here."

msgid "end_text_quest_4535"
msgstr ""
"Ahahaha. I bet that felt good, killing those Cave Hags one by one. Hahaha, "
"well done, Here is your reward as agreed. The Sirith Dain Dungeon Cave Hag "
"Hunt will be available again in 21 hours. Until then, go kill something else."

msgid "end_text_quest_4537"
msgstr ""
"Well done. You definitely have what is needed to assist the Lords in the "
"work. Should you wish to assist us, do not hesitate to speak to me again."

msgid "end_text_quest_4539"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have performed quite well. As agreed, here is your reward you "
"successfully completing the hunt. The Kaerdan Dungeon Cave Spider Hunt will "
"be available again in 21 hours. Until we meet again, try not to die."

msgid "end_text_quest_4543"
msgstr ""
"Well well. If it isn't a messenger sent from my cousin Hanthar. Yes, what is "
"it?  A fire pillar you say, discovered withing the severii stronghold in "
"{$j23}. Now, that is strange. Hmmm, I shall search our libraries for any "
"similar references to such a structure."

msgid "end_text_quest_4545"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. I see that you have bot fear of these Shadow Spirits. This "
"is good. I would like of you to help us clear tis dungeon of these dark "
"spirits. If you would like to earn a little something extra, I'll be here "
"waiting."

msgid "end_text_quest_4547"
msgstr ""
"Once again you have perform well. And of course, here is your reward as "
"agreed for your services. The Hardruk Dungeon Shadow Spirit Hunt will be "
"available again in 21 hours."

msgid "end_text_quest_4549"
msgstr ""
"Well done. I see that 3 Shade Salamanders wasn't much of a problem for you. "
"My superiors will surely be please to hear about your success. Here is your "
"well earned reward. Ah, and let me know if you wish to continue providing "
"your services."

msgid "end_text_quest_455"
msgstr "Thank you. Here is the reward I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_4553"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Here is your reward for killing 25 Shade Salamanders. The Velmuna "
"Dungeon Shade Salamander Hunt will be available again in 21 hours."

msgid "end_text_quest_4555"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You truly are worthy of the hunt. Here is you reward. Speak to me "
"if you wish to hear the terms of the hunt."

msgid "end_text_quest_4557"
msgstr ""
"Well done. As agreed, here is your reward for killing 30 Cave Spiders. The "
"Winterworth Dungeon Cave Spider Hunt will be available again in 21 hours."

msgid "end_text_quest_4559"
msgstr ""
"You kill 4 Cave Troll. You pass small test. Take your reward. Talk to me if "
"you not scared of Cave Trolls, and want to kill many more."

msgid "end_text_quest_4561"
msgstr ""
"You kill 40 Cave Trolls. You good warrior. Now take reward. In 21 hours, you "
