msgid "end_text_quest_5024"
msgstr ""
"I extend my sincerest thanks to you. With those two monstrosities out of the "
"way we can see about regaining all the ground we lost and the souls of our "
"fallen can rest in peace."

msgid "end_text_quest_5026"
msgstr ""
"I knew I could count on you, my friend. Come back soon, for there is always "
"more work that needs to be done, and riches to be earned."

msgid "end_text_quest_5028"
msgstr ""
"Well done. I am thoroughly impressed. To be honest, I wasn’t sure you had it "
"in you. I wasn’t sure anyone did. The next time there is trouble, I’ll turn "
"to you."

msgid "end_text_quest_503"
msgstr "Thank you for conjuring up that reminder for the goblins."

msgid "end_text_quest_5030"
msgstr ""
"You’re a braver soul than I, I’ll give you that. There is a reason I send "
"the message and you carry out the heroics. Well done."

msgid "end_text_quest_5032"
msgstr ""
"You have proved your worth, hero. I’ve lost track of how many men we’ve lost "
"and I know now that we should have sought you out first. You have our "
"deepest thanks."

msgid "end_text_quest_505"
msgstr "Well done. We'll soon have the ruins cleared of goblin scum."

msgid "end_text_quest_507"
msgstr ""
