msgstr ""
"Thank you. Our enchanters will use these ingredients to create useful "
"magical items."

msgid "end_text_quest_531"
msgstr "Thank you for giving the goblins that magical reminder."

msgid "end_text_quest_538"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for your efforts on behalf of the people of Leafhelm. Here is the "
"reward I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_540"
msgstr "Thank you. Here is the reward I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_542"
msgstr "Well done. Here is the reward I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_544"
msgstr "Thank you. Here is the reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_546"
msgstr ""
"Thank you. I now have all the ingredients I need in order to complete a "
"large shipment of potions for the elflords of {$h18}."

msgid "end_text_quest_548"
msgstr "Thank you. Here is the reward I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_550"
msgstr "Thank you for conjuring up that reminder for the goblins."

msgid "end_text_quest_552"
msgstr ""
"Well done. Hopefully, the goblins that have infest the sacred river will "
"soon be eradicated utterly."

msgid "end_text_quest_554"
msgstr ""
"Very good. This means that new goblin invaders will have to fight and "
"harvest without the weapons dropped by their fallen predecessors."

msgid "end_text_quest_556"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for helping us safeguard our territory against future monster "
"invasions."

msgid "end_text_quest_558"
msgstr ""
"You have accumulated five units of timber. Return to Tiyawen the Blacksmith "
"in Beladin's Rest to claim a reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_56"
msgstr ""
"Thanks to your efforts, more of our warriors will fight under the protection "
"of a Magic Shield."

msgid "end_text_quest_560"
msgstr ""
"Thanks to you your efforts, I will now be able to complete several large "
"orders of potions on time."

msgid "end_text_quest_562"
msgstr ""
"Thank you. I shall give these teeth to our enchanters, who no doubt will "
"will find them useful."

msgid "end_text_quest_564"
msgstr "Thank you for conjuring up that reminder for the goblins."

msgid "end_text_quest_566"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for your efforts on behalf of the people. Here is the reward I "
"promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_568"
msgstr ""
"Very good. This means that the remaining goblins will have to fight without "
"the weapons dropped by their fallen comrades."

msgid "end_text_quest_570"
msgstr ""
"Thank you. The work of strengthening the town's defenses will commence soon."

msgid "end_text_quest_572"
msgstr ""
"Thanks to you and other industrious volunteers, we now have enough timber to "
"begin the construction of our new watchtowers."

msgid "end_text_quest_574"
msgstr "Thank you for the mandrake herbs. Here is the reward I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_576"
msgstr ""
"Thank you. Our enchanters will use these ingredients to create useful "
"magical items."

msgid "end_text_quest_578"
msgstr "Thank you for giving the goblins that magical reminder."

msgid "end_text_quest_58"
msgstr ""
"Your back hurts from all the scrounging about in the undergrowth, but you "
"finally have three mandrakes in your possession."

msgid "end_text_quest_617"
msgstr "Humans! What were they thinking, trying to hide in the Tribelands."

msgid "end_text_quest_619"
msgstr ""
"Yes, this will do. Removing the Timeless Blood is the least we can do for "
"our fallen. Still, I am puzzled why the centaurs would attack us in such a "
"way."

msgid "end_text_quest_62"
msgstr ""
"These teeth will be very useful to our enchanters, who are busy creating "
"magical items for the defense of the city."

msgid "end_text_quest_621"
msgstr ""
"I thank you for putting a stop to those cultist. From now on, the only "
"torturing that will be allowed, will be done by us!"

msgid "end_text_quest_623"
msgstr ""
"I see. The Cult of the Moonbeast is growing in strength, while slowly "
"recruiting new members. We must increase our search in locating out these "
"cultists, before the situation gets out of hand."

msgid "end_text_quest_625"
msgstr ""
"Such weakness dose not belong within Tribelands. You have done well by "
"putting them out of their misery."

msgid "end_text_quest_627"
msgstr ""
"So, the great Mardem-kai has entrusted you with dealing with the hobgoblins. "
"You are the one that has been chosen to restore the pride of the Wolfmasks."

msgid "end_text_quest_629"
msgstr ""
"Yes. The pride of the Wolfmasks is restored. Never again shall a Wolfmask "
"fall to a Hobgoblin. You have done well. Accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_631"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Neithstone Hall is a very important site, and even more now in "
"our battle against the Cult of the Moon-Beast."

msgid "end_text_quest_633"
msgstr ""
"If the Ravager is the most powerful of the cult, then it is not powerful "
"enough. The Cultists will have to do better than that, if they wish to best "
"the Wolfmasks and destroy the work of the Elders. Well done, here is your "
"reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_635"
msgstr ""
"I see the blood of our enemies is still upon you. Yes, you have done well. "
"Reports have already arrived of our victorious battle against the Cult of "
"the Moonbeast. You have proven yourself of being an ally and true friend to "
"the Wolfmasks. Here is a reward for all you have done."

msgid "end_text_quest_637"
msgstr "Well done. Now our enchanters may continue their work."

msgid "end_text_quest_639"
msgstr ""
"So, Celetia the White has sent you to check on my progress. I admit that I "
"have run into a bit of trouble here, and my search for the scroll has "
"progressed little."

msgid "end_text_quest_64"
msgstr ""
"These teeth will be very useful to our enchanters, who are busy creating "
"magical items for the defense of the city."

msgid "end_text_quest_641"
msgstr ""
"Although this ancient city has long been abandoned by the Nithron, Revenants "
"will surely arise again to guard the home of their masters. Still, this is "
"enough that i may continue my search of the scroll."

msgid "end_text_quest_643"
msgstr ""
"Well done. Harvesting a Quartz from an Earth Elemental is no easy task."

msgid "end_text_quest_645"
msgstr ""
"Yes, the final piece of the ancient text! Thanks to your efforts, we are "
"ready to continue our search for the artifact."

msgid "end_text_quest_647"
msgstr ""
"So, it wasn't a scroll after all, but ancient writings on a wall. The Circle "
"of Neith thanks you for assisting us in locating these ancient writings. "
"Accept the reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_649"
msgstr ""
"So the Svartdvergir thought they could just march in and steal our secrets. "
"Let that be a lesson to all!"

msgid "end_text_quest_651"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You are proving to be most valuable to the Circle. Here is a "
"reward for your efforts."

msgid "end_text_quest_653"
msgstr ""
"You have done well disposing of the Ogres. Here is a reward for your efforts."

msgid "end_text_quest_656"
msgstr ""
"Such a wonderful artifact, such ancient knowledge, can only belong to the "
"Circle of Neith!  A glorious moment, and you PLAYER'S NAME have played your "
"part in our success. The Circle of Neith acknowledges all you have done, and "
"offers you this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_658"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You disposed of those Revenant as if they where nothing! Now our "
"researchers may continue their work."

msgid "end_text_quest_660"
msgstr ""
"Splendid!  How I wish I was nearby to watch you drain the life out of those "
"filthy trolls. With this troll blood we shall succeed in creating the most "
"horrid disease Agon has ever seen!"

msgid "end_text_quest_662"
msgstr ""
"I am Naelah Ghostshard, one of the Radiant Circle, and in Melek's name I "
"greet you. If Shulazu has sent you to assist me, then you must be of some "
"worth. Fine then, let us waste no time, and begin our search for this book."

msgid "end_text_quest_665"
msgstr ""
"The Book of Greater Necromancy, the complete work of the once powerful "
"necromancer Kalruk. Yes, I can already feel the power of this book. Truly a "
"remarkable piece of work."

msgid "end_text_quest_667"
msgstr ""
"Now I should be able to continue my work here, without any interference from "
"those annoying trolls."

msgid "end_text_quest_669"
msgstr ""
"The Book of Greater Necromancy, magnificent! So, the necromancer returns, at "
"least his work does and that is all that matters. How wonderful, how ironic. "
"A grand moment for the Radiant Circle. You have done well."

msgid "end_text_quest_671"
msgstr ""
"I never really understood those pathetic Manscorpions. Anyway, a job well "
"done. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_673"
msgstr ""
"Ah, Nightmare Bile, such beautiful ingredients. Yes, yes, the Staff of "
"Rotting Flesh will be ours! Here is your reward as I promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_676"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful! Kalruk's skull. So, this time the necromancer does return. Yes, "
"this is definitely something Cyriacus will remember for a very long time. "
"You have done very well. The Radiant Circle acknowledges all you have done. "
"You are truly a superior Alfar. Here is a well earned reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_678"
msgstr ""
"Well done. You have successfully passed our little trial. It seems you could "
"be of some use to us."

msgid "end_text_quest_68"
msgstr "Thank you for giving the goblins that reminder."

msgid "end_text_quest_680"
msgstr ""
"Good work. You've created enough panic among the forest dwellers. Even as we "
"speak, our agents are moving in."

msgid "end_text_quest_682"
msgstr ""
"So, Nathar Blackorb sends you to me. If you did manage to pass his little "
"test against the Severii, then I am sure you are of some value.  Let us now "
"see what you are truly made of."

msgid "end_text_quest_684"
msgstr ""
"Well done. By the time those thick headed Hobgoblins noticed any of their "
"guards missing, our men should be returning with their reports."

msgid "end_text_quest_686"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You are proving to be quite valuable to us. Here is a reward for "
"your efforts."

msgid "end_text_quest_688"
msgstr ""
"Incredible! You have no fear of battle. You are willing to go to any lengths "
"to prove your superiority. The Hobgoblins have been reminded once more who "
"rules these lands. A job well done."

msgid "end_text_quest_690"
msgstr ""
"I see that all has gone well, and that Kaldahan has everything under "
"control. It is as I knew it would be. The Alfar are superior, and the God "
"King Melek would have it no other way. Kaldahan is one of our most valuable "
"and experienced agents, and has seen quite a few battles.  Anybody serving "
"under him, can only learn. And from what I am reading here, it seems you "
"have learned quite a bit. Kaldahan ranks you among his best men. Well done."

msgid "end_text_quest_692"
msgstr ""
"Yes, you have succeeded in bringing down one of the Oaklords, and sending a "
"clear message to all the forest dwellers. Excellent. They will think twice "
"before interfering in our affairs again."

msgid "end_text_quest_696"
msgstr ""
"It seems that this trail did not pose much of a challenge for you. Good, the "
"Arrowhead are always on the lookout for resourceful and skilled individuals "
"much like yourself."

msgid "end_text_quest_698"
msgstr ""
"Well done. Although it pains me to see the Ciel Fey die by our hand, the "
"peace and safety of the lands comes first."

msgid "end_text_quest_70"
msgstr "Thank you for giving the goblins that reminder."

msgid "end_text_quest_700"
msgstr ""
"So, the hobgoblins have fortified themselves, and established a strong "
"presence in the area. This is most worrying. You have done well  "
"#PlayerName#."

msgid "end_text_quest_702"
msgstr ""
"Well done. The Forest Prophets have been stopped. Until we discover the "
"reason behind these attacks, we shall keep an eye on them. I thank you for "
"your help."

msgid "end_text_quest_704"
msgstr ""
"It still surprises me that those hobgoblins believed that they could "
"establish a stronghold on Mirdain soil. #PlayerName#, you have performed "
"very well. Here is a reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_706"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have managed to show us what you are truly made of. It is an "
"honor for me to say, that you rank amongst some of the best Arrowhead we "
"have. You have definitely earned this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_708"
msgstr ""
"I am pleased to hear that you are here to help. I am Seirinna Oakstaff. I "
"mostly deal with what the Arrowhead like to refer to as the magic matters. "
"Not a great title if you ask me. So, anything from strange magical "
"occurrences, to the hunt of magical ancient weapons or artifact, is what I "
"deal with."

msgid "end_text_quest_710"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName#, your help has been most valuable. Our scouts have managed to "
"find Siledin's diary. We will immediately begin studying for any information."

msgid "end_text_quest_713"
msgstr ""
"Thank you  for finding and delivering this foul Orb for us. We must quickly "
"now follow the instructions from Siledin's diary and destroy it, before it "
"does any more harm."

msgid "end_text_quest_715"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. So, the cause for the strange disease has been found. I am "
"confident that Seirinna will find a cure, now that she has the evil orb in "
"her possession. Well done. Accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_717"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. It is nice to see the trolls doing their part around here. Here "
"is your reward for your effort."

msgid "end_text_quest_719"
msgstr ""
"It saddens me to see such wonderful creatures of the forest, engross "
"themselves in such acts of violence. Still, I thank you for assisting us."

msgid "end_text_quest_721"
msgstr ""
"Thanks to your efforts, our researchers have had enough time to study the "
"crystals. You have been most helpful."

msgid "end_text_quest_723"
msgstr ""
"You have done well. Our agents have moved in, and begun the interrogations. "
"Soon, we will have the answers we seek. These are dark and violent times, "
"and unfortunately it is often called upon for harsh decisions to be taken."

msgid "end_text_quest_725"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName#, your help has been most valuable. We will send our best "
"healers to the sacred tree. The Serene Spire would like to give you this "
"reward, for all that you have done."

msgid "end_text_quest_728"
msgstr ""
"So, this is the Ring of Crystals. I hope next time our researchers are a "
"little more careful with their grand ideas, an leave the adventuring to the "
"experts. Here is a reward for your help."

msgid "end_text_quest_730"
msgstr ""
"Such wonderful ingredients. Our enchanters will surely be pleased. I thank "
"you. Here is your reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_732"
msgstr ""
"Although I am not sure if that is the end of the Giant Skeletons, for now "
"the area is definitely safer. I thank you for your help."

msgid "end_text_quest_734"
msgstr ""
"Success. Here within the Serene Spire, we will confine the power of the "
"shard and learn its secrets. #PlayerName#, without your help, we would not "
"have succeeded. Please accept this reward, for all you have done for us."

msgid "end_text_quest_736"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Soon we shall begin mining. The Elders would like to reward you "
"for your help."

msgid "end_text_quest_738"
msgstr ""
"You have done well in finding this letter and bringing it to us. It is very "
"disturbing to discover that these human bandits had access to this kind of "
"information. It is vital that we discover who has given such information to "
"the humans and why."

msgid "end_text_quest_740"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. I see you have completed the Troll Hunt. Here is your reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_742"
msgstr ""
"You have done well. Nothing shall stand in the way of progress. Nothing "
"shall stand in the way of the Elders."

msgid "end_text_quest_744"
msgstr "Well done. From now on we shall show the respect our dead deserve."

msgid "end_text_quest_747"
msgstr ""
"This is a grand moment in Mahirim history. And you  #PlayerName#, are now "
"part of it. At last, the sacred tablet will be whole again, once more for "
"all Mahirim to read the Words of Amurran. The Elders of Red Moon thank you. "
"Except this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_750"
msgstr ""
"We should have never allowed this to happen. In our quest to modernize the "
"Mahirim, we seem to have forgotten who we are. One nation and its people can "
"only become whole, if they embrace both the past and the future equally."

msgid "end_text_quest_752"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful. These Quartz will definitely become useful in the hands of the "
"Circle of Neith."

msgid "end_text_quest_754"
msgstr "So, you have killed the Night Hags. Well done."

msgid "end_text_quest_756"
msgstr ""
"You disposed of the Ogres? Of course you did! Here is a little something for "
"your effort."

msgid "end_text_quest_758"
msgstr ""
"I am  Lashur Wraithglider, officer of the Harn Mandean. You have been "
"assigned to me. Excellent."

msgid "end_text_quest_760"
msgstr ""
"You have done well. I will send a report to headquarters with our assessment "
"of their strength."

msgid "end_text_quest_763"
msgstr ""
"The Holy Symbol of Melek. Yes, you have done well. Here is the reward I "
"promised you. And what is this!?! A detailed map of our capital city {$n23}, "
"in the hands of the Severii. Impossible! This can only mean one thing. A "
"traitor!"

msgid "end_text_quest_765"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have executed the order I gave you perfectly. This will buy "
"us time."

msgid "end_text_quest_767"
msgstr ""
"This cannot be! An Alfar traitor working for the Severii. You have done well "
"in discovering these plans. Now we must move quickly, if the Harn Mandean is "
"to find itself one step ahead of the Severii. I will sent a message "
"immediately to Shoal."

msgid "end_text_quest_769"
msgstr ""
"If those Ogres ever show their ugly faces around here again, I will "
"personally kill them all."

msgid "end_text_quest_771"
msgstr ""
"Well done. If the Radiant Circle want more, let them find it themselves. "
"Here is something for your effort."

msgid "end_text_quest_773"
msgstr ""
"Soon,  Shoal's grand army will march into the Severii cities, and grind them "
"into the ground. Yes, the time has come to obliterate the Severii. The Harn "
"Mandean have once more proven that they are Shoal's front line of defense."

msgid "end_text_quest_781"
msgstr ""
"The Emerald Thrones thanks you for assistance. Here is your reward as "
"promised."

msgid "end_text_quest_782"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for assisting the Emerald Throne. Here is a reward for your "
"efforts."

msgid "end_text_quest_783"
msgstr ""
"Wonderful. Now the Emerald Throne may send its scholars and researches to "
"investigate these Nithron ruins. Here is a reward helping the Emerald Throne."

msgid "end_text_quest_784"
msgstr ""
"Thank you. Now construction on the new port may continue. The Elflords wish "
"to give you this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_786"
msgstr ""
"This is most wonderful. The Orb of Mirdain History. I never believed that "
"such an artifact ever existed. So much historical information is truly a "
"great treasure for any people. The Emerald Throne thanks you for your help."

msgid "end_text_quest_787"
msgstr ""
"I am grateful for the bravery and effort you have shown on behalf of the "
"Elflords. Please except this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_789"
msgstr ""
"Yes. Truly wonderful. The second orb of history. Now we may at last learn "
"the truth about what lead to the most tragic part of mirdains history, the "
"dark years. #PlayerName#, you have played a vital part  in our quest to "
"uncover the true facts of the past, of the mirdain past. Please accept this "
"reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_790"
msgstr ""
"You have done well. This information is most valuable to us. We will "
"immediately send a report off to Charybdis. We must discover if the Raven "
"Standard Army has returned."

msgid "end_text_quest_799"
msgstr ""
"I see I was correct in entrusting you with this task. Well done. Here is the "
"reward I promised you."

msgid "end_text_quest_800"
msgstr ""
"I see you have returned successful. The gnolls are no match for us. Here is "
"a reward for your efforts."

msgid "end_text_quest_801"
msgstr "You have done well disposing of the Ogres. Accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_802"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. The Cult of the Moonbeast has been a thorn in our side for too "
"long. You have done well. Here is a reward for your efforts."

msgid "end_text_quest_803"
msgstr ""
"Reclaiming the island of Ebonyth, is the least we can do for those brave "
"mahirim. May their souls now rest in peace. Please accept this well earned "
"reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_804"
msgstr ""
"I hope this is the last time the Circle of Neith asks us for a favor like "
"this. Still, a job well done. Here is a reward for your efforts."

msgid "end_text_quest_805"
msgstr ""
"Yes, this will do. We will send off these Tribal Lifeforce to the Elders. "
"Once we discover what exactly these creatures are, then we may eliminate "
"them. Accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_806"
msgstr ""
"Now we may begin exploring the ice continent. #PlayerName#, you have done "
"well. Your help has been of great value to the Longclaw. Please accept this "
"reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_815"
msgstr ""
"So, it is true. The Raven Standard Army is once again assembling. We will "
"have to quickly decide how to deal with this new threat. #PlayerName# , you "
"have done well. This information is most valuable. The Elders of {$j12} wish "
"to give you this reward, for all that you have done."

msgid "end_text_quest_817"
msgstr ""
"Yes? I see. You've managed to complete the task that was assigned to you. "
"Very well. Accept this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_818"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. Now we shall prepare for the ritual. Yes, with this ritual we "
"shall fuel Melek's burning desire to concur Agon. You have done well. Accept "
"this reward."

msgid "end_text_quest_819"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. I see that the undead dwarves were no match for one of your "
"skills. Soon we will launch an attack onto their city and send them back to "
"theirs graves."

msgid "end_text_quest_821"
msgstr ""
"Very well done. You have managed to return with the artifact. This thing, "
"this rune stone is suppose to symbolize this new god? Now we will see, who "
"and what this god really is."

msgid "end_text_quest_823"
msgstr ""
"Marvelous. Durganon's Flame, the legendary artifact of weaponsmithing. With "
"the flame from this ancient artifact, and the superior crafting skills of "
"the Alfar, we will create some of the most feared weapons upon Agon. Here, "
"accept this reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20000"
msgstr ""
"You have killed 10 Goblins. Head back North to Allan the Councillor and "
"inform him of your success."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20001"
msgstr ""
"You have collected 5 Goblin Axes and 3 Lizard on Stick. Head back to Allan "
"the Councillor for your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20002"
msgstr ""
"You have killed 200 Skeleton Archers and 20 Deadeyes. Return to Allan the "
"Councillor in Sanguine and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20003"
msgstr ""
"You have gathered all the raw materials.  Now bring them to Simeon in "
"Sanguine."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20004"
msgstr ""
"You have finished the cooking task from Simeon, return to him to see what "
"other work he has."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20005"
msgstr ""
"You have used your taming skill to create a Mount Figurine.  Go back to "
"Simeon for your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20006"
msgstr "You have reached Talaod the Blacksmith."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20007"
msgstr "You have refined all the materials.  Head back to Talaod."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20008"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully crafted all the items Talaod asked for.  Talk to him "
"for your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2001"
msgstr "You have made contact with Isenda the Clever."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20014"
msgstr ""
"You have collected enough Cooked Fish.  Head to Eanna the Merchant on the "
"West side of Monkfield for your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20015"
msgstr ""
"You have killed 200 Akathars. Return to Simeon the Merchant in Sanguine to "
"collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20016"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully gathered 200 Iron Ore, 300 Stone, 300 Timber and 200 "
"Fish. Deliver all the gathered materials to Talaod the Blacksmith in "
"Sanguine, and collect your title and rewards."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20017"
msgstr ""
"You have cleared out the Scumlings. Exit the sewer system and report to "
"Niane the Arcanist Southeast of the bank."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20018"
msgstr ""
"You have collected 6 Corpseflesh.  Exit the Sewer and talk to Jonn the Mage "
"in the tower near the bank."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20019"
msgstr "You crafted a Trollstaff.  Bring it back to Niane for payment."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2002"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed three Gnolls. Return to Isenda and claim your "
"reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20020"
msgstr ""
"You used your Alchemy skill at the Laboratory.  Now talk to Torgard in the "
"Barracks to the North."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20021"
msgstr ""
"You now have an enchanted Crystal.  Bring it to Torgard the Fighter in the "
"barracks to the North for your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20022"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed 200 Kobold Scroungers, 200 Kobold Scrappers and "
"20 Kobold Raiders. Return to Niane the Arcanist in Sanguine, and collect "
"your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20023"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed 200 Zombies, 100 Zombie Warriors and 20 Dire "
"Zombies. Return to Jonn the Mage in Sanguine, and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20024"
msgstr ""
"You have killed 200 Goblin Scouts, 100 Goblin Fighters and 20 Goblin "
"Shamans. Return to Torgard the Fighter in Sanguine for your title badge."

msgid "finished_text_quest_20025"
msgstr ""
