"With a squawk and an explosion of feathers, yet another windlord falls to "
"the ground. You have now killed three of them, and may report your success "
"to Garin Silvervault in Wintercrown."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2178"
msgstr ""
"Shards of ice clatter to the ground as the second Windgraive expires. You "
"may now claim Garin Silvervault's reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2179"
msgstr "You have located Thargal {$n09}."

msgid "finished_text_quest_218"
msgstr ""
"Using your skinner, you extract yet another tooth from a dead goblin's "
"mouth. You may now return to Chopping Necks in order to present your macabre "
