"You discover a strange mural. This mural does not appear to be of dwarven "
"origin. It depicts a striding lion with a head that appears to be monstrous "
"or deformed. Perhaps this symbol offers a clue to the identity of the "
"pyramid's creator or creators? You should report this find to Garin "
"Silvervault in Wintercrown."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2184"
msgstr "You have reached Garin Silvervault."

