msgid "finished_text_quest_2189"
msgstr ""
"You now have Arduin Blackpeak's last blade in your possession. Take it to "
"Stonevault to claim a reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2190"
msgstr "You hand the sword to Thain Strongforge."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2191"
msgstr ""
"The fanatic glint is extinguished from the eyes of another hobgoblin grunt. "
"After killing five of them, you may claim Thain Strongforge's reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2192"
msgstr ""
"Yet another ogre falls to the ground, his raiding career brought to an end. "
"You have now killed at least four Ogres within the time limit set by Thain "
"Strongforge. Return to Stonevault to claim his reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2193"
msgstr ""
"Something glitters within this pile of mangled bones. Digging your way "
"through, you find a signet ring that is still attached to a finger that has "
"been stripped of flesh."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2194"
msgstr "You hand the signet ring to Thain Strongforge."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2196"
msgstr ""
"Yet another monstrous raider falls. You have killed at least six Troll Lords "
"and two Swamp Hags. Return to Stonevault and claim the reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2197"
msgstr ""
"Black liquid oozes from the svartdvergir as he falls down dead. You have now "
"killed at least eight Svartdvergir. Return to Stonevault and claim Thain "
"Strongforge's reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2198"
msgstr ""
"All around you lie the scattered remains of undead pirates. You have killed "
"five Bonecrew and you may now claim Thargal {$n09}'s reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2199"
msgstr "You now have enough Darktaint to claim Thargal {$n09}'s reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_220"
msgstr ""
"Your Mana Missile hits another Goblin. You have now done your bit in "
"breaking the spirit of the runaway slaves."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2200"
msgstr ""
"You put the Arctic Bear out of its misery. Three of the animals lie dead, "
"and you may report your success to Garn Runeshield in Gemstone Reach."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2201"
msgstr ""
"Another tainted soul expires. You have now killed at least four "
"Svartdvergir. Return to Garn Runeshield and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2202"
msgstr ""
"The magic is broken and the pieces of the Basalt Golem clatter to the "
"ground. Garn Runeshield in Gemstone Reach has promised you a reward for "
"destroying this construct."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2203"
msgstr ""
"With a deep, hollow groan, yet another undead dwarf collapses to the ground. "
"After at least four of them on to the next life, you have qualified for Garn "
"Runeshield's reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2204"
msgstr ""
"You have killed at least three Frostwalkers and one Windgraive. Report to "
"Gardar Stonevalley and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2205"
msgstr ""
"Another forest dweller falls in defense of the Whitebough. You have now "
"killed at least three Ciel Fey and five Centaurs. Report your success to "
"Gardar Stonevalley in Nordakyst."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2206"
msgstr ""
"You now have three Timeless Blood in your possession. Bring them to Gardar "
"Stonevalley and claim his reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2207"
msgstr ""
"The fifth Oathbound falls down dead. You may now claim Gardar Stonevalley's "
"reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2208"
msgstr ""
"Hidden among other, much less interesting volumes, you find a book which "
"matches the description of the Occluded Mirror. Bring it to Gardar "
"Stonevalley in Nordakyst ."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2209"
msgstr "You hand the book to Gardar Stonevalley."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2210"
msgstr "You have reached Garn Runeshield,"

msgid "finished_text_quest_2211"
msgstr "You have located Vestri the Blacksmith."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2212"
msgstr "You have reached Garin Silvervault."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2213"
msgstr ""
"You now possess two doses of Staunch Heart. Bring them to Garn Runeshield "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_222"
msgstr ""
"The fourth goblin falls before you, whimpering as it dies. You may now claim "
"your reward from Bosork the Councillor in Metal Heart."

msgid "finished_text_quest_224"
msgstr ""
"You now have two goblin axes in your possession. Return to Bosork the "
"Councillor for a reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2247"
msgstr ""
"Sparks, smoke and ashes scatter in all directions as you deal the final "
"blow. After killing two Lesser Fire Elementals, you are ready for the next "
"part of Krushar Breakskull's test."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2248"
msgstr ""
"The raptor receives a fatal wound and falls to the ground. Its jaw-muscles "
"still twitch in death, and a hateful, fading growl escapes from its throat. "
"You have killed two raptors. Return to Iron Maiden and report your success."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2249"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Doom Spiders and two Sarlids. Return to "
"Krushar Breakskull and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2250"
msgstr ""
"You have now in your possession two Baleful Venom Sac and two units of "
"Caustic Bile. Return to Krushar Breakskull and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2251"
msgstr ""
"The chest contains a large, lavishly decorated book which matches the "
"description of the Endemoniad. Bring the book to Krushar Breakskull in Iron "
"Maiden, a claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2252"
msgstr "You hand the Endemoniad to Krushar Breakskull."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2253"
msgstr ""
"Yet another guardian construct falls, uttering no sound. You have now killed "
"at least three Snake Revenants and three Oathbound, and may file a report to "
"the Iron Orks about their strengths and weaknesses."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2254"
msgstr ""
"This ancient-looking book resembles the Endemoniad, and it may well be the "
"magical source sought by the Iron Orks. Clawmarks and mud spots indicate "
"that the book has been well thumbed by the local reptilians."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2255"
msgstr "You hand the Tome of Legend to Krushar Breakskull."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2256"
msgstr ""
"Another Sadayel falls in the defense of Silmah, the last great stronghold of "
"their race. You may now return to Iron Maiden and claim a reward from "
"Krushar Breakskull."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2257"
msgstr ""
"Another Hill Giant crushes to the ground. You have now killed at least four "
"Hill Giants Sluggers. Return to Krushar Breakskull and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2258"
msgstr ""
"With a low groan, another hobgoblin falls. You have now killed seven "
"hobgoblins. Return to Krushar Breakskull and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_226"
msgstr ""
"You now have five units of stone in your possession. To claim his reward, "
"give them to Strongar the Blacksmith in Metal Heart."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2269"
msgstr ""
"The shine of evil cunning is extinguished from its eyes, and the Swamp Hag "
"tumbles back into the swamp that hatched it. You have killed four Swamp "
"Hags. Return to Bigclubs Trollmangler."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2270"
msgstr "You locate and speak to Sir Bonehard the Cruel."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2271"
msgstr ""
"Almost separating the torso from the hindquarters, you deal the final blow "
"to yet another half-horse freak. You have now killed at least five Centaurs, "
"and may claim a reward from Bonehard the Cruel in Elfkill Keep."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2272"
msgstr ""
"As you touch the bark of the withered, insignificant-looking twig, you "
"fingers tingle with a brief surge of power. You have the Sacred Bough in "
"your possession. Now bring it to Sir Bonehard the Cruel in Elfkill Keep."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2273"
msgstr "You have handed the Sacred Bough to Sir Bonehard the Cruel."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2274"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Ciel Fey has looked his last upon the sun. After killing six "
"Ciel Fey, you may now claim Bonehard the Cruel's reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2275"
msgstr "You have succeeded in locating Hardzkul Warmaster."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2276"
msgstr ""
"A hateful hissing sound escapes from the throat of the dying Sadayel. You "
"have now killed three Guardians and three Shamans and may claim the reward "
"promised by Hardzkul Warmaster."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2277"
msgstr ""
"Yet another guardian creature falls. The path from the waterfall to the "
"Shrine of Memory should now be relatively clear."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2278"
msgstr ""
"Using brute force, you hammer and bend the ancient statue until it topples "
"and falls. The magic of the Shrine of Memory has now been broken, and the "
"hapless Thaelicians have been driven even closer to oblivion."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2279"
msgstr ""
"Like a felled tree, the Hill Giant slowly falls to the ground with a loud "
"thud. Report your success to Bigclubs Trollmangler in Swampton."

msgid "finished_text_quest_228"
msgstr ""
"You have accumulated five timber. Return to Strongar the Blacksmith in Metal "
"Heart to claim a reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2280"
msgstr ""
"You carve an unspeakable insult into the side of the human statue. Report "
"your success to Bigclubs Trollmangler in Swampton."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2292"
msgstr ""
"Yet another bandit falls. You have successfully killed six Ork Bandits. You "
"may return to Emberhall in order to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2293"
msgstr ""
"You open the chest and find a simple cup made from a silvery material and "
"decorated with strange, jagged runes. As you pick it up, tendrils of liquid "
"start to rise from the Banegrail, wafting and waving about in a tentative "
"fashion. You now hold the Banegrail in your possession. Talk to Bigork "
"Blacktongue in Emberhall if you want to exchange the terrible artifact for a "
"reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2294"
msgstr "You have delivered the Banegrail to Bigork Blacktongue."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2295"
msgstr "You have located Slayor Strongork."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2296"
msgstr ""
"Though the city is in ruins, the magic of {$x11} remains strong, and new "
"revenants will  rise to replace the ones you have killed. For now, though, "
"the islands have been made safe enough that the excavations may continue."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2297"
msgstr ""
"As you open the chest, the soft sounds emanating from it grow louder. Within "
"you find the translucent, gracefully curving shape of the Amber Harp. "
"Deliver Bigork Blacktongue in Emberhall."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2298"
msgstr "You have handed the Amber Harp to Bigork Blacktongue."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2299"
msgstr ""
"As you crush the giant egg, wailing voices rise from the sadayel villages of "
"the {$v11}."

msgid "finished_text_quest_230"
msgstr ""
"Your back hurts from all the scrounging about in the undergrowth, but you "
"finally have five mandrakes in your possession."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2300"
msgstr "You have located Stranglar Bloodaks."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2301"
msgstr ""
"Inside the chest you find a badly decayed, mold-covered copy of the Fecund "
"Leaf. Despite the book's relatively poor condition, large sections of text "
"appear to be legible."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2302"
msgstr "You have delivered the copy of the Fecund Leaf to Stranglar Bloodaks."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2303"
msgstr ""
"As you open the chest, a fetid stench of rotting vegetation escapes from the "
"chest. Inside, layer upon layer of mold envelops an emerald green orb. As "
"you pick it up you notice that it feels wet to the touch. Bring the orb to "
"Bigork Blacktongue in Emberhall."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2304"
msgstr "You have handed the Orb of Decay to Bigork Blacktongue."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2305"
msgstr ""
"Inside the chest you find a silver necklace which bears a black pendant "
"decorated with strange, softly glowing red sigils. Bring the necklace to "
"Bigork Blacktongue in Emberhall."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2306"
msgstr "You have handed the Mark of Morneid to Bigork Blacktongue."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2317"
msgstr ""
"The sound of hooves grows dim in the forest. You have killed four centaurs."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2318"
msgstr ""
"Five of the Human Renegades in Wychwater have fallen before you. Return to "
"Jeremiah Grace and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2319"
msgstr ""
"Another troll falls before you. You have successfully killed four trolls. "
"Return to Jeremiah Grace."

msgid "finished_text_quest_232"
msgstr ""
"Using your skinner, you extract the fourth tooth from the mouth of a dead "
"goblin. You may now claim a reward by presenting your grisly collection to "
"Bosork the Councillor in Metal Heart."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2320"
msgstr ""
"The third Air Elemental dissolves into nothingness. You may now claim your "
"reward from Sir Jeremiah Grace."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2321"
msgstr ""
"The Greater Below lets out an unearthly, high-pitched scream as it falls to "
"the ground, shadow-smoke issuing from its mouth."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2322"
msgstr ""
"The shadows of the cavern seem to diminish around you. You have killed five "
"Malaut Acolytes and two Human Highwaymen, and may claim a reward from Sir "
"Jeremiah Grace."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2323"
msgstr ""
"Malaut's grip on Snowthorpe grows weaker as you kill yet another of his "
"servants. You have now killed four Malaut Beguilers and four Human "
"Highwaymen, and may claim a reward from Sir Jeremiah Grace."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2324"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Below and three Malaut Beguilers. Return "
"to Sir Jeremiah Grace and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2333"
msgstr ""
"You have sent a small army of the undead back to their graves, and you may "
"now claim your reward from Maria Hawksgate."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2334"
msgstr ""
"As you cast the mana drain spell onto the Shadow Tree, the river around its "
"trunk seems to grow clearer and to flow with a gentler sound. Return to "
"Maria Hawksgate."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2335"
msgstr ""
"An aura of shadow disperses from the Dire Zombie as you slay it. It falls "
"pathetically to the ground as a normal corpse."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2336"
msgstr ""
"The Hill Giant falls to the ground with a loud, sickening thud. You have now "
"killed four Hill Giants. Return to Maria Hawksgate and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2337"
msgstr ""
"With a final scream, another hobgoblin crumbles to the ground. You have now "
"killed four hobgoblins. Return to Maria Hawksgate and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2338"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Melechar. Return to Maria Hawksgate and claim your "
"reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2339"
msgstr ""
"As you slice off another chunk of the second golem's putrid flesh, it "
"finally collapses and dies. You may now claim Maria Hawksgate's reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_234"
msgstr ""
"Your Mana Missile hits another Goblin. Hopefully, this will help encourage "
"the goblins to settle further away from the village."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2340"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Giant Skeleton falls clattering to the ground, its bones "
"scattering all around you. You have killed four Giant Skeletons now, and you "
"may claim Maria Hawksgate's reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2349"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed three Sarlids and five Spiders. Return to Iain "
"Deepwode and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2350"
msgstr ""
"As your fingers touch the crown, it starts to shine softly with a reddish "
"light. As you lift the artifact from the chest, a sharp, insistent woman's "
"whisper echoes through your mind. For a brief moment, the reality in front "
"of you is replaced by a vision of countless mangled bodies on a battlefield "
"which stretches on forever. You have found the Diadem of Dawn."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2351"
msgstr "You have handed the Diadem of Dawn to Iain Deepwode."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2352"
msgstr ""
"With a tired and pathetic groan, the last Undead Dwarf keels over and falls "
"to the ground. You have now completed Iain Deepwode's quest."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2353"
msgstr "You have successfully located Eva Rainbird."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2354"
msgstr ""
"The sixth salamander fixes you with a hateful glare, then falls down dead at "
"your feet."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2355"
msgstr ""
"Hissing pathetically through its forked tongue, the sixth lizardman lifts "
"its head towards the sky and dies."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2356"
msgstr ""
"You have reached Iain Deepwode and have handed over the Wainfold Tapestry."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2357"
msgstr ""
"Inside the chest you find a large bronze necklace which consists of two "
"entwined dragon-shapes which end in gaping mouths that almost meet at the "
"front. As you pick up the artifact, you hear the same female whisper as you "
"did when you picked up the Diadem of Dawn, but stronger and more insistent "
"this time. Now claim your reward by bringing it to Iain Deepwode in {$u21}."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2358"
msgstr "You have delivered the Dragontorc to Iain Deepwode."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2359"
msgstr ""
"You now possess three Menhir Hearts. Return to Iain Deepwode in {$u21} to "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_236"
msgstr ""
"Four goblins lie slain before you. Claim your reward from Vilethug the "
"Councillor in New Flayed Elf."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2369"
msgstr "You have made contact with Arduin Strayshadow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2370"
msgstr ""
"As yet another stunted green shape falls to the ground. You have now killed "
"four Goblin Fighters and four Goblin Scouts have fallen before you. Return "
"to Arduin Strayshadow and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2371"
msgstr ""
"You have killed three Goblin Shamans and two Goblin Marauders. Return to "
"Arduin Strayshadow and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2372"
msgstr ""
"You have successful killed one Goblin Warlord and two Goblin Marauders. "
"Report to Arduin Strayshadow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2373"
msgstr ""
"You have located Maria Hawkgate of the White Order and have handed Arduin's "
"report to her."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2379"
msgstr ""
"Your weapon is smeared with blood and gore from six Hivekin Foragers. Return "
"to William the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_238"
msgstr ""
"You retrieve yet another goblin axe, taking the tally to two. You may now "
"claim a reward from Vilethug the Councillor in New Flayed Elf."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2380"
msgstr ""
"You now have five hivekin claws in your possession. Give the grisly "
"collection to William the Councillor to claim a reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2381"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Hivekin Broodguards and the Hivekin Queen. "
"Return to William the Councillor and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2382"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully located the Noonday Moon. Deliver the gemstone to Sir "
"Jeremiah Grace and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2383"
msgstr "You have handed the Noonday Moon to Sir Jeremiah Grace."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2388"
msgstr "You have located and talked to Maren Winterspar."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2389"
msgstr ""
"After relentlessly killing dozens of members of {$v20}'s undead population, "
"you have now retired at least four Zombies and four Skeletons. Return to "
"Maren Winterspar."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2390"
msgstr ""
"Striking blow after blow against the Unseen Hand, you've killed three Human "
"Brawlers and three Human Outlaws."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2391"
msgstr ""
"You now have three units of skeleton bone and one unit ofcorpseflesh in your "
"possession. Give them to Maren Winterspar to claim a reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2392"
msgstr ""
"You now have in your possession one Baleful Venom Sac. Deliver it to Iain "
"Deepwode  in Hildershall."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2398"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed enough Gnolls to gather three units of Bile. "
"Return to Isenda and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_240"
msgstr ""
"You now have five units of stone in your possession. Give them to Wolfork in "
"New Flayed Elf to claim his reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2400"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully gathered two units of Bile. Return to Yaleria-Sai the "
"Able."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2402"
msgstr "You have located Talaod the Blacksmith."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2404"
msgstr "You have located Allan the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2406"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed seven goblins. Return to Allan the Councillor "
"in Sanguine, and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2408"
msgstr "You have made contact with Jonn the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2410"
msgstr ""
"You have managed to collect five units of sulfur. Return to Jonn at Sanguine."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2412"
msgstr ""
"You have now five units of resin in your possession. Return to Jonn the mage "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2414"
msgstr "You have reached Allan the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2416"
msgstr "You have located Anton the Blacksmith."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2418"
msgstr "You have made contact with William the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_242"
msgstr ""
"You have collected five timber. Return to Wolfork the Blacksmith in New "
"Flayed Elf to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2420"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed seven goblins. Return to William the Councillor "
"in Sandbrook, and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2422"
msgstr "You have made contact with Carrad the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2424"
msgstr ""
"You have managed to collect five units of sulfur. Return to Carrad at "
"Sandbrook."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2426"
msgstr ""
"You have now five units of resin in your possession. Return to Carrad the "
"mage and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2428"
msgstr "You have reached William the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2430"
msgstr "You have located Jeremiah the Blacksmith."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2432"
msgstr "You have located Aidan the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2434"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed seven goblins. Return to Aidan the Councillor "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2436"
msgstr "You have made contact with Caradwen the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2438"
msgstr ""
"You have managed to collect five units of sulfur. Return to Caradwen at "
"Heart of Eanna and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_244"
msgstr ""
"Your back hurts from all the scrounging about in the undergrowth, but you "
"finally have five mandrakes in your possession."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2440"
msgstr ""
"You have now five units of resin in your possession. Deliver them to "
"Caradwen the mage and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2442"
msgstr "You have made contact with Aidan the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2444"
msgstr "You have located Bigthug the Blacksmith."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2446"
msgstr "You have made contact with Uzrok the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2448"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed seven goblins. Return to Uzrok the Councillor, "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2450"
msgstr "You have made contact with Bloodzkul the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2452"
msgstr ""
"You have managed to collect five units of sulfur. Return to Bloodzkul and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2454"
msgstr ""
"You have now five units of resin in your possession. Return to Bloodzkul the "
"Mage and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2456"
msgstr "You have reached Urzok the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2458"
msgstr "You have located Strongar the Blacksmith."

msgid "finished_text_quest_246"
msgstr ""
"Using your skinner, you extract the fourth tooth from the mouth of a dead "
"goblin. You may now return to New Flayed Elf in order to present your  "
"handiwork to Vilethug the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2460"
msgstr "You have made contact with Bosork the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2462"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed seven goblins. Return to Bosork the Councillor, "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2464"
msgstr "You have made contact with Manglar the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2466"
msgstr ""
"You have managed to collect five units of sulfur. Return to Manglar and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2468"
msgstr ""
"You have now five unit of resin in your possession. Return to Manglar the "
"Mage and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2470"
msgstr "You have reached Bosork the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2472"
msgstr "You have located Wolfork the Blacksmith."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2474"
msgstr "You have made contact with Vilethug the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2476"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed seven goblins. Return to Vilethug the "
"Councillor and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2478"
msgstr "You have made contact with Skullgor the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_248"
msgstr ""
"Your Mana Missile hits another Goblin. Return to Vilethug the Councillor in "
"New Flayed Elf to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2480"
msgstr ""
"You have managed to collect five units of sulfur. Return to Skullgor and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2482"
msgstr ""
"You have now five unit of resin in your possession. Return to Skullgor the "
"Mage and claim your reward."

