"You have successfully used the oven and cooked your meal. Report your "
"success to Arinthu the Merchant."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2890"
msgstr "You have reached Taelis the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2892"
msgstr "You have located Kaelit the Merchant."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2894"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully gathered four pieces of leather. Return to Kaelit the "
"Merchant and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2896"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully used the oven and cooked your meal. Report your "
"success to Kaelit the Merchant."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2898"
msgstr "You have reached Nirgash the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2900"
msgstr "You have located Talduk the Merchant."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2902"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully gathered four pieces of leather. Return to Talduk the "
"Merchant and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2904"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully used the oven and cooked your meal. Report your "
"success to Talduk the Merchant."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2906"
msgstr "You have reached Irshanta the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2908"
msgstr ""
"You have killed two Mahirim player characters, two Dwarf player characters "
"and two Ork player characters. Return to Shoal and claim your reward from "
"Ensharra the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2910"
msgstr "You have reached Ordgrim the Councillor in Ymir's Tear."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2912"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Ork players character. Return to Ymir's "
"Tear, and claim your reward from Ordgrim the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2914"
msgstr "You have reached Sylanae the Councillor in Charybdis."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2916"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Mahirim players character. Return to "
"Charybdis, and claim your reward from Sylanae the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2918"
msgstr "You have reached Allan the Councillor in Sanguine."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2920"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Alfar players character. Return to "
"Sanguine, and claim your reward from Allan the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2922"
msgstr "You have reached Tivasta the Councillor in Red Moon."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2924"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Mirdain players character. Return to Red "
"Moon, and claim your reward from Tivasta the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2926"
msgstr "You have reached Izkruul the Councillor in Flaming Skull."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2929"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed five Alfar players character. Return to Red "
"Moon, and claim your reward from Tivasta the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2931"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed five Alfar players character. Return to Flaming "
"Skull, and claim your reward from Izkruul the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2933"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Human players character. Return to Flaming "
"Skull, and claim your reward from Izkruul the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2934"
msgstr "You have reached Arinlit Icethrone."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2936"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully gathered three Wind Shadowcrests from the Windlords. "
"Return to Arinlit Icethrone, and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2938"
msgstr ""
"As you lift the Demon Hand from the chest, it starts to softly glow with a "
"sickly green light. You feel a sudden rush of unearthly energy coursing "
"through your whole body. Return the Demon's Hand to Arinlit Icethrone."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2939"
msgstr "You have successfully delivered the Demon Hand to Arinlit Icethrone."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2941"
msgstr "You have handed over the Demon Hand to Shulazu Nightshade."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2943"
msgstr "You have reached Kaldahan Deepshadow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2945"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed seven Melechar. Return to Kaldahan Deepshadow "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2947"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully retrieved the Holy Symbol of Melek. Return to Kaldahan "
"Deepshadow and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2948"
msgstr "You have handed the Holy Symbol of Melek to Kaldahan Deepshadow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2950"
msgstr "You have handed Kaldahan Deepshadow's report to Nathar Blackorb."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2952"
msgstr ""
"You come across an old weather-torn tombstone, with strange symbols carved "
"upon it. The symbols does not appear to be of severii origin. Perhaps these "
"symbols offers a clue to the identity of who or what is behind the sudden "
"serpentine appearance? You copy the symbols on a piece of parchment. Report "
"this find to Aeshanta Darkspire."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2954"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed three serpentines. Return to Aeshanta "
"Darkspire, and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2956"
msgstr "You have reached Ninnah the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2958"
msgstr ""
"You now have in your possession three units of elemental cinder. Deliver "
"them to Ninnah the Mage, so she may complete the deciphering of the demonic "
"writings."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2960"
msgstr "You have reached Ninseri the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2962"
msgstr ""
"You now have in your possession ten Cursed Darktaint. Deliver them to "
"Ninseri the Mage in Espenhal."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2964"
msgstr "You have handed the copy of the demonic writings to Ninnah the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2967"
msgstr ""
"Yet another gray ork falls. You have killed at least three gray orks. Find "
"your way out of the dungeon and return with for report to Dekazu Fearweaver."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2969"
msgstr "You have reached Elena the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2971"
msgstr ""
"You have fought and defeated four Oathbound, and you now feel ready to give "
"Elena a thorough report on their strengths and weaknesses."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2973"
msgstr ""
"While most of the books on the shelf are yellowed and brittle with age, one "
"volume seems almost new. You take it down and read the title on the first "
"page: Chronicles of the Firstborn."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2974"
msgstr "You have handed the Chronicles of the Firstborn to Elena the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2976"
msgstr "You hand the message to Allan the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2978"
msgstr "You have reached  Allan the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2980"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully located the unholy book of Malaut. Find your way out "
"of the dungeon and deliver the book to Allan the Councillor at Sanguine."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2981"
msgstr "You have handed the unholy book of Malaut to Allan the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2983"
msgstr "You have reached Oona Fern."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2985"
msgstr ""
"Another gray ork falls to the ground. You have now killed four gray orks. "
"Report your successes to Oona Fern in Silverley."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2987"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed three Guildmasters, three Outlaws and three "
"Highwaymen. Return to Maria Hawksgate, and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2989"
msgstr "You have reached Aurmon the Brave."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2991"
msgstr ""
"With a wild scream, another centaur falls to the ground. You have now killed "
"six centaurs. Return to  Aurmon the Brave."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2993"
msgstr "You have reached Yaleria-Sai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2995"
msgstr ""
"From the piles of ash that remain of the once powerful elemental, you manage "
"to retrieve one unit of Elemental Cinder. Return to Yaleria-Sai and collect "
"your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2997"
msgstr "You have reached Katila the Arcanist."

msgid "finished_text_quest_2999"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Bonecrew falls by your hand. All that lays around you is rotten "
"flesh and bones. Return to Mardem-kai and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3001"
msgstr ""
"You have located the marked gravestone and successfully destroyed the "
"markings upon it. Report back to Mardem-kai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3003"
msgstr ""
"You have completed your assessment of the Gray Orks of Dagnamyr. Return to "
"Mardem-kai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3005"
msgstr "You have reached Tivasta the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3007"
msgstr ""
"You come across an old dusty tomb. Upon its lid you read, here lies the "
"faithful guardian of the mahirim people, Larren-Tai. You have found the "
"resting place of Larren-Tai. Return to Tivasta the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3009"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully harvested a Tribal Lifeforce. Return to Celetia the "
"White and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3011"
msgstr ""
"You have reached Levynna the Arcanist at the Elders of Red Moon headquarters."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3013"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully gathered three Wind Shadowcrest. Deliver them to "
"Celetia the White at the Circle of Neith, and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3015"
msgstr ""
"As you cast the Mana Missile Spell on the magical gravestone, a large book "
"appears atop of it. On its cover you read, “Book of Bad Magic”. You have "
"found the lost work of Siritos. Deliver it to Caradial Elmheart at the "
"Emerald Throne."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3016"
msgstr "You have delivered the Book of Bad Magic to Caradial Elmheart."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3018"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully destroyed four ghouls. Return to Caradial Elmheart and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3020"
msgstr ""
"You have killed four gray orks. Report to Sylanae the Councillor in "
"Charybdis."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3022"
msgstr ""
"Another gray ork falls to the ground, while looking at you in absolute "
"terror. You have now killed four gray orks. Return to Eredethil Swiftarrow "
"at the Arrowhead headquarters."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3024"
msgstr ""
"Another melechar falls to the ground. You have now killed at least four "
"melechar. Find your way out of the dungeon and report to Eredethil "
"Swiftarrow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3026"
msgstr "You have reached Sylanae the Councillor in Charybdis."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3028"
msgstr "You have reached Theila Brightstar."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3030"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully found the unholy book of Melek. Find your way out of "
"the dungeon and report to Sylanae the Councillor in Charybdis."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3031"
msgstr "You have handed the unholy book of Melek to Sylanae the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3033"
msgstr "You have reached Naianir Treedancer."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3035"
msgstr ""
"You have found the Rod of Bad Magic inside the unmarked dusty tomb. As you "
"hold it, you feel an uneasy connection to the wizard Damanthel, as if his "
"soul is trapped inside the staff. Return to Aelathil Silverleaf at the "
"Serene Spire."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3036"
msgstr "You have handed the Rod of Bad Magic to Aelathil Silverleaf."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3038"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully destroyed six Oathbound. Find your way out of the "
"dungeon and report to  Aelathil Silverleaf."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3040"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully harvested three units of Putrid Corpseflesh. Deliver "
"them to Aelathil Silverleaf at the Serene Spire and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3042"
msgstr "You have reached Nairath the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3044"
msgstr ""
"You now have in your possession four units of Timeless Blood and two Tainted "
"Hearts. Return to Nairath the Mage and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3046"
msgstr ""
"You now have in your possession three Barbed Claw. Return to Nairath the "
"Mage and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3048"
msgstr "You have reached Riathen the Mage and handed her Nairath's package."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3050"
msgstr "You have reached Kanute Wayfarer."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3052"
msgstr ""
"You have decimated the glacier-based army in accordance with the wishes of "
"the Voice of Ymir. Report your success to Garin Silvervault in Wintercrown."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3054"
msgstr ""
"Inside the badly scratched and dented chest you find a golden scepter which "
"seems to glow with untapped power. It matches the description of the fabled, "
"long-lost scepter which was once wielded by the Ice Demon Aegin. Bring "
"Aegin's Scepter to Garin Silvervault in Wintercrown."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3055"
msgstr "You handed the scepter to Garin Silvervault."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3057"
msgstr "You have reached Nidstein the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3059"
msgstr ""
"Inside the chest you find a golden, glowing amulet which matches the "
"description given to you by Nidstein the Mage. You now have the amulet in "
"your possession. Deliver it to Nidstein the Mage and claim his reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3060"
msgstr "You hand the amulet to Nidstein the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3062"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Oathbound falls before you. After killing four of these "
"constructs, you have now formed an opinion of their relative strengths and "
"weaknesses. Return to Nidstein the Mage and give him a verbal report."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3064"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Svartdvergir Summoner falls. You have now killed at least five "
"Svartdvergir summoners. Make your way out of the dungeon and report your "
"success to Garn Runeshield."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3066"
msgstr "You have reached Eyvind the Merchant."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3068"
msgstr ""
"Another Hivekin Solder falls to the ground. You have now killed eight of "
"these hideous creatures. Report to Eyvind the Merchant and collect your "
"reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3070"
msgstr "You have reached Garn Runeshield."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3072"
msgstr ""
"You discover a skeleton magically floating above a shrine dedicated to "
"Sahul, the svartdvergir god. Perhaps the svartdvergir and their dark magic, "
"or even Sahul are spawning the undead dwarves within the Otretdale mine. "
"Report this find to Garn Runeshield in Gemstone Reach."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3073"
msgstr "You have reached Garn Runeshield."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3075"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed three Gray Orks. Return to Stonevault and claim "
"you reward from Thain Strongforge."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3077"
msgstr ""
"You have found a letter from the leaders behind this group of Fire Standard "
"hobgoblin grunts. Return to Stonevault and report your finding to Thain "
"Strongforge."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3078"
msgstr "You have handed the letter to Thain Strongforge."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3080"
msgstr ""
"As the third Hobgoblin Veterans falls, you discover a letter in his "
"possession. You pick it up at quickly read through it. It contains orders "
"sent by the Raven Standard hobgoblins. Return to Thain Strongforge to report "
"your finding."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3081"
msgstr ""
"You have reached Thain Strongforge, and handed him the Raven Standard letter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3083"
msgstr ""
"Another Raven Standard Grunt falls to the ground. You have now killed three "
"Raven Standard Grunts. Report your success to Thain Strongforge."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3085"
msgstr "You have reached Frostinn the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3087"
msgstr ""
"As you cast the mana missle spells upon the brazier, you feel as if your "
"whole body is covered if fire. You have found Durganon's Brazier. Report "
"this find to Frostinn the Mage in Stonevault."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3088"
msgstr "You have reached Frostinn the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3090"
msgstr "You have reached Ninnah the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3092"
msgstr ""
"You now have in your possession one unit of Ichor and one unit of Numen. "
"Return to Shoal and deliver the ingredients to Ninnah the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3094"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed two Nalaed and three Sarlid Darkweavers. Go "
"straight to Ensharra the Councillor, to report your assessment of the "
"creatures strengths and weaknesses."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3096"
msgstr "You have reached Sriva Ghostweb."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3098"
msgstr ""
"You now have in your possession five Vile Horn. Return to Sriva Ghostweb and "
"collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_31"
msgstr ""
"As the last goblin falls down with a pathetic gurgle, you can now head back "
"North to Allan the Councillor and inform him of your success."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3100"
msgstr ""
"Skillfully you remove another Gloomy Darktaint from the body of the arthain. "
"You now have six Gloomy Darktaint in your possession. Return to Sriva "
"Ghostweb at Castle Obad and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3102"
msgstr "You have reached Shulgan Shadowscream."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3104"
msgstr ""
"Yet another hobgoblin falls. You have now killed at least four hobgoblins. "
"Return to Shulgan Shadowscream and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3106"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Nahdruk crumbles to the ground, while looking at you in "
"disbelief. You have succeeded in killed three Nahdruk in less than two "
"hours. Report to Shulgan Shadowscream and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3108"
msgstr "You have reached Tialanta the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3110"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Human player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Shoal and claim your reward from Tialanta the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3112"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Mirdain player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Shoal and claim your reward from Tialanta the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3114"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Mahirim player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Shoal and claim your reward from Tialanta the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3116"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Ork player characters within the four hour time limit. "
"Return to Shoal and claim your reward from Tialanta the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3118"
msgstr "You have reached Hanthar Blackfrost."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3120"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed six Nahdruk. Return to Hanthar Blackfrost and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3122"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully gathered five units of Mystical Eye. Return to Hanthar "
"Blackfrost and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3124"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully removed eight elemental quartz from the fallen Earth "
"Elementals. Return to Hanthar Blackfrost and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3126"
msgstr "You have reached Shulazu Nightshade."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3128"
msgstr ""
"The second Gnoll Butcher fixes you with a hateful glare as it falls down "
"dead at your feet. Return to Hanthar Blackfrost and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3130"
msgstr "You have reached Hildr the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3132"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Mahirim player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Ymir's Tear and claim your reward from Hildr the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3134"
msgstr "You have reached Torgard the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3136"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Ork player characters within the four hour time limit. "
"Return to Sanguine and claim your reward from Torgard the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3138"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Alfar player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Sanguine and claim your reward from Torgard the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3140"
msgstr "You have reached Galien the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3142"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Alfar player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Charybdis and claim your reward from Galien the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3144"
msgstr "You have reached Hildr the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3146"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Ork player characters within the four hour time limit. "
"Return to Ymir's Tear and claim your reward from Hildr the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3148"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Mahirim player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Ymir's Tear and claim your reward from Hildr the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3150"
msgstr "You have reached Torgard the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3152"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Ork player characters within the four hour time limit. "
"Return to Sanguine and claim your reward from Torgard the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3154"
msgstr "You have reached Galien the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3156"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Mahirim player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Charybdis and claim your reward from Galien the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3158"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Alfar player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Charybdis and claim your reward from Galien the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3160"
msgstr "You have reached Cyreia the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3162"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Dwarven player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Red Moon and claim your reward from Cyreia the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3164"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Mirdain player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Red Moon and claim your reward from Cyreia the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3166"
msgstr "You have reached Aksmaster the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3168"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Human player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Flaming Skull and claim your reward from Aksmaster the "
"Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3170"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Alfar player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Flaming Skull and claim your reward from Aksmaster the "
"Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3172"
msgstr "You have reached Aksmaster the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3174"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Dwarven player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Flaming Skull and collect your reward from Aksmaster the "
"Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3176"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Human player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Flaming Skull and claim your reward from Aksmaster the "
"Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3178"
msgstr "You have reached Cyreia the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3180"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Mirdain player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Red Moon and claim your reward from Cyreia the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3182"
msgstr ""
"You have killed five Alfar player characters within the four hour time "
"limit. Return to Red Moon and claim your reward from Cyreia the Fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3184"
msgstr ""
"You removed the last Gloomy Darktaint from the body of the fallen Arthain. "
"Return to Brehan Thornbrook, and collect you reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3186"
msgstr ""
"You have two units of Ghostly Darktaint in your possession. Return to Brehan "
"Thornbrook and clain your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3188"
msgstr "You have reached Brehan Thornbrook and handed him the scroll."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3190"
msgstr ""
"You now have in your possession two units of Elemental Cinder. Return to "
"Brehan Thornbrook and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3192"
msgstr ""
"You have handed the sack with the ingredients to Niane the Arcanist. Return "
"to Brehan Thornbrook to inform him of the delivery and to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3193"
msgstr "You have reached Brehan Thornbrook."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3195"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully cast a mana missile spell on the first of the guardian "
"statues. You have activated the first of the guardian statues."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3196"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully used physical force on the second of the guardian "
"statues. You have battled the Defender."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3197"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully cast a mana drain spell on the third of the guardian "
"statues. You have now drained the Scholar of his power."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3198"
msgstr ""
"You now have in your possession the Healing Gem. Deliver the gem to Brehan "
"Thornbrook and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3199"
msgstr "You have delivered the Healing Gem to Brehan Thornbrook."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3201"
msgstr "You have reached Colman Ashbourne."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3203"
msgstr ""
"Yet another ogre falls. You have now killed four Ogres. Return to Colman "
"Ashbourne and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3205"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four revenants and extracted revenge for Colman "
"Ashbourne."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3207"
msgstr ""
"You have killed three Ork player characters. Return to Colman Ashbourne and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3209"
msgstr ""
"You have now in your possession five Baleful Venom Sacs. Return to Colman "
"Ashbourne in Carpendale."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3211"
msgstr ""
"You have now in your possession three units of Tainted Hearts. Return to "
"Colman Ashbourne in Carpendale."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3213"
msgstr ""
"You have reached Oona Fern and handed her the package from Colman Ashbourne."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3215"
msgstr ""
"You find the battered and broken body of the dead agent. You manage to find "
"hidden away in one of the pockets the agents signet ring. Find you way out "
"of the dungeon, head straight for Sanguine and deliver the ring to Allan the "
"Councillor."

