"the dungeon, and deliver the book to Symyr-dan."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3622"
msgstr "You have handed the Book of Heroes to Symyr-dan."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3624"
msgstr ""
"With a loud thud, another arthain crumbles to the ground. You have "
"successfully killed three arthian. Return to Symyr-dan in Amurranyr and "
"collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3626"
msgstr "You have reached Naticia the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3628"
msgstr ""
