"for. Exit the dungeon complex, and deliver the list to Sister Lyrissa in "
"Hintenfau."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3637"
msgstr "You have reached Sister Lyrissa and handed the List of Names to her."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3639"
msgstr "You have reached Mardem-kai the Loyal."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3641"
msgstr ""
"You come across an old weather-torn tombstone, with strange symbols carved "
"upon it. The symbols does not appear to be of any language you know. Perhaps "
"these symbols offers a clue to the identity of who or what is controlling "
"the cultists. You copy the symbols on a piece of parchment. Return to Mardem-"
"kai and report your finding."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3642"
msgstr "You have reached Mardem-kai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3644"
msgstr ""
"Yet another member of the Cult of the Moon-Beast falls to the ground. You "
"have now killed ten members of the Cult of the Moon-Beast. Return to Mardem-"
"kai and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3646"
msgstr "You have reached Tivasta the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3648"
msgstr ""
