"Councillor in Valfather's Edge."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3650"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully gathered three unit of Caustic Bile. Return to "
"Seirinna the Mage, and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3652"
msgstr ""
"You have in your possession two units of Gloomy Darktaint. Return to "
"Seirinna the Mage in Krisathel and collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3654"
msgstr "You have reached Aelathil Silverleaf."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3656"
msgstr ""
"You find the missing Arrowhead agent, but unfortunately it's too late. What "
"you do manage to recover from the dead agent, is the signet ring of the "
"Arrowhead. Return to Krisathel, and deliver the agents ring and the dire "
"news to Eredethil Swiftarrow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3657"
msgstr "You have handed the ring to Eredethil Swiftarrow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_3659"
msgstr ""
"You come across an old weather-torn tombstone with strange symbols carved "
"upon it. The symbols do not appear to be in any written language you know "
"of. Perhaps these symbols offers a clue to the identity of who or what is "
"behind the sudden appearance of these tombstones. You copy the symbols onto "
"a piece of parchment. Return to Krisathel, and report your finding to "
"Eredethil Swiftarrow."

