"interacting with it, to complete the fifth step."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4199"
msgstr ""
"As you cast the Mana Drain spell upon the demon tombstone, you feel a sudden "
"rush of energy leaving the demon tombstone. You have successfully removed "
"the magical properties from the demon tombstone. Return to {$l14}, and "
