msgstr ""
"You have succeeded in killing two Gray Ork Chieftain. Exit the {$j14} "
"dungeon and report your success to Mardem-kai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4379"
msgstr "You have handed the letter to Krushar Breakskull."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4381"
msgstr ""
"You have found a chest containing a very suspicious letter. Unfortunately, "
"as you quickly look through it, you notice that the letter is written in "
"some secret code that makes no sense to you. Deliver this find to Merdem-kai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4383"
msgstr "You have handed the coded letter to Mardem-kai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4385"
msgstr ""
"Among all the ruins of Neithstone Hall, you find a perfectly intact altar "
"with a bright fire burning on top of it. As you touch the mysterious altar, "
"you feel a faint magical current passing through your body. This altar could "
"possibly be the reason why the Menhir have gathered at Neithstone Hall. "
"Report this find to Isind-dai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4387"
msgstr ""
"Searching through the chest, you find fragments of an old map together with "
"instructions to search for an ancient artifact called the Night Stone. "
"Because of the maps poor condition, you cannot determine which parts of the "
"Tribelands are depicted on this incomplete map. Return to Isinda-dai and "
"report this important find."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4388"
msgstr "You have reached Isinda-dai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4394"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Gnolls. Return to Marden-kai to report "
"your success."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4396"
msgstr ""
"With a look of horror upon its face, the Ogre falls dead to the ground. You "
"have successfully killed three Ogres. Report your success to Marden-kai and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4398"
msgstr "You have reached Tamari the Arcanist."

msgid "finished_text_quest_44"
msgstr ""
"Swinging your pickaxe, you carve another fine piece of stone from the "
"boulder. You now have enough rock to claim a reward from Talaod the "
"Blacksmith in {$u19}."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4400"
msgstr ""
"You have found a beast totem that symbolized a raging brown bear in the "
"vicinity of the Forest Prophets. Perhaps this is the symbol that Tamari is "
"looking for. Return to Nightspire and report this find to Tamari the "
"Arcanist."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4401"
msgstr "You have reached Tamari the Arcanist."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4403"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully destroyed two of the Black Knight that guard the "
"floating island in {$n25}. Report your success to Dekazu Fearweaver and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4405"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed six Akathars and one Windlord. Report you "
"success to Thain Strongforge and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4407"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four of the Forest Prophets that have take over "
"the Order of the Axe's small logging camp in {$p12}. Report you success to "
"Thain Strongforge and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4409"
msgstr "You have reached Torgard the fighter."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4411"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have scored five successful melee hits against the training "
"dummies, and have almost completed your first training quest. Return to "
"Torgard the Fighter to report your success and to collect your rewards.\r\n"
"You must interact with the Torgard the Fighter using the F key to turn in "
"the quest and to collect your rewards."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4413"
msgstr ""
"Excellent. You have struck the archery targets using archery five times and "
"have almost completed your second training quest. Return to the Stonegar the "
"Fighter to report your success and to accept your rewards.\r\n"
"You must interact with the Stonegar the Fighter using the F key to turn in "
"the quest and to claim your rewards."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4415"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully used the Sprint skill. Now execute Torgard's next "
"skill, the Parry Skill by using the V key while equipped with a melee weapon."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4416"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully used the Parry skill. Now execute Torgard's next "
"skill, the Crouch Walk by using the C key while moving forward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4417"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully used the Crouch Walk skill. Now execute Torgard's next "
"skill, the Rest Skill, which you will find under General Skills."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4418"
msgstr ""
"As simple as it may be, you now know how to use the Rest skill. Report to "
"the Torgard the Fighter to accept your rewards, and any further tasks that "
"might be available to you."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4420"
msgstr "You have reached Jonn the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_4422"
