"have killed at least seven Hobgoblins. Report to Isinda-dai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_631"
msgstr ""
"You have removed enough of the Windlords, that Neithstone Hall may be used "
"again by the Wolfmasks. Report to Isinda-dai and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_633"
msgstr ""
"With a final roar, the huge and powerful Ravager crushes to the ground. "
"Return to Isinda-dai to report your success and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_635"
msgstr ""
"You have killed kill four Moonbeast Officers. Return to Wolfmask "
"headquarters and report to Mardem-Kai."

msgid "finished_text_quest_637"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully harvested two units of Baleful Venom Sac from the "
"Ghost Spiders. Return to Celetia the White and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_639"
msgstr "You have reached  Avarran-yth."

msgid "finished_text_quest_64"
msgstr ""
"Using your skinner, you extract the fourth tooth from the mouth of the dead "
"goblin. You may now return to Sandbrook in order to present your grisly "
"collection to William the Councillor."

msgid "finished_text_quest_641"
msgstr ""
"You have cleared out enough Revenants so Avarran-Yth may continue his work "
"and search for the scroll. Return to Avarran-Yth to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_643"
msgstr ""
"Dirt and stone is all that remains of the once fierce Earth Elemental. As "
"the dust settles, you retrieve the Quartz from the pile of rubble. Deliver "
"the Quartz to Avarran-yth and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_645"
msgstr ""
"As the fourth of the undead guardians crumbles to the ground, images of "
"ancient writings swirl in your mind. Return to Avarryn-yth so he may "
"complete the text."

msgid "finished_text_quest_647"
msgstr "You have handed the scroll to Celetia the White."

msgid "finished_text_quest_649"
msgstr ""
"You have killed at least six Svartdvergir. Return to Celetia the White to "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_651"
msgstr ""
"You have killed enough Crogs to harvest two Vile Horns. Return to Celetia "
"the White to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_653"
msgstr ""
"Another Ogre crushes to the ground. You have killed  four Ogre Bullies and "
"two Ogre Boss. Return to {$h12} to claim Celetia's reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_655"
msgstr ""
"As you cast the Mana Drain spell on the statue, a staff starts to form in "
"front of you in mid air. Images from Agon's mysterious past fill your mind. "
"You have found the Moonstaff of Knowledge. Return to the Circle of Neith to "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_656"
msgstr "You have handed the staff to Celetia the White."

msgid "finished_text_quest_658"
msgstr ""
"You have now killed enough Revenant for the Mages of the Radiant Circle to "
"begin there experiments. Return to Shulazu Nightshade to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_660"
msgstr ""
"You have finished removing enough blood from the Trolls. It was a bloody "
"job, but somebody had to do it. Return to Shulazu to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_662"
msgstr "You have located Naelah Ghostshard."

msgid "finished_text_quest_664"
msgstr ""
"The chest contains a large black book, which has its cover engraved with "
"blood red writings that read the Book of Greater Necromancy. As you hold the "
"book, you temporarily feel a sudden loss in strength, as if life itself was "
"leaving your body. Return the book to Nealah to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_665"
msgstr "You have handed the book to Naelah Ghostshard."

msgid "finished_text_quest_667"
msgstr ""
"Yet another trolls falls to the ground. You have killed six Trolls and two "
"Troll Shamans. Return to Naelah to claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_669"
msgstr "You have handed the book to Shulazu Nightshade."

msgid "finished_text_quest_671"
msgstr ""
"You have killed at least five Manscorpions. Return to Shulazu Nightshade to "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_673"
msgstr ""
"The massive Flesh Golem crushed to the ground, and pieces of rotting flesh "
"fall all around you. You have successfully extracted two units of Nightmare "
"Bile. Return to Sulazu Nightshade and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_675"
msgstr ""
"As you remove the skull, cries and screams fill the air around you. It "
"sounds as if a thousand voices are shouting at you, trying to stop you from "
"carrying out this sacrilegious act. Bring Kalruk's skull to Shalazu "
"Nightshade."

msgid "finished_text_quest_676"
msgstr "You have delivered Kalruk's skull to Shulazu Nightshade."

msgid "finished_text_quest_678"
msgstr ""
"You have managed to defeat four Severii in less than an hour. Return to "
"Nathar Blackorb."

msgid "finished_text_quest_68"
msgstr ""
"Your Mana Missile just hit another Goblin. Hopefully, this will serve to "
"remind them that human magic should be feared. Return to Allan the "
"Councillor to collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_680"
msgstr ""
"Blood and screams is all that remains in the forest area around you. You "
"have successfully taken the life from three Centaurs and three Ciel Fey. "
"Report to Nathar Blackorb and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_682"
msgstr "You have reached Kaldahan Deepshadow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_684"
msgstr ""
"Another hobgoblin falls to the ground. You have successfully killed the "
"Hobgoblins at the guardhouse. Kaldahan's men may start moving in. Report to "
"Kaldahan."

msgid "finished_text_quest_686"
msgstr ""
"You have killed three Jackal Revenants, three Hawk Revenants and two "
"Oathbound. Return to Kaldahan."

msgid "finished_text_quest_688"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Hobgoblin slumps to the ground, bathed in it's own warm blood. "
"You have killed five Hobgoblin Grunts, one Hobgoblin Veteran and one "
"Hobgoblin Officer. Report to Nathar Blackorb at the Temple of the God King, "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_690"
msgstr "You have reached Nathar Blackorb."

msgid "finished_text_quest_692"
msgstr ""
"With a low groan, the Oaklord crumbles to the ground. Wood and splinters is "
"all that remain from the once powerful forest guardian. Return to Nathar "
"Blackorb and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_696"
msgstr ""
"You have succeeded in putting four skeletons back to sleep in less that an "
"hour. Return to Eredethil Swiftarrow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_698"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Ciel Fey falls. You have now killed at least four Ciel Fey. "
"Return to Eredethil Swiftarrow and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_70"
msgstr ""
"Your Mana Missile just hit another Goblin. Hopefully, this will serve to "
"remind them that human magic should be feared. Return to William the "
"Councillor to collect your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_700"
msgstr ""
"With a low groan, another hobgoblin falls. You have now killed four "
"hobgoblins. Return to Eredethil Swiftarrow and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_702"
msgstr ""
"You have killed at least four Forest Prophets and successfully delivered the "
"message, that the Arrowhead will not tolerate their rebellious behavior. "
"Return to Eredethil Swiftarrow and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_704"
msgstr ""
"Yet another hobgoblin falls to the ground. You have successfully killed four "
"Hobgoblin Grunts, one Hobgoblin Veteran and one Hobgoblin Officer. Return to "
"Eredethil Swiftarrow and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_706"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed at least four Beastman. Return to  Eredethil "
"Swiftarrow and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_708"
msgstr "You have reached Seirinna the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_710"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Ciel Fey falls to the ground. You have successfully killed six "
"Ciel Feys. Return to Seirinna the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_712"
msgstr ""
"As you cast the Mana Drain spell onto the statue, a secret compartment opens "
"and reveals the Orb of Disease to you. Immediately, you can feel the deadly "
"power of the Orb weakening your body. Quickly deliver the Orb of Disease to "
"Seirinna the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_713"
msgstr "You have handed the dangerous orb to Seirinna the Mage."

msgid "finished_text_quest_715"
msgstr "You have reached Eredethil Swiftarrow."

msgid "finished_text_quest_717"
msgstr ""
"You have managed to kill enough trolls to harvest three units of Timeless "
"Blood. Return to Aelathil Silverleaf and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_719"
msgstr ""
"You have killed four centaurs and successfully sent the rest running into "
"the ambush. Return to Aelathil Silverleaf and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_721"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Sadayel falls to the ground. You have now killed at least four "
"Sadayel. Return to Aelathil Silverleaf and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_723"
msgstr ""
"You have killed at least four Forest Prophets. Return to Aelathil Silverleaf."

msgid "finished_text_quest_725"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully located the Sacred Tree. Return to Aelathil Silverleaf "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_727"
msgstr ""
"Yet another undead dwarf falls to the ground. Something seems to gleam on "
"one of it's fingers. It is the Ring of Crystals. Return to Aelathil "
"Silverleaf and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_728"
msgstr "You have delivered the Ring of Crystals to Aelathil Silverleaf."

msgid "finished_text_quest_730"
msgstr ""
"You have managed to gather three units of Elemental Cinder.  A few burning "
"remains are all that is left of the Lesser Fire Elementals. Return to "
"Aelathil Silverleaf and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_732"
msgstr ""
"Scattered bones are all that remains from the Giant Skeletons. You have "
"successfully destroyed six Giant Skeletons. Return to Aelathil Silverleaf "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_734"
msgstr ""
"With a final growl, another beastman falls. You have killed at five "
"beastmen. Return to  Aelathil Silverleaf."

msgid "finished_text_quest_736"
msgstr ""
"With a loud thud, another Hill Giant crushes to the ground. You have now "
"killed four Hill Giant Sluggers. Return to Symyr-dan and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_737"
msgstr ""
"As the last of the humans falls, you discover a letter in his possession. "
"You pick it up at quickly read through it. It is a letter that contains "
"information regarding specific mahirim patrol routes. Report this find to "
"Symyr-dan the Firm."

msgid "finished_text_quest_738"
msgstr "You have handed the letter to Symyr-dan the Firm."

msgid "finished_text_quest_740"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed three Troll Lords in less than half an hour. "
"Return to Symyr-dan and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_742"
msgstr ""
"Another Svartdvergir falls to the ground. You have killed five Svartdvergir. "
"Return to Symyr-dan and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_744"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Night Hags falls. You have now killed at least four Night Hags. "
"Return to Symyr-dan and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_746"
msgstr ""
"You have found the lost half of the sacred stone tablet. Return it to Symyr-"
"dan and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_747"
msgstr "You have delivered the lost half of the sacred tablet to Symyr-dan."

msgid "finished_text_quest_750"
msgstr ""
"Yet, another of the undead crumbles to the ground. You have now destroyed "
"two skeletons, two zombies and one Gravelord. Return it to Symyr-dan and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_752"
msgstr ""
"You have now harvested two Quartz. Return it to Symyr-dan and claim your "
"reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_754"
msgstr ""
"You have killed two Night Hags. Report to Aeshanta Darkspire and claim your "
"reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_756"
msgstr ""
"With a loud thud, another Ogre falls to the ground. You have kill at least "
"four Ogres. Return to Aeshanta Darkspire and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_758"
msgstr "You have reached Lashur Wraithglider."

msgid "finished_text_quest_760"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Severii crumble to the ground. All that remains is a pile of "
"bones. Return to Lashur with your assessment of their strength."

msgid "finished_text_quest_762"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully found the Holy Symbol of Melek. As you pick up the "
"amulet, inside the chest you also find a map. It is a detailed map of the "
"Alfar capital city {$n23}. You must return to Lashur Wraithglider an report "
"about this disturbing finding."

msgid "finished_text_quest_763"
msgstr ""
"You have handed the Holy Symbol of Melek and the map of Shoal to Lashur "
"Wraithglider."

msgid "finished_text_quest_765"
msgstr ""
"Yet another Severii crumbles to the ground. All that remains is a pile of "
"bones. Return to Lashur Wraithglider and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_767"
msgstr "You have reached Aeshanta Darkspire."

msgid "finished_text_quest_769"
msgstr ""
"You have killed  two Hill Giant Sluggers and four Ogre Bosses. Return to to "
"Aeshanta Darkspire and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_771"
msgstr ""
"You have killed enough Trolls to harvest three units of Timeless Blood. "
"Return to to Aeshanta Darkspire and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_773"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed seven Severii and one Gravelord. Return to to "
"Aeshanta Darkspire and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_781"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four gnolls. Report to Caradial Elmheart at the "
"Emerald Throne and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_782"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed five akathars. Return to the Emerald Throne and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_783"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully destroyed four revenants. Return to the Emerald Throne "
"and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_784"
msgstr ""
"You have killed at least five Forest Prophets. Return to Caradial Elmheart "
"at the Emerald Throne and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_785"
msgstr ""
"You discover a hidden compartment at the base of the statue. Inside it you "
"find an orb. As you pick it up in your hands, hundreds of images of "
"historical events from Mirendil's past flash before your eyes. Return the "
"orb of history to the Emerald Throne and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_786"
msgstr "You have handed the orb to Caradial Elmheart."

msgid "finished_text_quest_787"
msgstr ""
"All around you lie the remains of undead pirates. You have killed at least "
"three Bonecrew Mutineers and one Bonecrew Mariner. Return to the Emerald "
"Throne and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_788"
msgstr ""
"You have found the second orb of history. As you look into the orb, hundreds "
"of images of Mirendil's past swirl in your mind. Return the orb of history "
"to the Emerald Throne and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_789"
msgstr "You have handed the orb to Caradial Elmheart."

msgid "finished_text_quest_790"
msgstr ""
"You have killed at least kill two Raven Standard Grunts and one Raven "
"Standard Veteran. Return to the Emerald Throne and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_799"
msgstr ""
"All around you lie remains of the once deadly doom spiders. You have "
"successfully killed three Doom Spiders. Return to Yaleria-Sai the Able and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_800"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Gnolls. Return to Yaleria-Sai the Able and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_801"
msgstr ""
"Another Ogre crushes to the ground. You have killed four Ogre Bullies and "
"two Ogre Bosses. Return to Yaleria-Sai the Able and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_802"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Moonbeast Disciples and two Moonbeast "
"Berserkers. Return to Yaleria-Sai the Able and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_803"
msgstr ""
"All around you lie the scattered remains of undead pirates. You have killed "
"at least six Bonecrew Mutineers. Return to Yaleria-Sai the Able and claim "
"your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_804"
msgstr ""
"All around you lie the scattered remains of the skeletons. Return to Yaleria-"
"Sai the Able and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_805"
msgstr ""
"You have gathered two Tribal Lifeforce. Return to Yaleria-Sai the Able and "
"claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_806"
msgstr ""
"With a terrifying scream, another hobgoblin falls to the ground. You have "
"now killed  five Hobgoblin Veterans and two Hobgoblin Officers. Return to "
"Yaleria-Sai the Able and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_815"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed three Raven Standard Hobgoblins. Return to the "
"Elders of {$j12}, and report to Symyr-dan the Firm your assessment of the "
"hobgoblin war group."

msgid "finished_text_quest_817"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully killed four Manscorpions. Return to Dekazu Fearweaver."

msgid "finished_text_quest_818"
msgstr ""
"Dirt and stone is all that remains of the once fierce Earth Elemental. As "
"the dust settles, you retrieve the Elemental Quartz from the pile of rubble. "
"Deliver the Elemental Quartz to Dekazu Fearweaver and claim your reward."

msgid "finished_text_quest_819"
msgstr ""
"All that is left of the undead dwarves is rotting flesh and bones. You have "
"successfully destroyed at least five undead dwarves. Return to Dekazu "
"Fearweaver."

msgid "finished_text_quest_820"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully located the shrine, and retrieved the artifact. It is "
"a dwarven rune stone. As you hold it in your hands, you feel the raw power "
"of the unknown god trying to sway you to it cause, with images of power and "
"glory. Return the rune stone to Dekazu Fearweaver."

msgid "finished_text_quest_821"
msgstr "You have delivered the artifact to Dekazu Fearweaver."

msgid "finished_text_quest_822"
msgstr ""
"You have successfully retrieved the artifact known as Durganon's Flame from "
"the Chamber of Fire. Return to the Shadow Salient and deliver the artifact "
"to Dekazu Fearweaver."

msgid "finished_text_quest_823"
msgstr "You have delivered Durganon's Flame to Dekazu Fearweaver."

