"Anybody who can kill at least seven Revenant within an hour will be well "
"rewarded. But, that is not all. Any Revenant killed beyond the seven "
"required for the hunt, will also result in a higher reward.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Well, what do you think? Do you have what I takes to kill more than seven "
"Revenants within an hour? And how many can you kill? \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The duration of the hunt is one hour. No participants will be able to "
"collect their reward before the end of the time limit."

msgid "start_text_quest_2728"
msgstr ""
"The Niasha Manscorpion Hunt. You must kill at least ten manscorpions in less "
"than an hour. The more manscorpions you kill, the higher the reward.\n"
"(Warning: Rewards are given at the end of the time limit. Countdown "
"continues even after logging out)."

msgid "start_text_quest_2729"
msgstr ""
"The pathetic manscorpions that occupy the connecting islands to the north of "
"here, have somewhat become a nuisance lately. The Shadow Masters of the "
"Shadow Salient have requested that the be eliminated. Therefor we have "
"issued a manscorpion hunt. Therefor we have issued a troll hunt.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Anybody who can kill at least ten manscorpions within an hour will be well "
"rewarded. But that is not all. With every kill beyond the ten required for "
"the hunt, a little more will be added to the reward.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Well, what do you think? Do you have what I takes to kill more than ten "
"manscorpions within an hour? And how many can you kill? \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The duration of the hunt is one hour. No participants will be able to "
"collect their reward before the end of the time limit."

msgid "start_text_quest_2730"
msgstr ""
"The Gul Kral Ogre Hunt. You must kill at least ten ogres in less than an "
"hour. The more ogres you kill, the higher the reward.\n"
"(Warning: Rewards are given at the end of the time limit. Countdown "
"continues even after logging out)."

msgid "start_text_quest_2731"
msgstr ""
"Our patrols have been wasting too much time dealing with the annoying Ogres "
"in the Gul Kral region, instead of focusing on patrolling the borders of "
"Nagast. This nonsense must end. Therefor we have issued an Ogre Hunt.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Anybody who can kill at least ten ogres within an hour will be well "
"rewarded. But that is not all. For any kills beyond the ten required for the "
"hunt, a little more will be added to the reward.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Well, what do you think? Do you have what I takes to kill more than ten "
"ogres within an hour? And how many can you kill? \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The duration of the hunt is one hour. No participants will be able to "
"collect their reward before the end of the time limit"

msgid "start_text_quest_2732"
msgstr ""
"The Mjoldenar Ogre Hunt. You must kill at least ten ogres in less than an "
"hour. The more ogres you kill, the higher the reward.\n"
"(Warning: Rewards are given at the end of the time limit. Countdown "
"continues even after logging out)."

msgid "start_text_quest_2733"
msgstr ""
"In the Mjoldenar region to the west of here, an ogre warband has established "
"camps on both sides of the valley, making impossible for most to travel "
"through. Although a military expedition against the ogres is soon to begin, "
"we an all help be killing as many as possible. Therefor we have issued a "
"ogre hunt.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Anybody who can kill at least ten ogres within an hour will be well "
"rewarded. But there is more. For every ogre killed beyond the ten required "
"for the hunt, a little more will be added to the reward.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Do you have what I takes to kill more than ten ogres within an hour? And how "
"many can you kill? \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The duration of the hunt is one hour. No participants will be able to "
"collect their reward before the end of the time limit."

msgid "start_text_quest_2734"
msgstr ""
"The Gorodron Hobgoblin Hunt. You must kill at least seven hobgoblins in less "
"than an hour. The more hobgoblins you kill, the higher the reward.\n"
"(Warning: Rewards are given at the end of the time limit. Countdown "
"continues even after logging out)."

msgid "start_text_quest_2735"
msgstr ""
"We have information that a hobgoblin army is slowly gathering to the north "
"of here in Gorodron. Although a military campaign is being prepared to deal "
"with this growing threat, all brave adventurers are welcomed to help. "
"Therefor we have issued a hobgoblin hunt.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Anybody who can kill at least seven hobgoblins within an hour will be well "
"rewarded. But, there is more. For every hobgoblin killed beyond the seven "
"required for the hunt, a little more will be added to the reward.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Well, what do you think? Do you have what I takes to kill more than seven "
"hobgoblins within an hour? And how many can you kill? \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The duration of the hunt is one hour. No participants will be able to "
"collect their reward before the end of the time limit."

msgid "start_text_quest_2736"
msgstr ""
"The Shadowbourne Hill Giant Hunt. You must kill at least five hill giants in "
"less than an hour. The more hill giants you kill, the higher the reward.\n"
"(Warning: Rewards are given at the end of the time limit. Countdown "
"continues even after logging out)."

msgid "start_text_quest_2737"
msgstr ""
"The war-ravaged region of Shadowbourne to the southeast of here, is overrun "
"by a clan of fierce Hill Giants. These Hill Giants are too unpredictable to "
"be left wondering freely at our borders. Therefor we have issued a Hill "
"Giant Hunt, to rid Morak of their presence.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Anybody who can kill at least five hill giants within an hour will be well "
"rewarded. But, there is more. For every hill giant killed beyond the five "
"required for the hunt, a little more will be added to the reward.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Well, what do you think? Do you have what I takes to kill more than five "
"hill giants within an hour? And how many can you kill? \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The duration of the hunt is one hour. No participants will be able to "
"collect their reward before the end of the time limit."

msgid "start_text_quest_2738"
msgstr ""
"The Laurgul Kobold Strongman Hunt. You must kill at least ten kobold "
"strongmen in less than an hour. The more kobold strongmen you kill, the "
"higher the reward.\n"
"(Warning: Rewards are given at the end of the time limit. Countdown "
"continues even after logging out)."

msgid "start_text_quest_2739"
msgstr ""
"The Kobold Strongmen that are based to the north of here in the Laurgul "
"region, are among the strongest and most fierce of the kobold race one may "
"come across. It is vital that we drive these impressively strong kobolds out "
"of northern Morak, before they become a threat to our trading routes and "
"local nearby communities. Therefor we have issued the Laurgul Kobold "
"Strongman Hunt.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Anybody who can destroy at least ten kobold strongmen within an hour, will "
"be well rewarded. But that is not all. For every kobold strongman killed "
"beyond the ten required for the hunt, a little more will be added to the "
"reward.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Well, what do you think? Do you have what I takes to kill more than ten "
"kobold strongmen within an hour? And how many can you kill? \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The duration of the hunt is one hour. No participants will be able to "
"collect their reward before the end of the time limit."

msgid "start_text_quest_2740"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Sylanae the Councillor. Kill three Mahirim "
"player characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2741"
msgstr ""
"I welcome you to Charybdis, the mirdain capital city here in the heart of "
"Mirendil. It is here within the vast Miredil forest of southwest Agon, that "
"we mirdain have lived for thousands of years our peaceful lives.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Agon is a vast world, and many other races dwell upon it too. Among those "
"races, there are the those that we have come to call our allies. Allies such "
"as the Humans of Mercia and the Dwarves of Dvergheim. But there are also "
"those races, which unfortunately we name as our enemies. Races such as the "
"Mahirim of the Tribelands to the north of Mirendil, the Alfar of Nagast to "
"the southeast of Mirendil, and the filthy Orks of Morak far to the "
"northeast. It is with these enemies that we and our allies are at constants "
"war with, my friend.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, if you are to survive upon Agon, you must be ready to do "
"battle with these blood-thirsty enemies. You must learn to strike out "
"without any remorse or fear at those who wish to harm us, and not just sit "
"within these cities walls living a life of ignorance, or even worse, full of "
"fear.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"First, I will ask of you to strike out at the mahirim of the Tribelands to "
"the north of Mirendil. This primitive race of wolf-like predators, have only "
"recently earned the right to call themselves a civilized race, but their "
"actions are anything but civilized. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The mahirim are growing bolder day by day, and our scouts are reporting that "
"the mahirim raids inside our borders have lately increased.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Your task will be to find and kill at least three of them. It may sound as a "
"small number, but if all mirdain do their part, we will eventually drive the "
"mahirim out of our lands.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and slay three mahirim."

msgid "start_text_quest_2742"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Sylanae the Councillor. Kill three Alfar "
"player characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2743"
msgstr ""
"Now that you have confronted the primitive mahirim, it is time for you to "
"strike against the sinister alfar. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The alfar are our most hated enemy. The are an abomination, and a disgrace "
"to any mirdain. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Under the guidance of their twisted god Melek, the alfar have been molded "
"into a dark and hateful race, that only seek to destroy all life upon Agon. "
"Their goal, and that of course of their god Melek, is total domination of "
"Agon. For them, there is no room for any other race. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to seek out and kill three alfar. Do not feel "
"anything for these dark twisted creatures. Remember, they are a race of pure "
"evil.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and kill three alfar."

msgid "start_text_quest_2744"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Allan the Councillor. Kill three Ork player "
"characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2745"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. You have reached Sanguine, the human capital city located in the "
"heart of Mercia. It is here within the borders of Mercia, that we humans "
"live our everyday lives, under the guiding light of Auros.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Agon is a vast world, and we are but one of the many races that dwell upon "
"it. Among Agon's many races, there are the those that we have come to call "
"our allies. Allies such as the Mirdain of Miredil and the Dwarves of "
"Dvergheim. But there are also those, which unfortunately we name as our "
"enemies. Races such as the Orks of Morak to the north of Mercia, the Alfar "
"of Nagast to the southwest of Mercia, and the primitive Mahirim of the "
"tribelands far to the northwest. It is with these enemies that we and our "
"allies are at constants war at, my fellow Mercian.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, if you are to survive upon Agon, you must be ready to do "
"battle with these blood-thirsty enemies. You must learn to strike out "
"without any fear at those who wish to harm us, and not sit within the safety "
"of city walls living a life of ignorance, or even worse, a life full of fear."
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"First, I will ask of you to strike out at the orks of Morak to the north of "
"Mercia. The orks, a race that live for the thrill of battle, are convinced "
"that through pure brute strength they will eventually concur all of Agon, "
"while enslaving all the other races, including us humans. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"One thing the orks are not aware of, is that we humans are a stubborn race. "
"We might be a good and talk nice, but when our cities, our people and our "
"way of life are threatened, we will fight back, and fight back hard!\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Your task will be to find and kill at least three orks. It may sound as a "
"small number, but if all us Mercians do our part, we will eventually weaken "
"the orks, and send a clear message to them, to stay out of our lands!\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and slay three orks."

msgid "start_text_quest_2746"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Allan the Councillor. Kill three Alfar player "
"characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2747"
msgstr ""
"Now that you have confronted the stupid orks, it is time for you to strike "
"against the sinister alfar. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Under the guidance of their twisted god Melek, the alfar have be molded into "
"a dark and hateful race, that only seek to destroy all life upon Agon. Their "
"goal, and that of course of their god Melek, is total domination of Agon. "
"For them, there is no room for any other race. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to seek out and kill three alfar. Do not feel "
"anything for these dark twisted creatures. Remember, they are a race of pure "
"evil.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and kill three alfar."

msgid "start_text_quest_2748"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Ordgrim the Councillor. Kill three Ork player "
"characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2749"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. You have reached Ymir's Tear, the dwarven capital city located in "
"the heart of Dvergheim. It is here within the borders of Dvergheim that we "
"dwarves under the guidance of Ymir, have lived for thousands of years, and "
"intent to live here for thousands more to come.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Agon is a vast world, and we are but one of the many races that dwell upon "
"it. Among the many races, there are the those that we have come to call our "
"allies. Allies such as the mirdain of Miredil and the humans of Mercia. But "
"there are also those, which unfortunately for them, we name as our enemies. "
"Races such as the orks of Morak to the southeast of Dvergheim, the mahirim "
"of the Tribelands to the southwest of Dvergheim, and the dark sinister alfar "
"of Nagast far to the south. It is with these enemies that we and our allies "
"are at constants war at, my friend.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, if you are to survive upon Agon, you must be ready to do "
"battle with these blood-thirsty enemies. You must learn to strike out, "
"without any remorse of fear at those who wish to harm us, and not sit within "
"the safety of city walls living a life of ignorance, or even worse, a life "
"full of fear.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"First, I will ask of you to strike against the orks of Morak to the "
"southeast of Dvergheim. The orks, a race that live for the thrill of battle, "
"are convinced that through pure brute strength they will eventually concur "
"all of Agon, while enslaving all the other races, including us dwarves. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"One thing the orks are not aware of, is that we dwarves are a stubborn race. "
"We might be a nice and good, but when our cities, our people and our way of "
"life are threatened, we will fight back, and fight back hard!\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Your task will be to find and kill at least three orks. It may sound as a "
"small number, but if all do our part, we will eventually weaken the orks, "
"and send a clear message to them, to stay out of our lands!\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and slay three orks."

msgid "start_text_quest_2750"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Ordgrim the Councillor. Kill three Mahirim "
"player characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2751"
msgstr ""
"Now that you have confronted the stupid orks, it is time for you to strike "
"against the primitive mahirim. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The mahirim, a race of wolf-like predators, have only recently earned the "
"right to call themselves a civilized race, if one can call these two-legged "
"wolves anything but civilized. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The mahirim are growing bolder day by day, and our scouts are reporting that "
"the mahirim raids inside our borders have lately increased.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to seek out and kill three mahirim. Remember, the "
"mahirim are a wild and primitive race, so be well prepared to do some "
"serious battle.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and kill three mahirim."

msgid "start_text_quest_2752"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Tivasta the Councillor. Kill three Mirdain "
"player characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2753"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. You have reached Red Moon, the mahirim capital city located in the "
"heart of the Tribelands. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"It is here within the Tribelands that the prophet-warrior Amurran united "
"many of the heartland tribes under his rule, and laid the foundations for "
"today's modern mahirim society. And it is our duty, to continue the work of "
"the prophet-king Amurran, by following his teachings\r\n"
"\r\n"
"But the Tribelands are only a part of the vast world of Agon, and we are "
"only but one of the many races that dwell upon it. Among those races, there "
"are those that have seen the growing power of the mahirim, and have accepted "
"to form an alliance with us. It is the Orks of Morak who have seen and "
"understand how powerful the united tribes of the heartland are, and wisely "
"enough have allied themselves with us.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"But there are also those races, which foolishly have become our enemies. "
"Races such as the Mirdain of Mirendil to the south of the Tribelands, the "
"Dwarves of Dvergheim to the northeast of the Tribelands, and the Humans of "
"Mercia far to the southeast. It is with these enemies that we and our allies "
"are at constants war with, my friend.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, if you are to survive upon Agon, you must be ready to do "
"battle with these foolish enemies of ours. You must learn to strike out, "
"without any fear at those who wish to harm us, and not sit within the safety "
"of city walls living a life of ignorance, or even worse, a life full of fear."
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"First, you will strike against the mirdain of Mirendil to the south of the "
"Tribelands. The mirdain, a pathetic weak ancient race, that continue "
"foolishly to live by their ancient ways, blindly refusing to accept the "
"growing power of our race. It is time for them to learn the hard way!\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Your task will be to seek out and kill at least three mirdain. It may sound "
"as a small number, but if we all do our part, the mirdain will eventually "
"listen, and understand that their time is almost over, and that the mahirim "
"are here to concur! \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and slay three mirdain."

msgid "start_text_quest_2754"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Tivasta the Councillor. Kill three Dwarven "
"player characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2755"
msgstr ""
"Now that you have confronted the weak mirdain, it is time for you to strike "
"against the stubborn dwarves. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The dwarves, although a short-statured race, that make up for what they lack "
"in height with raw strength and endurance. But most importantly, from all "
"the pathetic races on Agon that refuse to join the growing power of the "
"mahirim, the dwarves are the most stubborn, proud and battle ready.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"These annoying short neighbors of ours from the northeast, seem to not enjoy "
"the idea of a powerful mahirim nation. Our scouts have reported about "
"spotting dwarven scouting parties entering the Tribelands and attacking many "
"of our settlements and disrupting our trade routes. This is an outrage!\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to seek out and kill three dwarves. Remember, the "
"dwarves are a  hardy and stubborn race that also enjoy a good battle, so be "
"well prepared to do some serious hunting.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and kill three dwarves."

msgid "start_text_quest_2756"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Izkruul the Councillor. Kill three Human "
"player characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2757"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. You have reached Flaming Skull, the ork capital city located in the "
"heart of Morak. It is from here within the borders of Morak, that we orks "
"will begin our march across the whole of Agon, to concur all. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Agon is a vast world, and many other races dwell upon it. Among those races, "
"there are those that have seen the growing power of the orks, and have "
"wisely accepted to form an alliance with us. It is the Mahirim of the "
"Tribelands who have seen and understand the power that our nation wields, "
"and wisely enough have allied themselves with us.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"But there are also those races, which foolishly have become our enemies. "
"Races such as the Humans of Mercia to the south of Morak, the Dwarves of "
"Dvergheim to the northwest of Morak, and the Mirdain of Mirendil far to the "
"southwest. It is with these enemies that we and our allies are at constants "
"war with, my friend.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, if you are to survive upon Agon, you must be ready to do "
"battle with these foolish enemies of ours. You must learn to strike out, "
"without any fear at those who wish to stand in our way, and not sit within "
"the safety of city walls living out a pathetic weak life, or even worse, a "
"life full of fear.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"First, you will strike against the humans of Mercia to the south of Morak. "
"The humans, the pathetic weak race they are, continue foolishly to not "
"accept the growing power of our race. Can they not understand that they are "
"doomed? Is it because of the blinding light of their pathetic sun god? "
"Hahahaha! Whatever the reason, it is time for them to learn the hard way!\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Your task will be to seek out and kill at least three humans. It may sound "
"as a small number, but as we all do our part, the humans will eventually "
"see, and understand that their time is almost over, and that the orks are on "
"their way to concur all! \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and slay three humans."

msgid "start_text_quest_2758"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Izkruul the Councillor. Kill three Dwarven "
"player characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2759"
msgstr ""
"Now that you have confronted the weak humans, it is time for you to strike "
"against the stubborn dwarves. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The dwarves, although a short-statured race, that make up for what they lack "
"in height with raw strength and endurance. But most importantly, from all "
"the pathetic races on Agon that refuse to join the growing power of the "
"orks, the dwarves are the most stubborn, proud and battle ready.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"These annoying short neighbors of ours from the northwest, seem to not enjoy "
"the idea of a powerful ork nation. Our scouts have reported spotting dwarven "
"scouting parties entering Morak and attacking many of our settlements and "
"disrupting our trade routes. This is an outrage!\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to seek out and kill three dwarves. Remember, the "
"dwarves are a  hardy and stubborn race that also enjoy a good battle, so be "
"well prepared.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and kill three dwarves."

msgid "start_text_quest_2760"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Ensharra the Councillor. Kill three Human "
"player characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2761"
msgstr ""
"Welcome. You have reached Shoal, the alfar capital city located in the heart "
"of Nagast. It is from here within the borders of Nagast, under the guidance "
"of Melek, we the superior alfar will begin our quest to concur all of Agon, "
"while eliminating anybody that dares to stand in our way! \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Agon is a vast world, and many other races dwell upon it. Among the many "
"races, none have been found worthy to form any kind of alliance with. All of "
"them pathetic, and all of the weak. We are at constant war with, the Humans "
"of Mercia to the northest of Nagast, the Mirdain of Mirendil to the "
"northwest of Nagast, the Orks of Morak far to the northeast, the Mahirim of "
"the Tribelands far to the northwest, and the Dwarves of Dvergheim for to the "
"north. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, if you are to survive upon Agon, you must be ready to do "
"battle with these foolish enemies of ours. You must learn to strike out, "
"without any fear at those who wish to stand in our way, and not sit within "
"the safety of city walls living out a pathetic weak life, or even worse, a "
"life full of fear.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Your task will be to seek out and kill at least three humans. It may sound "
"as a small number, but as we all do our part, the humans will eventually see "
"and understand that their time is almost over, and that the alfar will "
"conquer all. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and slay three humans."

msgid "start_text_quest_2762"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Ensharra the Councillor. Kill three Mirdain "
"player characters."

msgid "start_text_quest_2763"
msgstr ""
"Now that you have confronted the pathetic humans, it is time for you to "
"strike against the worst of  our enemies. The mirdain. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"The mirdain are our most hated enemy. Their mere existence if an insult to "
"the alfar. Under the guidance of their twisted gods, who's names I will not "
"mention, the mirdain have be brainwashed into a paranoid weak race, that "
"only live to stand in the way our Melek's quest, which is to concur and rule "
"all of Agon.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"The mirdain, the pathetic weak race the are, continue foolishly to ignore "
"the inevitable. That their time is over, and very soon they will all find "
"death, at the end of an alfar blade! It is time for them to die!\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to seek out and kill three mirdain. Use any means "
"possible to inflict the largest amounts of pain you can upon them. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Go now, and kill three mirdain."

msgid "start_text_quest_2764"
msgstr ""
"Silawen the Councillor has asked you to report to Merthir the Merchant."

msgid "start_text_quest_2765"
msgstr ""
"I have just received word from Merthir the Merchant, that some of our "
"caravans have been delayed because of the goblin hordes. I want you to "
"report to Merthir, and see if there is anything you can do to help him."

msgid "start_text_quest_2766"
msgstr ""
"Merthir the Merchant has asked you to gather four pieces of leather from the "
"goblins."

msgid "start_text_quest_2767"
msgstr ""
"I have received word that one of our caravans has been attacked by the "
"goblin hordes, and therefor greatly delaying the delivery of specific "
"materials I have ordered. One of those materials is leather, that can be "
"used in the creation of numerous items.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"From what I have been told, many of the annoying goblins have been seen "
"carrying some of those leather pieces I have been expecting. #PlayerName#, I "
"want those pieces of leather delivered here to me as soon as possible.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"You could help me by hunting down a few of goblins and looting off them four "
"pieces of leather. In return, I will later on teach you some basic cooking "
"skills and also provide you with right tools needed. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"So #PlayerName#, will you help by bringing back to me four pieces of leather "
"from those stinking goblins?"

msgid "start_text_quest_2768"
msgstr ""
"Merthir the Merchant has asked you to catch a trout and then cook it, using "
"the oven in Leafhelm. Once you have cooked the trout, return to Merthir with "
"the cooked trout to collected your reward."

msgid "start_text_quest_2769"
msgstr ""
"Life might seems relatively easy and safe to you, while you are close to "
"Leafhelm, but venture a little further out, and you will discover that Agon "
"can be a very dangerous world. There will come times that you will need a "
"little extra help in regaining health or stamina, to be able to overcome "
"many of the difficult life threatening situations you may come across.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"As I said earlier, I would teach you some basic skills. So, what about "
"catching some fish and then cooking them? I suggest a trout for this lesson. "
"It might not sound that exiting, or promising as drinking a magical potion, "
"but it is a good source of nourishment that will help you recover. Also, "
"cooking is not that difficult, so why not learn it.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"One thing you will need is a fishing rod. If you don't have any of these, "
"which I did give you earlier, you can always buy one from me.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"First, you will have to catch a trout. When standing near water, equip "
"yourself with the fishing rod. Then, slightly standing in the water, aim you "
"crosshair in the water and begin fishing. If you don't succeed catching a "
"fish the first time, just try again. There are many different kinds of fish "
"you might catch.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Once you have caught a trout, next step will be to cook it. Return to "
"Leafhelm, and search for the oven. You will find it the central plaza with "
"most of the other workstations, near Ciredan the Blacksmith. You will also "
"recognize it from the banner with the loaf of bread and wheat on it. While "
"unarmed, stand in front of the oven. Make sure you have with you in your "
"backpack the trout. Then while targeting the oven use the action button to "
"begin. From the list of recipes that appear, select the one that "
"corespondents to the fish you have caught. It will also be highlighted. If "
"your cooking skills fail you just try again. So I recommend that you catch "
"more than one fish just to avoid the running around. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"When you have successfully cooked you meal, return to me with the cooked "
"trout."

