msgid "start_text_quest_3559"
msgstr ""
"Ayrdyr-dan the Mage has asked you to report to Samalom-tai the Mage of the "
"Circle of Neith, where you may be able to earn further intelligence "
"achievement titles."

msgid "start_text_quest_356"
msgstr ""
"The flint used in goblin axes is rare in this part of Dvergheim, and since "
"their tools are primitive and their skills rudimentary, goblins are unable "
"to make weapons from other, harder types of material. For these reasons, "
"looting goblin axes is an effective way of limiting the size of their armies."
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"To access a fallen goblin's possessions, you must first be unarmed. Then "
"while targeting the remains, use the action button. You may then drag items "
"from his backpack and into yours. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"I want you to bring me two goblin axes."

msgid "start_text_quest_3560"
msgstr ""
"The title of The Clever is only the first of the intelligence achievement "
"titles that can be earned. If you wish to gain titles that will give your "
"further bonuses to your intelligence, travel to Moonclaw and talk to Samalom-"
"tai the Mage of the Circle of Neith."

msgid "start_text_quest_3561"
msgstr ""
