msgid "start_text_quest_3581"
msgstr ""
"Thain Strongforge has asked you to report to Reiknir the Merchant, and see "
"if you can help with the mysterious bear attacks."

msgid "start_text_quest_3582"
msgstr ""
"We have received reports that  bears have being seen attacking caravans "
"along the trade routes. This is very strange. Why would the bears be "
"attacking our caravans?\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Although I don't see this as a serious problem, I want you report to Reiknir "
"the Merchant, and see if there is anything you can do to help."

msgid "start_text_quest_3583"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Reiknir the Merchant. Kill three of the "
"elusive brown bears that have been attacking the merchants."

msgid "start_text_quest_3584"
msgstr ""
"Very strange reports have arrived lately from merchants arriving here at "
"Stonevault, that brown bears have been attacking the trade routes. We've had "
"goblins, trolls, ogres, hobgoblins, gnolls, even giants attacking trading "
"caravans, but never bears before.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Our scouts have tried to locate these brown bears, but to no avail. Anybody "
"that can find and kill at least three brown bears, will be well rewarded. If "
"you want to help, find these brown bears, and kill three of them."

