"armadillo can be harvested for their meat. #PlayerName#, meat is one of the "
"main sources of food for the majority of our people, and we must keep our "
"people fed and happy.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"You can help us gather the meat we need, by gathering six units of meat. "
"Hunting either fox, armadillo, or any other animal does not really matter. "
"If you accept, you will have to track down the prey yourself. I cannot mark "
"their exact location on your map, because most of these animal are always on "
"the move. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Bring back six units of meat, and you will be rewarded well for your "
"services. Don't forget to take along your skinning knife."

