msgid "start_text_quest_3757"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to have your archery skills put to the test by Meadhin the "
"Fighter. You must succeed in hitting the goblins twenty times with your "
"arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3758"
msgstr ""
"The bows and arrows you brought in earlier, are already being put to good "
"use by our young archers. King's Holdfast's next batch of archers will be "
"ready in no time.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Archery plays a very important part in warfare. When one is well trained in "
"the art of archery, that one will have a huge advantage against his enemy. "
"While attacking, the archer has the opportunity of scoring many hits against "
"the enemy, before resorting to hand to hand combat. Hits that will have "
"tipped the balance of the battle's outcome to his or hers favor. But the "
"archer is also vital to the protection of a town and its people. Archery "
"combined with the protection of solid strong walls, is very difficult and in "
"some cases impossible to overcome.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, do you wish to have your archery skills put to the test? I "
"would very much like to see your skills with the bow. If you agree, I have a "
"simple test for you. All you need to do, is to score twenty successful hits "
"against the goblins only by using archery. Hit the goblins twenty times with "
"your arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3759"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Merthir the Merchant. Bring back to Merthir "
"six unit of meat, from either hunting deer, fox or any other animal. You "
"will need a skinner for this quest."

msgid "start_text_quest_3760"
msgstr ""
"The hunters of our town are preparing for the annual meat hunt. Groups of "
"deer and fox, travel through our lands this time of year. You can understand "
"how difficult it is to pass by such an opportunity, to hunt these animals "
"for their meat.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Hunting wild game for meat not only is a way of life for the hunters, but is "
"one of the main sources of food for our people. You can partake in the "
"annual meat hunt is you wish. You can hunt either for fox, deer, or any "
"other animal. All you have to do is bring back six units of meat.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Because these animals are always on the move, I will not be able to mark "
"their exact location on your map. You will have to track them down yourself. "
"Return with six units of meat, and you will be rewarded well for your "
"services. Don't forget to use your skinner, once you have killed your prey."

msgid "start_text_quest_3761"
msgstr ""
"Silawen the Councillor has requested that you gather five shortbows and "
"twenty arrows, and deliver them to Eolindir the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3762"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName#, as we speak, young men and women are being recruited to become "
"the future protectors of Leafhelm. We cannot rely forever on warriors like "
"yourself to fight off our enemies. Leafhelm needs to train its own children, "
"to be able protect their homes and families. It is obvious that the violence "
"will never end, and there will always be somebody attacking our peaceful "
"town. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Eolindir the Fighter has been assigned to train Leafhelm's young militia. "
"Eolindir has requested that we use the weapons of our enemies, as training "
"weapons for our young recruits. Weapon such as those used by the goblins. "
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"I have been informed by Eolindir, that we are running low on bows and "
"arrows. We are always at war, and cannot afford to use our best weapons for "
"training the new. What we have noticed, is that the goblin scouts who are "
"the majority of the attacking goblins, favor the use of the shortbow. "
"Eolindir has decided that the shortbow will be used to train our young "
"archers.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to gather five shortbows and twenty arrows, and to "
"deliver them to Eolindir the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3763"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to have your archery skills put to the test by Eolindir "
"the Fighter. You must succeed in hitting the goblins twenty times with your "
"arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3764"
msgstr ""
"Very soon our new young recruits will begin training in archery. The goblins "
"attacks, although not catastrophic to our town, made it obvious that "
"Leafhelm needs to be better prepared in the future for similar attacks. "
"Therefor we have been recruiting many young warriors, to train them to "
"become the future defenders of our town.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"When defending a town, archery can provide a huge advantage. Combined "
"together with the protection of its town's strong walls, a army of well "
"trained archers can hold off an enemy for a very long time, making it in "
"some cases impossible to overcome.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I have a challenge for you. How do you feel having your "
"archery skills put to the test? I would very much like to see your skills "
"with the bow. All you need to do, is to score twenty successful hits against "
"the goblins only by using archery. Hit the goblins twenty times with your "
"arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3765"
msgstr ""
