msgid "start_text_quest_3766"
msgstr ""
"We have reached that time of the year, when all our hunters prepare for the "
"big meat hunt. We organize the hunters around this time of the year, because "
"of the many groups of deer and fox that pass near our lands. Both the deer "
"and fox can be harvested for their meat, and meat is one of the main sources "
"of food for the majority of our people. We must keep our people fed and "
"happy.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"If you wish, you can take part in the big meat hunt, and gather six units of "
"meat. Hunting either deer, fox, or any other animal does not really matter. "
"If you accept, you will have to track down the prey yourself. I cannot mark "
"their exact location on your map, because most of these animal are always on "
"the move. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Bring back six units of meat, and you will be rewarded well for your "
"services. Don't forget to take along your skinning knife."

msgid "start_text_quest_3767"
msgstr ""
