"Councillor has requested that you gather five shortbows and twenty arrows, "
"and deliver them to Yman the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3768"
msgstr ""
"It is obvious that Leenglow will have to be better prepared in the future to "
"withstand many more attacks and invasions, be it either from goblin hordes, "
"raiding dwarves, or any other enemy. Sending out brave warriors to slay the "
"goblins, or strengthening our wall, are only some of the many things that we "
"can do. We must also continue preparing new warriors, to protect our town "
"and its people in the future. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Yman the Fighter will be the one training our young warriors. According to "
"Yman, it is not in our best interest to use our finest equipment for "
"training purposes. Fortunately, Yman has come up with an excellent idea. "
"What we can do, is to collect the weapons of our enemies, and to use them as "
"training weapons for our young warriors.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Yman is to soon begin training the young archers. For their training, many "
"bows and arrows will be needed. We have noticed that the goblin scouts, who "
"are the majority of the attacking goblins, favor the use of the shortbow. It "
"is these bows that we will be using for training purposes.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to gather five shortbows and twenty arrows, and to "
"deliver them to Yman the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3769"
msgstr ""
