"attacking, he who is well trained in the art of archery, has a huge "
"advantage against his opponent. He can manage a many attacks against his "
"opponent, before needing to draw his sword and engaging into hand to hand "
"combat. But it is also one of the best ways to defend a town or city from "
"behind the cover of its strong solid walls.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, do you wish to be tested in the art of archery? I would very "
"much like to see your skills with the bow. If you agree, I have a little "
