msgid "start_text_quest_3801"
msgstr ""
"Very soon our new young recruits will begin training in archery. The goblins "
"attacks, although not catastrophic to our town, made it obvious that "
"Valfather's Edge needs to be better prepared in the future for similar "
"attacks. Therefor we have been recruiting many young warriors, to train them "
"to become the future defenders of our town.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"When defending a town, archery can provide a huge advantage. Combined "
"together with the protection of its town's strong walls, a army of well "
"trained archers can hold off an enemy for a very long time, making it in "
"some cases impossible to overcome.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I have a challenge for you. How do you feel having your "
"archery skills put to the test? I would very much like to see your skills "
"with the bow. All you need to do, is to score twenty successful hits against "
"the goblins only by using archery. Hit the goblins twenty times with your "
"arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3802"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Azog the Merchant. Bring back to Azog six "
"unit of meat, from either hunting fox, armadillo or any other animal. You "
"will need a skinner for this quest."

msgid "start_text_quest_3803"
msgstr ""
"It is that time of the year, where our hunters go out for the big meat hunt. "
"We organize the hunters around this time of year, because of the many fox "
"and armadillo that pass near our lands. Both the fox and armadillo can be "
"harvested for their meat, and meat is the main source of food for the "
"majority of our people.  #PlayerName#, our people must be kept fed and happy."
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"You can take part in the big meat hunt if you wish to. Hunting either fox, "
"armadillo, or any other animal does not really matter. All you have to do, "
"is to bring back six units of meat. If you accept, you will have to track "
"down the prey yourself. I cannot mark their exact location on your map, "
"because most of these animal are always on the move. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Bring back six units of meat, and you will be rewarded well for your "
"services. Don't forget to take along your skinning knife."

msgid "start_text_quest_3804"
msgstr ""
"In order to begin training New Flayed Elf's next batch of archers, Vilethug "
"the Councillor has requested that you gather five shortbows and twenty "
"arrows, and deliver them to Biggor the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3805"
msgstr ""
"It is obvious that New Flayed Elf needs to better prepared in the future for "
"many more attacks and invasions, be it either from goblin hordes, raiding "
"dwarfs, or any other enemy. Sending out brave warriors to slay the goblins, "
"or strengthening our wall, are only some of the many things that we can do. "
"We must also continue training new warriors, to protect our town and its "
"people in the future. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Biggor the Fighter will be the one training these young warriors. According "
"to Biggor, it is not in our best interest to use our finest equipment for "
"training purposes. Fortunately, Biggor has come up with an excellent idea. "
"What we can do, is to collect the weapons of our enemies, and to use them as "
"training weapons for our young warriors.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Biggor the Fighter is to soon begin training New Flayed Elf's young archers. "
"For their training, many bows and arrows will be needed. We have noticed "
"that the goblin scouts, who are the majority of the attacking goblins, favor "
"the use of the shortbow. It is these bows that we will be using for training "
"purposes.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to gather five shortbows and twenty arrows, and to "
"deliver them to Biggor the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3806"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to have your archery skills put to the test by Biggor the "
"Fighter. You must succeed in hitting the goblins twenty times with your "
"arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3807"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for bringing earlier those bows and arrows. They will definitely "
"be put to good use by our young trainee archers.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Archery is a vital part of combat, be it either attacking or defending. When "
"attacking, he who is well trained in the art of archery, has a huge "
"advantage against his opponent. He can manage a many attacks against his "
"opponent, before needing to draw his sword to engage in hand to hand combat. "
"But it is also one of the best ways to defend a town or city from behind the "
"cover of its strong solid walls.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, do you wish to be tested in the art of archery? I would very "
"much like to see your skills with the bow. If you agree, I have a little "
"test for you. I want you to score twenty successful hits against the goblins "
"only by using archery. Hit the goblins twenty times with your arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3808"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Gulgon the Merchant. Bring back to Gulgon six "
"unit of meat, from either hunting fox, armadillo or any other animal. You "
"will need a skinner for this quest."

msgid "start_text_quest_3809"
msgstr ""
"We are preparing to organize a group of hunters to go gather meat for the "
"townsfolk. Around this time of the year, large groups of fox, and sometimes "
"deer, pass through our lands. This is a great opportunity to hunt both the "
"fox and armadillo for their meat. Not everybody agrees with the idea of a "
"mass organized hunt, but meat is the main sources of food for most of our "
"people.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"If you want to, you can take part in the hunt. All you need to do is to "
"bring back at six units of meat. Hunting either fox, armadillo, or any other "
"animal does not really matter. You will have to track down the prey "
"yourself. I cannot mark the exact location of the animals on your map, "
"because they are always on the move. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Bring back six units of meat, and you will be rewarded well for your "
"services. Don't forget to take along your skinner."

msgid "start_text_quest_3810"
msgstr ""
"In order to begin training Metal Heart's next batch of archers, Bosork the "
"Councillor has requested that you gather five shortbows and twenty arrows, "
"and deliver them to Killoroth the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3811"
msgstr ""
"The council has requested that we hasten the training of our new recruits. "
"It is obvious that the violence will not end any time soon, and there will "
"always be somebody attacking our town. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Killoroth the Fighter will be training Metal Heart's young warriors. "
"Killoroth has requested that instead of using up our best equipment for "
"training purposes, we should gather the weapons of our enemies, and to use "
"them as training weapons for our future warriors.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"I have been informed by Killoroth that there is a shortage in bows and "
"arrows. If we are to prepare our next batch of archers, both are needed in "
"great numbers. We have noticed that the goblin scouts, who are the majority "
"of the attacking goblins, favor the use of the shortbow. It has been decided "
"that the shortbow will be used to train our young archers.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to gather five shortbows and twenty arrows, and to "
"deliver them to Killoroth the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3812"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to have your archery skills put to the test by Killoroth "
"the Fighter. You must succeed in hitting the goblins twenty times with your "
"arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3813"
msgstr ""
"The bows and arrows you brought in earlier, are already being put to good "
"use by our young archers. Metal Heart's next batch of archers will be ready "
"in no time.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Archery plays a very important part in warfare. When one is well trained in "
"the art of archery, that one will have a huge advantage against his enemy. "
"While attacking, the archer has the opportunity of scoring many hits against "
"the enemy, before resorting to hand to hand combat. Hits that will have "
"tipped the balance of the battle's outcome to his or hers favor. But the "
"archer is also vital to the protection of a town and its people. Archery "
"combined with the protection of solid strong walls, is very difficult and in "
"some cases impossible to overcome.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, do you wish to have your archery skills put to the test? I "
"would very much like to see your skills with the bow. If you agree, I have a "
"simple test for you. All you need to do, is to score twenty successful hits "
"against the goblins only by using archery. Hit the goblins twenty times with "
"your arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3814"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Grabgold the Merchant. Bring back to Grabgold "
"six unit of meat, from either hunting fox, armadillo or any other animal. "
"You will need a skinner for this quest."

msgid "start_text_quest_3815"
msgstr ""
"The hunters of our town are preparing for the annual meat hunt. Groups of "
"fox and armadillo travel through our lands this time of year. You "
"understand, that this is a grand opportunity to hunt these animals for their "
"meat.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Hunting wild game for meat, not only is a way of life for the hunters, but "
"is the main source of food for our people. You can take part in the annual "
"meat hunt is you wish. All you have to do is hunt either for fox, armadillo, "
"or any other animal, and bring back six units of meat.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Because these animals are always on the move, I will not be able to mark "
"their exact location on your map. You will have to track them down yourself. "
"Return with six units of meat, and you will be rewarded well for your "
"services. Don't forget to use your skinner, once you have killed your prey."

msgid "start_text_quest_3816"
msgstr ""
"Uzrok the Councillor has requested that you gather five shortbows and twenty "
"arrows, and deliver them to Angorok the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3817"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName#, as we speak, young men and women are being recruited to become "
"the future defenders of Chopping Necks. We cannot rely forever on warriors "
"like yourself to fight off our enemies. Chopping Necks needs to train its "
"own children, to be able protect their homes and families. It is obvious "
"that the violence will never end, and there will always be somebody "
"attacking our town. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Angorok the Fighter has been assigned to train the new defenders of Chopping "
"Necks. Angorok has requested that we use the weapons of our enemies, as "
"training weapons for our young recruits. Weapon such as those used by the "
"goblins. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"I have been informed by Angorok, that we are running low on bows and arrows. "
"We are under attack, and cannot afford to use our best weapons for training "
"the new. What we have noticed, is that the goblin scouts who are the "
"majority of the attacking goblins, favor the use of the shortbow. Angorok "
"has decided that the shortbow will be used to train our young archers.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to gather five shortbows and twenty arrows, and to "
"deliver them to Angorok the Fighter."

msgid "start_text_quest_3818"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to have your archery skills put to the test by Angorok the "
"Fighter. You must strike the goblins twenty times with your arrows."

msgid "start_text_quest_3819"
msgstr ""
