msgid "start_text_quest_3820"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Isabel the Merchant. Travel to {$v18}, get "
"the trading report letter from Robert the Merchant, and bring it to back to "
"Isabel in {$v19}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3821"
msgstr ""
"Robert the Merchant has given you her trading report letter. Deliver it to "
"Isabel the Merchant and collect your reward."

msgid "start_text_quest_3822"
msgstr ""
"I need somebody to travel to {$v18}, and report to Robert the Merchant. It "
"has been over two weeks when I last received a trade report letter from him."
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Once a week, usually towards the end of the week, the merchants that are "
"posted at various trading posts, send a report letter on how trade has been "
"faring in the region. The reports are vital to trade, as they are one of the "
"few ways to keep track of what goods are selling and what not. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"I want you to travel to {$v18}, and get that report letter from Robert. You "
"will receive your payment when you return back to me with the report letter. "
"You will find Robert the Merchant to the north of here, in {$v18}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3826"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to travel to {$v20}, and to deliver a bag to Sofia the "
"Merchant."

msgid "start_text_quest_3827"
msgstr ""
