"for delivering the bag to her. You may now return to {$u20}, speak the code "
"word to Thora, and collect your reward."

msgid "start_text_quest_3828"
msgstr ""
"I'm looking for somebody to help me out. I need an item delivered to Sofia "
"the Merchant.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Sofia recently left for {$v20}, to replace the previous merchant that was "
"stationed there. But Sofia being the hasty character she is, forgot some of "
"her luggage, including a bag with many important documents inside. "
"Fortunately her sister discovered this, and has brought the bag to me. All I "
"need is for somebody to travel to {$u20}, and deliver the bag to Sofia. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Are you willing to deliver the bag to Sofia? If you accept, once you have "
"delivered the bag to Sofia, Sofia will give you a code word. This code word "
"you will have to report back to me, so I can be sure know that you have "
"delivered the bag. Only then will you receive your payment. You will find "
"Sofia the Merchant to the northeast of here, in {$v20}."

