"code word to Ulfrid, and collect your reward."

msgid "start_text_quest_3858"
msgstr ""
"I'm looking for somebody to help me out. I need an item delivered to Helga "
"the Merchant.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Helga recently left for {$q08}, to replace the previous merchant that was "
"stationed there. But Helga being the hasty character she is forgot some of "
"her luggage, including a bag with many important documents inside. "
"Fortunately her sister discovered this, and has brought the bag to me. All I "
"need is for somebody to travel to {$q08}, and deliver the bag to Helga. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Are you willing to deliver the bag to Helga? If you accept, once you have "
"delivered the bag to Helga, Helga will give you a code word. This code word "
"you will have to report back to me, so I can be sure know that you have "
"delivered the bag. Only then will you receive your payment. You will find "
"Helga the Merchant to the east of here, in {$q08}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3859"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to deliver the small package that Erling the Merchant has "
"given you, to Ornulf the Merchant in {$o10}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3860"
msgstr ""
"Ornulf the Merchant has given you the merchants secret code word, after "
"delivering Erling's package to him, as proof of the delivery. You may now "
"return to Eirhjelm, speak the code word to Erling, and collect your reward."

msgid "start_text_quest_3861"
msgstr ""
"I need somebody to deliver a small package to Ornulf the Merchant, who is "
"stationed at the trading post in {$o10}.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Just before he left for {$o10}, there was a change in plans. From being "
"stationed in {$o10} for a few days, poor Ornulf will now be there for a few "
"weeks. Fortunately Ornulf managed to send me a list of items that he needs, "
"via another traveling merchant.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"I have prepared a small package here, with the items he has requested. All I "
"ask is that you deliver this package to him. When you have handed the "
"package to Ornulf, he will give you a code word. This code word you will "
"report back to me, so I may know that the package has been delivered. Only "
"then will you receive your payment.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"So, can I rely on you to deliver this package? You will find Ornulf the "
"Merchant to the south of here, in {$o09}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3862"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Agnor the Merchant. Travel to {$p10}, get the "
"trading report letter from Borr the Merchant, and bring it to back to Agnor "
"in Valfather's Edge."

msgid "start_text_quest_3863"
msgstr ""
"Borr the Merchant has given you his trading report letter. Deliver it to "
"Agnor the Merchant and collect your reward."

msgid "start_text_quest_3864"
msgstr ""
"I need somebody to travel to {$p10}, and report to Borr the Merchant. It has "
"been over two weeks when I last received a trade report letter from him.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Once a week, usually towards the end of the week, the merchants that are "
"posted at various trading posts, send a report letter on how trade has been "
"faring in the region. The reports are vital to trade, as they are one of the "
"few ways to keep track of what goods are selling and what not. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"I want you to travel to {$p10}, and get that report letter from Borr. You "
"will receive your payment when you return back to me with the report letter. "
"You will find Borr the Merchant to the west of here, in {$q10}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3865"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to travel to {$w14}, and to deliver a bag to Uzkar the "
"Merchant."

msgid "start_text_quest_3866"
msgstr ""
"Uzkar the Merchant has given you the merchants secret code word, as proof "
"for delivering the bag to him. You may now return to New Flayed Elf, speak "
"the code word to Azog, and collect your reward."

msgid "start_text_quest_3867"
msgstr ""
"I'm looking for somebody to help me out. I need an item delivered to Uzkar "
"the Merchant.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Uzkar recently left for {$w14}, to replace the previous merchant that was "
"stationed there. But Uzkar being the hasty character he is, he forgot some "
"of his luggage including a bag with many important documents inside. "
"Fortunately his brother discovered this, and has brought the bag to me. All "
"I need is for somebody to travel to {$w14}, and deliver the bag to Uzkar. "
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Are you willing to deliver the bag to Uzkar? If you accept, once you have "
"delivered the bag to Uzkar, Uzkar will give you a code word. This code word "
"you will have to report back to me, so I can be sure know that you have "
"delivered the bag. Only then will you receive your payment. You will find "
"Uzkar the Merchant to the south of here, in {$w14}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3868"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to deliver the small package that Gulgon the Merchant has "
"given you, to Kulgarash the Merchant in {$u14}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3869"
msgstr ""
"Kulgarash the Merchant has given you the merchants secret code word, after "
"delivering Gulgon's package to him, as proof of the delivery. You may now "
"return to Metal Heart, speak the code word to Gulgon, and collect your "
"reward."

msgid "start_text_quest_3870"
msgstr ""
"I need somebody to deliver a small package to Kulgarash the Merchant, who is "
"stationed at the trading post in {$u14}.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Just before he left for {$u14}, there was a change in plans. From being "
"stationed in {$u14} for a few days, Kulgarash will now be there for a few "
"weeks. Fortunately Kulgarash managed to send me a list of items that he "
