"\r\n"
"So, can I rely on you to deliver this package? You will find Kulgarash the "
"Merchant to the west-southwest of here, in {$u14}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3871"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted a quest from Grabgold the Merchant. Travel to {$u12}, get "
"the trading report letter from Akzar the Merchant, and bring it to back to "
"Grabgold in Chopping Necks."

msgid "start_text_quest_3872"
msgstr ""
"Akzar the Merchant has given you her trading report letter. Deliver it to "
"Grabgold the Merchant and collect your reward."

msgid "start_text_quest_3873"
msgstr ""
"I need somebody to travel to {$u12}, and report to Akzar the Merchant. It "
"has been over two weeks when I last received a trade report letter from her."
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Once a week, usually towards the end of the week, the merchants that are "
"posted at various trading posts, send a report letter on how trade has been "
"faring in the region. The reports are vital to trade, as they are one of the "
"few ways to keep track of what goods are selling and what not. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"I want you to travel to {$u12}, and get that report letter from Akzar. You "
"will receive your payment when you return back to me with the report letter. "
"You will find Akzar the Merchant to the north of here, in {$u12}."

msgid "start_text_quest_3874"
msgstr ""
"Thora the Merchant has offered to reward you each time you accept to hunt "
"twelve units of meat for her."

msgid "start_text_quest_3875"
msgstr ""
"#PlayerName#, ready to hunt some more? As with all of my hunters, the same "
"applies to you. Bring me twelve units of meat, and the reward is yours. You "
"can hunt for deer, fox, or whatever else can provide us with meat. You "
"choose."

