"destroyed. #PlayerName#, I want you to attack the goblin shaman village, and "
"kill four goblin shamans. Enough with their pathetic little spells. We will "
"stop their attacks by crippling them from the top of whatever hierarchy they "
"might seem to have."

msgid "start_text_quest_4232"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to search the goblin shaman village near {$t19} for the "
"goblin shrine, and to destroy it. According to Jonn the Mage, twenty solid "
"hits should be enough to destroy the goblin shrine."

msgid "start_text_quest_4233"
msgstr ""
"The goblin shamans believe that is it the goblin god Ngobil that has given "
"them the ability to cast spells. They believe that they are the chosen ones "
"that must guide and protect the goblin race. It is from this faith in their "
"god, that the goblin shamans draw their strength from.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Somewhere in the goblin shamans village, their should be a shrine dedicated "
"to the goblin god Ngobil. It is through the power of the shrine that the "
"shamans believe that they attain their spellcasting abilities. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Your task  #PlayerName# will be to search the goblin shamans village near "
"{$t19} and to destroy the goblin shrine, therefor destroying the shamans "
"belief in their spellcasting abilities. When you have located the shrine, "
"wielding any of your melee weapons use physical force to desecrate it. "
"Twenty solid hits should be enough to destroy it."

msgid "start_text_quest_4234"
msgstr ""
"Jonn the Mage has instructed you attack the goblin shaman village and kill "
"four of the annoying goblin shamans."

msgid "start_text_quest_4235"
msgstr ""
"It is obvious by now, that it is the goblin shamans are the ones leading the "
"goblin attacks. If they are the true leaders or are following orders from "
"elsewhere, I do not know. What I do know is that by attacking the goblin "
"shamans and weaken them, we will be delivering a crippling blow to the "
"goblins as a whole.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, I want you to attack the goblin shaman village, and kill four "
"goblin shamans."

msgid "start_text_quest_4236"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to search the goblin shamans village near {$v19} for the "
"goblin shrine, and to destroy it. According to Caradwen the Mage, twenty "
"solid hits should be enough to destroy the goblin shrine."

msgid "start_text_quest_4237"
msgstr ""
"The goblin shamans are causing problems by leading the goblin hordes against "
"our people. It is imperative that we find a way to stop them.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"The shamans believe that Ngobil, the father and creator of the goblin race, "
"created the goblin shamans to guide the goblins. Therefor Ngobil blessed the "
"shamans with the ability of spellcasting. If we can somehow destroy the "
"goblins shamans faith in Ngobil, we might be able to disrupt the shamans "
"work.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"In the goblin shamans village near {$v19}, there should be a shrine "
"dedicated to the goblin god Ngobil. By destroying the shrine, the one thing "
"that represents their connection to their god, we can destroy the shamans. "
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Search the goblin shamans village near {$v19} for the goblin shrine. When "
"you have located the shrine, wielding any of your melee weapons use physical "
"force to desecrate it. Twenty solid hits should be enough to destroy it."

msgid "start_text_quest_4238"
msgstr ""
"Caradwen the Mage has instructed you to go to the goblin shaman village and "
"kill four goblin shamans."

msgid "start_text_quest_4239"
msgstr ""
"After observing the goblins, we have come to the conclusion that the goblin "
"shamans are the ones coordinating the goblin attacks. Therefor it is logical "
"that to weaken the goblin attacks against {$v19}, we must attack the goblin "
"shamans.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"#PlayerName#, attack the goblin shaman village, and kill four goblin "
"shamans. Once you have completed this simple but vital task, report back to "
"me."

msgid "start_text_quest_4240"
msgstr ""
"You have accepted to search the goblin shamans village near {$o23} for the "
"goblin shrine, and to destroy it using physical force with any of your melee "
"weapons. According to Kaelat the Mage, twenty solid hits should be enough to "
"destroy the goblin shrine."

msgid "start_text_quest_4241"
msgstr ""
"All goblins worship the goblin deity Ngobil, but none more than the goblin "
"shamans. The goblin shamans believe that Ngobil has chosen them as his "
"favorite to defend and guide the goblin race. That is why he has blessed "
"them with the spellcasting abilities which they have, to be able to fulfill "
"this important role that has been given to them. But intelligent as the "
"goblin shamans might be, they are still goblins, they are still primitive. "
"\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Where there are goblins shamans, there is always a goblin shrine dedicated "
"to Ngobil the goblin god. By protecting this shrine, the shamans believe "
"that they are protecting the spellcasting abilities given to them. Destroy "
"the shrine, and you destroy the shamans. \r\n"
"\r\n"
"Destroying the shrine will not actually remove the spellcasting abilities of "
"the shamans, but will surely remove them from the battle while they run "
"around franticly trying to discover who and how desecrated their precious "
"shrine. I want you to search the goblin shaman village near {$o23} for the "
"goblin shrine. When you have located the shrine, while wielding any of your "
"melee weapons, use physical force to desecrate it. Twenty solid hits should "
