msgid "start_text_quest_4451"
msgstr ""
"Report to William the Councillor to complete your basic training in "
"Sandbrook."

msgid "start_text_quest_4452"
msgstr ""
"I believe that William the Councillor is waiting to hear from you, as to how "
"your basic training has come along. #PlayerName#, please report to William "
"the Councillor."

msgid "start_text_quest_4453"
msgstr ""
"Aidan the Councillor has asked you to report to Kai the Fighter to begin "
"your combat training. Kai the Fighter has been highlighted on your map. To "
"interact with Kai the Fighter, use to F key."

msgid "start_text_quest_4454"
msgstr ""
"Welcome to the Heart of Eanna. Our town is experiencing a goblin outbreak, "
"one that could threaten the safety of our people. Before we ask you to "
"assist us removing the goblins from the surrounding lands, we must make sure "
"that you are well prepared.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"We will begin with your combat training with Kai the Fighter. Kai the "
"Fighter is highlighted on your map. Walk up to Kai and interact with him "
"using the F key. One you have reported for training, use the F key to talk "
"to Kai again, and then select the quest tab to see what tasks Kai might have "
"for you. To accept a quest, simply hit the accept button."

msgid "start_text_quest_4455"
msgstr ""
"Kai the Fighter has instructed you to hit the training dummies with your "
"Leafblade five times. The location of the training area has been highlighted "
"on your map."

msgid "start_text_quest_4456"
msgstr ""
